ɡafakʼarafitewakʼɪlafafɪɡubaumeɡafasɪlaftɪduwafulaɪnkʼabduakaɪndʒirtuammalledukantɪdimmubɪsanɪɡubadʒirtɪɪrrenɪwakʼaɡudonɪbɪsanɪɡubadedemtɪdʒennanɪwakʼɪwandʒedeɪfsanɪhatahudubaɪfsanɪtahewakʼɪakaɪfsanɪsunɪdansaarɡeɪfsafɪdukanaɡarɡarɪbasedʒennanɪwakʼɪɪfsanɪɡu??adʒededukananɪhalkanɪdʒedeakananɪɡalɡalɪtahediramɪlenɪtahekuninɪɡu??akʼaradʒennanɪwakʼɪwandʒedewontɪbɪsanɪfullalamatɪɡarɡarɪbasahatatudubawakʼɪwansunɪmɪdaseakananɪbɪsanɪwansunɪɡubadʒɪrafɪkadʒaladʒɪraleɡarɡarɪbasedubaakumasunɪtatewakʼɪwanbɪsanɪɡarɡarɪbasasuninɪɡubadʒedeakananɪɡalɡalɪtahediramɪlenɪtahekuninɪɡu??alamesodʒennanɪwakʼɪwandʒedebɪsanɪlafaɡubadʒɪranɪhafullatokotɪwoltɪdebɪanɪakabi??enɪɡodunɪmullatudubaakumasunɪtatewakʼɪbɪ??eɡodusuninɪlafadʒedeammallebɪsanɪwoltɪdebɪanɪsuninɪbarinɪdʒedewakʼɪwontɪkuninɪdansaarɡewakʼɪwandʒedelaftɪlatehamukhafɪmarraɡosatʃʼahaufabaftumukhamɪdanɪkilletifɪmitʃɪranɪkʼabufɪkainkʼamneledubaakumasunɪtatedubalaftɪlatemukhafɪmarraɡosatʃʼahaufakamɪdanɪkilletifɪkamitʃɪranɪkʼabufɪkainkʼamnelebaftewakʼɪwontɪkuninɪdansaarɡeakananɪɡalɡalɪtahediramɪlenɪtahekuninɪɡu??asadesodʒennanɪwakʼɪwandʒedeɪfsanɪhaɡubamullatuakahalkanifɪɡu??aɡarɡarɪbekhanɪammalleɪfsanɪkunɪhaɡubaifsuakalaftɪifsaarɡatudʒededubaakumasunɪtateakananɪwakʼɪifsaɡuɡurdalamatoltʃeadutaɡu??amohatudʒiakahalkanɪmohatuammalleurdʒilemɪdaseinnɪifsasunɪɡubaka?eakalafatɪifsehalkanifɪɡu??amohateɪfsafɪdukanaɡarɡarɪbasuwakʼɪwontɪkuninɪdansaarɡeakananɪɡalɡalɪtahediramɪlenɪtahekuninɪɡu??aafresodʒennanɪwakʼɪwandʒedebɪsanɪwanlubukʼabaheduhadalanɪsimpɪrrelenɪhaɡubakʼɪllensakesabariftuakananɪwakʼɪbɪnensaɡuɡurdafɪdɪdikʼakabɪsanɪkesaɡalusɪmpirreɡosatʃʼahaufalewolinɪumewakʼɪwontɪkuninɪdansaarɡewakʼɪwankanatʃʼahaufaebisewandʒedehorabulabarinɪɡutasimpɪrrelenɪhoralafairadabradʒedeakananɪɡalɡalɪtahediramɪlenɪtahekuninɪɡu??aʃanesodʒennanɪwakʼɪwandʒedehorifɪbɪnensɪɡosatʃʼahaufaɡudafɪdikʼalenɪlafaɡubatɪhadalatulonifɪbɪnensalafairalohufɪbɪnensaɡosatʃʼahaufahedulenɪhadalatudubaakumasunɪtateakananɪwakʼɪbɪnensaɡosatʃʼahaufakalafairalohufɪkaillonnefɪammallehorilet utʃʼahaɪnatʃaɪsatokokesafudefullasunɪakumaduritɪdebisedubatʃʼahaɪnatʃakesafudanɪkanɪnamauwatoltʃenamɪtʃatinɪdufedʒennanɪnamitʃɪwandʒedeeɡɪufɪdʒɪbadelafelafetɪ??akesabate?okhanɪfonɪfonɪkɪ??akesabahe?aarɡadeuwaɪsinɪdʒedanɪwanɪsinɪdirakesabatefɪnamɪtʃafɪnɪtinɪkʼulla?anɪammoɡafasɪwantʃʼahaeraimbekhanɪnɪtinɪtanɪwandʒetenɪmɪdanɪmukhaobrutanakesadʒirukamafenuɲannaammowakʼɪwannunɪdʒedemɪdanɪmukhawodakaobrukesaedʒuiɲatina?okhanɪinkʼabatina?oɲatanɪindotanɪdʒedeammobofɪwannɪtinɪdʒedelakɪakasɪnitɪindotanɪwakʼɪɪmbekhaakaɡu??aɪsanɪɲatanɪiltɪtesanɪbanamteakawakʼatatanɪwanhamtufɪdansaɡarɡarɪbetanɪdubanɪtinɪakamɪdanɪmukhasunɪɲatadansatifɪɪlamɪdaɡoaɡarteammalleakaɪsanɪhubatʃanamakennanɪdaɡennanɪbukʼifteɲatedɪrsalekenniteinnɪlenɪɲatedubaworralatʃuiltɪbanamteakakʼulla?anɪufɪarɡanɪobensaodawoltɪkʼabanɪkʼullanɪdofatanɪɡalɡalasunɪabowakʼaobrukesademudaɡa?anɪdʒennanɪdɪrsafɪnɪtinɪɪsamukhadubatɪdokhatanɪammoabowakʼɪnamitʃa?ameatinɪesadʒirtadʒedeɡafateinnɪwandʒedeaninɪedʒatakankeobrukesatɪdaɡa?eakakʼullademuufɪarɡedubasodadedokhadeinnɪwandʒedenɪenutɪkʼullademtasinɪdʒedeatinɪmɪdanɪaninɪiɲatinaisaninɪdʒedekanɪ?aɲatenamitʃɪwandʒedenɪnɪtumaatinɪwahelanakennitetanitɪnatinɪdufenaɲatʃiseabowakʼɪwannɪtinɪdʒedewontɪatinɪtatekuninɪmalnɪtinɪwandʒetenɪbofatɪnasobedʒennanɪɲadedʒennanɪabowakʼɪwanbofanɪdʒedewanatinɪakanatatefɪaninɪlasiabareatinɪhorifɪbɪnensaalatʃʼahaufaɪraɡorteɡaranɪlafairalotehaɡadʒirtutʃʼahaufabɪ??eɲataaninɪsifɪnitɪtanaɲapawoltɪtoltʃedalotɪkesanɪlenɪwolɪdʒibadalotɪɪsimatasitʃʼahaaraseatɪlenɪhirbaworraɲataammallewaninnɪnɪtinɪdʒedehodʒdʒaatinɪɡaratʃoftudibasitɪɡudisehodʒdʒaatinɪdaltuletʃʼahainɪnfatedukubsataammohatatutɪdirsakankeɡudodʒalatedaratefɪinnɪlenɪsimohataammallewannamɪtʃanɪdʒedewanatinɪkʼonkʼonitɪtetɪtʃʼahaakʼaftemɪdanɪmukhaaninɪiɲatinɪsinɪdʒedeɲatefɪlafafɪbi??enɪsifɪabaramtɪitɪɡarɡaltumalesaɡalekesaɪɲatuhaɡadʒɪrennaketɪtʃʼahaufaɪsinɪhoɡorafɪkʼoratɪsitɪbaftɪatɪlenɪrafuɲatahodʒatedamfitumalesaɡaleɪɲatuhaɡabɪ??ekesabatetɪdebɪtutɪatinɪkʼarabɪ??ebi??umasunitɪdebitanamitʃɪnitɪmakʼahawaɪ nadʒabesaesautɪhima?oinnɪfulakesaɪsanɪdufewanɪsanɪdʒetanɪhodʒatunɪtante?akobonɪeɡetennadʒira?akobonɪwanufinɪdʒedeaninɪhorɪkanatʃʼahaufaesaukenneaka?owolɪarɡinuinnɪɡaranalafebɪranademuakananɪhorɪesauerɡekanɪufɪduraerɡeammoufɪeɡetɪhafebulehalkanumasunɪ?akobonɪkaenadenɪɪsalamanifɪnadenɪhodʒatulamanifɪɪdʒolleɪsakudanɪtokofudateɡalana?abokɪtakedʒarɪkunɪtakedʒennanɪhorifɪhodʒatuɪsaletʃʼahaufatakɪsiseufɪkobaeɡetɪhafedʒennanɪnamɪinnɪɪmbennedufeɪsanɪwolwolanehaɡabɪftunɪbatutɪnamɪsunɪaka?akoboindabsannearɡedʒennanɪtafadaemɪtatɪbukʼiseinnɪwan?akobonɪdʒedelaftɪ?abariteɡadɪnalakisɪɪndema?akobonɪillakisuhaɡaatinɪnaebɪftutɪdʒedenɪnamitʃɪwandʒedenɪmakʼanɪkeenudʒennanɪinnɪ?akobodʒedenamitʃɪwandʒedenɪmakʼanɪkearmaatʃɪ?akobonitɪatinɪ?awakʼafɪnamanɪwolmorkɪtanɪlatʃudabsatetanafɪmakʼanɪkankeisraelɪtaha?akobonɪfullasunɪpenɪelɪmakʼabasewandʒede?awakʼanɪfulakesawolarɡineɪrahafeadunɪbananɪ?akobonɪkatafahokolupenɪelɪkesabahehaɡaarraleɡotʃitɪisraelɪfonɪtafaɪɲatuwanfullasunɪ?akobodanifɪ?akobonɪesaufɪdʒarɪɪsakadibaafurɪkanɪkaɡadɪdufudʒɪranɪarɡedʒennanɪɪlmanɪtaɡarɪleakʼodetaɡarɪrahelikʼodeammalletaɡarɪnadenɪhodʒatutanɪlamanitɪkʼodeinnɪnadenɪhodʒatutanifɪɪlmanɪɪsiduraanseleafɪɪlmanɪɪsiitɪanserahelifɪ?usufueɡeanseufɪworradurademeobolesaɪsatɪdiannanɪmarotorbaduratɪɡadʒedeammoesaunɪfulakesautaleitɪmamarateisadunɡateworrɪlatʃuwoltɪboheesaunɪufɪdatumɪllatenadenifɪɪdʒollearɡeworrɪɪsanɪwolinɪdʒɪrtanɪkuninɪkaenudʒedenɪ?akobonɪwandʒedenɪaboidʒollenɪtuninɪtawakʼɪebanɪnakennedʒennanɪnadenɪhodʒatutanifɪidʒollenɪɪsidufteduratɪɡadʒeteakumasunɪleafɪidʒollenɪisɪlenɪdufteeɡe?usufufɪrahelinɪdufanɪduratɪɡadʒedanɪesaunɪwandʒedenɪworrɪaninɪkʼarabahenɪsunɪmanɪworrɪkamɪkana?akobonɪwandʒedenɪworrɪki??umakaaninɪnasusɪrafedadademunɪammoesaunɪwandʒedenɪɡurbaaninɪ?akʼufewankʼabduolumake?adɪ?akobonɪwandʒedenɪakananitɪ?oatinɪnasunakʼabatewananinɪsikennukanafudaduaɡartanɪfulaketɪakanamafulawakʼaarɡenatɪfakatɪeɡɪatinɪammadʒalalahaɡanaɡetunaɡarsiftewananinɪsidufenɪkananarafudaduwakʼɪ?ananahenakʼubse?akobonɪɪtumadowefudatʃiseesau inɪammalleworrakɪ??aɡadisudideaninɪborɪawanisalafatetɪbusaawanisɪsunɪlafatʃʼahaufakʼabatebɪ??etʃʼahaufadossewanboka?adakhanɪrobuɪrahafekaniletʃʼahaufaɲatemukhaobrutantekesatɪhafetʃʼahaufafitamanenɪtetifɪtahodʒatutantetifɪammalletaworramɪsirɪtʃʼahaufaawanisɪɪnɡutawontɪkuninɪwanabafɪababotɪtesanɪhaɡadalatelafatanaduftehaɡaarratakainarɡinɪtatɪdubaakanadʒennanɪkaefaraobɪrademehodʒatunɪfaraowandʒetenɪnamitʃɪkunɪ?aɡudowanhamtunutɪmalatenuballeseinnɪ?omɪwankanalakisadirtɪtʃʼahaallanɪha?ateabowakʼaworrasunɪkadatuatinɪakalaftɪtennatamɪsirɪtuninɪbaduɪnɡartudubamusafɪharunɪfaraotinɪdufanɪdʒennanɪfaraonɪwanworranɪdʒedebenɪdakʼaabowakʼakesanɪkadadaammoenufatɪ?amusanɪwandʒedenɪnutʃʼahauftɪi??anaɪdʒolletennafɪdʒaroletennafɪɪlmanɪtennafɪretennafɪlonɪkennalenɪtʃʼahauftɪi??anɪwontɪakanatifɪnudʒilaɡudoabowakʼatoltʃufenafaraonɪwandʒedenɪwakʼɪnadɪdinna?oaninɪisanifɪɪdʒolletesanɪɡadiseaninɪakaɪsanɪmalahamaɡarakʼabdanɪarrakaleinarɡinɪaninɪ?adideɪsanɪdirtɪtʃʼahaallanɪ?aabowakʼa?amadaɪsanɪkʼaratanabarbadanɪdubaworrafulafaraoduraɡussanɪdʒennanɪabowakʼɪwanmusanɪdʒedeharkakankelafamɪsirɪɡubakʼabɪakaawanisɪlafamɪsirɪtʃʼahaufakʼabatewanbahatʃʼahaufakaboka?adakhanɪrobukanɪɪrahafeɲatefitudubamusanɪuleufiolkʼabeabowakʼɪlenɪbubeilaborutɪkasebubenɪsunɪɡu??asunifɪhalkanɪsunɪtʃʼahaufalafairabubifte?olaftɪborɪ??atebaritebubenɪsuninɪ?a?uawanɪsanɪduftetutɪawanisaduftelafamɪsirɪtʃʼahaufakʼabatetutɪawanisasuninɪɡudotaduranɪtakanamɪinarɡinɪkadebɪanɪeɡɪtanalenamɪɪnɡarreawanisɪlafamɪsirɪtʃʼahaufadossedukanesewanboka?adakhanɪrobeɪrahafefɪmɪdanɪmukhaletʃʼahaufaɲatewontɪdotatunɪtʃʼahauftɪtaobrukesadʒɪrtufɪtamukhaɡubadʒirtulenɪtokolenɪɪnhamnelafasunɪkesabadedʒennanɪfaraonɪhurrisemusafɪharunɪ?amewandʒedenɪaninɪ?a?uabowakʼakesanifɪisanɪletɪtʃʼahaubamearratʃʼahaallatʃʼahaubutɪ??anaararamaabowakʼakesanɪnakadadaakainnɪɡarɡaladuahamakananurafudumusanɪfaraobɪrademeabowakʼakadatedubaabowakʼɪbubedʒabdutokoɡarailaadutɪdufenɪbubenɪsunɪawanisatʃʼahaufafuteɡalanadɪmatɪnatewontɪawanisafakatatokolenɪlafamɪsirɪkesatɪɪnhamneammoab wo?abofta?okhanɪdabassitɪtananɪ?okhanɪwanɡoɡanɪmidasanɪtananɪtanaabowakʼɪwanmusanɪdʒedeadanɪnamadukubaɡoɡafudefa??enɪkʼulkʼullesanɪtanaɡu??ainnɪ?akʼulkʼullaedʒedanɪbɪ??abesɪsanɪhakʼallɪtʃatinɪdufanitɪdubakʼallitʃɪhaɡumɪkesakobabaseisailalutɪhodʒdʒainnɪkafaɲetatekʼallitʃɪhasɪmpirrekʼulkʼullolamafɪdamemukhahindesatifɪmusensadimatokofɪdameurɡotinɪkotɪdʒedunɪdʒennanɪkʼallitʃɪhasɪmpirretokookotefaratabɪsanɪmadakʼabduɡubatɪkʼalabi??anɪdʒedudubainnɪhasɪmpirretanɪfudedamehindesatifɪmusensadɪmafɪdameurɡotanɪfudediɡasɪmpirrekʼalanɪtanɪkesabusuinnɪdiɡahamarotorbanamitʃadukubaɡoɡairakʼulkʼullesanitɪfɪfite?akʼulkʼullaedʒedesɪmpirredʒirtutanɪdɪdatɪɡadisudubanamitʃɪsunɪlenɪhawo?amɪtʃatematahadatenafadɪkʼateakasinɪkʼulkʼullautɪinnɪdandaeollasenekesademaammowaroɪsahaɡabultɪtorbainseninɪɡu??atorbesoinnɪhamatafɪaredafɪrɪfensaɡarailatifɪrɪfensanafaɪsatʃʼahaufahadatewo?amɪtʃatenafadɪkʼateakananɪkʼulkʼullauɡu??asadetesoinnɪhaelemɪ?elamafɪholadalaɡannatokokakamuaboinkʼamnefɪmɪdanɪdakhanɪkakilosadikadadanɪwoltɪmakhanifɪdadadulotokokʼallɪtʃatinɪdufutɪkʼallitʃɪhanamɪtʃafɪwaninnɪbasukanatʃʼahaufafullawarowo??umatinɪdufutɪdʒennanɪkʼallitʃɪelemotokofɪdadadulokanɪfudewanɡatɪsoriobasanɪbaseolkʼabeakaabowakʼabasanɪɡarsɪsutɪinnɪelemosunɪhafullakʼulkʼullotahorɪdabanɪufɪɪrabasanɪ?okhanɪsorioɡubanɪbasanɪitɪkʼalanitɪkʼalutɪwontɪinnɪwankanatoltʃufɪwontɪɡatɪsoriobasanɪakumasoriodabanɪufɪɪrabasanɪtanɪtakʼallutɪammalleɡudokʼulkʼullokʼallitʃɪhadiɡaelemosunɪfudeɲabaɡurramirɡɪtʃatifɪkʼubaaɡitʃokaharkamirɡatifɪkʼubaaɡitʃokamilamirɡakanamakʼulkʼullesanɪsunɪtinɪkʼabukʼallitʃɪhaammalledadadikʼatokofudeharkaɪsabitatʃatɪnakʼekʼubaɪsatokokaharkamirɡadadasunɪkesaka?emarotorbadadasunɪabowakʼaduratɪfiftudubadadaharkaɪsakesadʒirukanɪhaɡatokofɪdiɡaelemolefudeɲabaɡurramirɡatifɪkʼubaaɡitʃokamilamirɡakanamitʃakʼulkʼullesanɪkanɪhaibsuammalledadaharkaɪsakesatɪhafekanɪhamatanamitʃasunɪibsuakananɪinnɪadanamanɪkʼulkʼullesanɪɡutadʒennanɪkʼallitʃɪsoriodabanɪufɪɪrabasanɪbaseadanamanɪkʼulkʼullesanɪɡutaeɡɪsunɪinnɪhorɪsorioɡubanɪkanɪk ɪirataetukʼelenɪhaɡaadunɪdɪtutɪkʼulkʼullonitɪammallenamɪwanɪinnɪirataekʼabatewo?amɪtʃatenafadɪkʼatʃumaleinnɪlenɪhaɡaadunɪdɪtutɪkʼulkʼullonitɪhodʒdʒanamɪtʃʼahaoftukʼabukaharkaindɪkʼatinɪnamadibɪkʼabatenamɪinnɪkʼabatesunɪwo?amɪtʃatenafadɪkʼatʃumaleammallehaɡaadunɪdɪtutɪinnɪkʼulkʼullonitɪokotefaratanamitʃɪsunɪtukʼeletʃʼahaabsumalanɪammalledamelamukhakainnɪkʼabatetʃʼahaufadikʼumalanɪeɡɪnamitʃɪtʃʼahaoftufa??etorbabuleinnɪwo?amɪtʃatebɪsanɪmadodɪkʼatʃumaledubainkʼulkʼullaɡu??asadetesoinnɪhasabalisalamadɪdikʼa?okhanɪɡuɡurdafudefullabalbalawarowo??umaɡesekʼallɪtʃatɪkennukʼallitʃuhasabalisasunɪtokosoriodabanɪufɪɪrabasanɪbasekanɪsorioɡubanɪbasanɪbasuakananɪinnɪadanamasuninɪkʼulkʼullesanɪɡutahodʒdʒanamɪdirahalkanɪufitɪobdʒateinnɪhanafatʃʼahaufadɪkʼatudubahaɡaadunɪdɪtutɪinnɪkʼulkʼullonitɪwaninnɪitɪobdʒateɪtiletananɪwo?atananɪdikʼumalanɪammallehaɡaadunɪdɪtutɪwontɪsuninɪkʼulkʼullonitɪnamɪdiratifɪkauwaeɡɪwolinɪrafeworrɪlatʃubɪsanɪdɪkʼatʃumaledubahaɡaadunɪdɪtutɪworrɪkʼulkʼullonitɪ?onadenɪadauwakʼabatenɪtinɪsunɪhaɡaɡu??atorbakʼulkʼullonitɪnamɪisɪkʼabatulenɪhaɡaadunɪdɪtutɪkʼulkʼullonitɪwontɪɪsinɪiratetufɪkaɪsinɪiratʃʼahauftɪkʼulkʼullonitɪnamɪsireisɪtifɪwanɪsinɪiratetekʼabatuwo?amɪtʃatenafadɪkʼatʃumaleammallehaɡaadunɪdɪtutɪinnɪkʼulkʼullonitɪhodʒdʒanamɪkaɪsinɪadauwakʼabdubirarafeinnɪlenɪhaɡaɡu??atorbakʼulkʼullonitɪammallesɪrenɪinnɪɡubatʃʼahaiselenɪkʼulkʼullonitɪhodʒdʒanadenɪadauwaɡu??aɪsimaleufɪratɪɡarte?okhanɪhodʒdʒaadanɪɪsitauwatʃʼahaitudideɪsinɪhaɡaadanɪuwasunɪɪra?atukʼulkʼullonitɪakumaɡafakʼaraɪsinɪadauwakʼabdusireɪsinɪiratʃʼahaɪftufɪwontɪɪsinɪɡafasɪiratetulenɪkʼulkʼullonitɪnamɪwansunɪkʼabatelenɪkʼulkʼullonitɪinnɪwo?amɪtʃatenafadɪkʼatʃumalehaɡaadunɪdɪtutɪinnɪkʼulkʼullonitɪeɡɪadauwakesabateɪsinɪhabultɪtorbatetudubaeɡekʼulkʼullotatɪɡu??asadetesoɪsinɪsabalisalamaɡuɡurda?okhanɪdɪdikʼafutekʼallitʃafullabalbalawarowo??umadʒɪrutɪhaɡesitudubakʼallitʃɪhatokofudesoriodabanɪufɪɪrabasanɪbasekanɪsorioɡubanɪbasudubaakananɪadaɪsinɪkʼulkʼullesanɪɡutafɪabowakʼɪwanmusafɪdʒedewanatinɪworraisraelɪtinɪd akʼatedueleɪsanɪinhalatuharrefɪlonɪhodʒdʒalafakʼotanɪwoltɪinhɪdinawo?adabassafɪboftanɪwolkesamidasanɪinke?atina?onamɪdubrafudenitɪtolfateeɡɪsunɪisɪdʒibeammalledaranɪhɪmatemakʼaɪsi?akeɪntaltɪtunɪɡafaaninɪfudeledubranitɪdʒededubaabafɪhatɪintalahawo?aworrɪirarafetadiɡakʼabdufutedʒarolediraɡarsiftudubaabanɪɪntalawandʒarolenɪdʒeduaninɪkʼaraɪntalatɪ??atanafudanamakanakenneammoinnɪamma?aisɪdʒibeammalleinnɪ?awandaratinɪhɪmateɡafaaninɪfudeleɪsinɪdubranitɪdʒedeammowontɪakaɪntaltɪtɪ??adubraɡarsiftuduɡanɪwo?atanamediɡaisɪlaladubadʒarolenɪdirasunɪhanamaɪntalafudesunɪfutedantutɪammallehaɡatɪkʼarsɪdibatokoirafudanɪabaintalatɪkennanitɪwaninnɪɪntalaɡosaisraelɪɡurraballesefɪammalleɪsinɪnɪtumaɪsatatɪdandaehaɡumadʒiruillakisuammo?owontɪinnɪhimatenɪsuninɪduɡatatekawontɪakaɪntaltɪdubraɡarsiftutokolenɪɪndʒirredubaworrɪhaɪntalatʃʼahaitʃaabaduratɪɡabaseatʃitɪdirtɪdirasunɪdakhanɪdanteidʒeftutɪɪsinɪtaatoinfudinɪkamanaabadalekesadʒirtudɪranɪwolinɪrafte?awantakainarɡinɪɡosatennataisraelɪkesatɪtateakananɪhamennaakasɪdurabatanɪ?onamɪnitɪnamadibɪtinɪrafeɪsafɪɪsilehaidʒesanitɪakananɪhamennaakasɪdurabatanɪ?onamɪɪntalakʼaranamadibɪfudakennanɪdirakesatɪarɡebufateworralatʃuhadirakesaalatɪbasanɪdakhanɪdananɪidʒesanitɪwontɪɪntalaidʒesanifɪwanɪsinɪatodirakesadʒirtukanamɪdatumidʒuɪ??udɪdefɪammallewontɪnamitʃaidʒesanifɪwaninnɪɪntalakʼaranamɪdibɪfudakennanɪbufatefɪakananɪhamennaakasɪdurabatanɪammo?oballinnalafatɪnamɪɪntalafudanamadibɪkennanɪarɡekʼabebufatenamitʃabufatetʃʼahaallaidʒesanɪammoɪntalawomaintoltʃanɪwontɪakanatifɪɪsinɪwollalaɪsiɪdʒesuintoltʃinedubinɪtuninɪdubɪnamaɡosaufɪhadeidʒesenɪwolfakatɪinnɪballɪnnumalafatɪɪntalafudanamakennanɪarɡekʼabebufateatoɪsinɪi??ɪtelekʼarkʼarsainarɡannedubainnɪhaabaɪntalasunitɪkʼarsɪʃantamabasutɪisɪlenɪhanitɪɪsatatutɪwaninnɪisɪbufatefɪhaɡadʒiruinnɪisɪillakɪsinɪnamɪkolasanifɪkanafasalamuratanɪtʃʼahaufahaɡumɪabowakʼakesakutanitɪtʃʼahaabanafɪɪlmanɪinnɪdaluhaɡadalotakudannesohaɡumɪabowakʼakesakutanitɪwontɪakanatifɪɡafaɪsanɪlafamɪsirɪkesabatanɪworrɪsaɡalefɪbɪsanɪɪsanɪdowateba akennehodɪharkaduwahadadirsaketitɪinɡalinɪnanɪdʒedenaominɪwandʒetenɪeɡɪɪntalatɪ??ahaɡawandubinɪtunɪtatuarɡɪnutɪheɡerɪnamitʃɪɪntauhaɡadubɪtanahobasutɪboatsinɪɡarafullodirasunɪdakʼeatʃɪtaedubanamitʃɪmiloantɪkaboatsinɪwanɪsadubatekanɪɡadufedʒennanɪboatsinɪisa?amewandʒedenɪdʒalɪkotɪmearmataɪinnɪɡoretaeammalleboatsinɪdʒarolekudanɪtadirasunɪ?amewandʒedenɪkotamearmatatatatanɪdʒennanɪnamitʃaɪsamiloantɪkaninɪwandʒedenaominɪtalafamoabutɪɡalteobrunamitʃaɡosatennakaelɪmelekɪdʒedanɪɡurɡurufetɪtanafɪaninɪsibesisufedeakafuladʒaroletetetutanaduratɪatɪ?ofetebɪtatu?obitufetebitɪammo?oɪmfenenatɪhimɪwontɪakanatifɪnamɪdɪbinɪkadandaebituɪndʒirusimaleanatɪsitɪananamitʃɪwandʒedenɪaninɪimbɪtadadʒennanɪboatsinɪwandʒedehatatuammoɡu??aatinɪobrusunɪnaomɪɪrabituatinɪruthiletaɡosamoabutadirsaɪnkʼamneimbɪtatabekhɪakamakʼaɪsabadɪdowartunamitʃɪmiloɪsakanɪwandʒedeaninɪdandaeɪmbitu?oɪsinɪakanatatetaɪlmanɪtɪ??aheɡerɪɪndallefullatɪ??aatumanɪbɪtadu?asiebisetanafɪnamitʃɪmilokanɪboatsinɪatumanɪbɪtadudʒedekobebafateboatsitɪkennedʒennanɪboatsinɪwandʒarolefɪnamatʃʼahaufakaartɪdʒɪrunɪdʒedeɪsanɪarraduɡatɪ??aakaaninɪnaomɪɪrawanelɪmelekɪtifɪammallewankilɪonɪtifɪkamalonɪkaharkanaomɪdʒirutʃʼahaufabɪtadesunɪmaleruthɪtaɡosamoabutamaloninɪɪradueaninɪ?abɪtadeakanitɪnatatuakananɪworrɪɪsahorɪarɡateammallemakʼanɪɪsadirakankankanafɪworrainnɪkesatɪdalatekesaɪmbaduɪsanɪarraduɡatɪ??aɪlmanɪtantetaabowakʼɪɪntalatanakenneɪsinɪsidaltuworrakankeakaworraperetsɪilma?udafɪtamarɪhatoltʃitudubaboatsinɪruthɪfudeworraufɪtinɪɡalateabowakʼɪisɪebiseɪsinɪɡaratʃofteilmadetenadenɪwannaominɪdʒetemakʼanɪabowakʼahaɡudatukainnɪsikʼabateakosikenneinnɪisraelɪkesadʒabatehaɡurrabafatuɪntaltɪilmaketɪtasidʒalateɪlmanɪtantetadiratorbanɪirawasibate?aakosidaltekadʒɪrennasidebiselubusideresudʒennanɪnaominɪdaimafutekʼomatɪkʼabatekʼabduɪsatatenadenɪrerasunɪilmɪ?anaomɪdalatedʒetemakʼaɪsaobedɪbaftefɪinnɪ?esedale?esenɪdaudɪdaleababotɪdaudɪtanadaudinɪka?ese?esenɪkaobedɪobedinɪkaboatsɪboatsinɪkasalmonɪsalmoninɪkanahʃonɪnahʃoninɪkaamɪnadabuamɪnadabunɪkaramuramunɪka amalafakaedubaeɡɪabowakʼakadatanɪworraɪsanɪkaramatɪdatʃanɪelkananɪnitɪisatinɪwolinɪbulanɪabowakʼɪkadaisɪdaɡa?efɪakananɪɪsinɪɡaratʃofteilmadaltemakʼaɪsasamuelɪbaftefɪwandʒeteaninɪɪsadʒedeabowakʼakadadehodʒanɪelkanafɪworrɪɪsaʃilodakʼesorioɡannatʃʼahaufaabowakʼabasanifɪsoriodibɪkakhuisatinɪɡutanɪɡeteammomarotanahananɪworraɡulaɪndemneɪsinɪwandirsaisɪtinɪdʒetehodʒdʒaheɡerɪaninɪdaimakanaharmaɪrakuteaninɪisamanaabowakʼatɪɡesaakainnɪhaɡumadʒirutʃʼahaufaatʃɪtauelkananɪwandʒedenɪha??ehatatutɪwanatinɪdansasetutoltʃɪhaɡaatinɪharmaɪrakututɪworrumatɪhafɪabowakʼɪwansikakhateɡutinnatanafɪhananɪworratɪhaftedaimaɪsihosɪfateeɡɪharmaɪrakuteɪsinɪisaʃɪlotɪɡesiteammalleisawolinɪdʒɪbitʃakormakaɡannasadɪtifɪkilokudanɪtadarɡa?edakhanɪtifɪɡordʒodadɪmidʒuɡesiteɡafasunɪkaɪsinɪsamuelɪmanaabowakʼatinɪdufteinnɪwandikʼaeɡɪdʒɪbitʃasunɪkʼalanɪworrɪdaimasunɪelitɪɡesedʒennanɪhananɪwandʒetenɪabokɪ??aatinɪnakʼabataaninɪnitɪbarannaatinɪaɡartetaarmaedʒiteabowakʼakadatetanɪaninɪakailmaarɡaduabowakʼakadadedʒennanɪinnɪɡurbakananakennetanafɪaninɪisaammatanaabowakʼakennainnɪhaɡadʒirutʃʼahaufakaabowakʼatɪdʒennanɪworrɪatʃitɪabowakʼakadateabowakʼɪ?a?uɡammatʃunɪɡarakɪ??aɡutemaroinnɪwankananatoltʃefɪammaɡaranɪ?a?unadʒabateaninɪammaɲapakɪ??akoblaaninɪakamɪɡammatʃukʼabamarowakʼɪnakʼarkʼarefɪnamɪtokolenɪkaakaabowakʼakʼulkʼulloɪndʒiruisamaletokolenɪkanamadʒabesekʼorkʼoratuɪndʒiruki??ibaufɪtoltʃɪtanɪlalaba?atanɪkanalakisadubɪufɪsadu?alabahawontɪakanatifɪabonɪwakʼainnɪwobekhawannamɪtoltʃutʃʼahaufaɪnkʼoraɡubeworraduladʒadʒannatʃʼahaatʃabsanɪworrɪlalafanɪdʒadʒabatanamɪdurɪsaɡaleufɪkʼufuammatanabeladʒedehudʒɪbarbadaammokakʼarabelakʼabudebieimbelaunɪtinɪkʼaramasenteamma?aɪlmanɪtorbadalteammohatɪkʼaraɪlmanɪhedukʼabduammatokoleɪnkʼabduabowakʼɪɪdʒesedʒɪresainnɪnamafullaekheraɡeseammalleɡadebisainnɪnamaɡarɪhi??omsekaɡarɪduromsakaɡarɪdɪkʼeseammokaɡarɪɡudisainnɪhi??e?ɪawarakesafudenamalafawomaɪnkʼamnefulladaraitɪharanɪkesabasainnɪworrasunɪworraɡuɡurdawolinɪtesisebartʃumaɡudinnakennafɪ?a?abɪlafakaabowakʼatɪinnɪɪsiɪratɪwantʃʼahaufadʒ tokofudedʒidumispatifɪʃenɪoldabewandʒedehaɡakanatʃʼahaufaabowakʼɪ?a?unukʼarkʼaredubainnɪdakhasunɪebentserɪmakʼabaseakasɪdʒetʃanɪdakhakʼarkʼarsadʒetʃadubaakananɪworrafɪlistɪdabsatanɪhaɡasamuelinɪdʒirutʃʼahaufaabowakʼɪworralafaisraelɪhadudowediraworrɪfɪlistɪkʼabatekaekronifɪɡathɪdʒidudʒirutʃʼahaufaɡosaisraelitɪdebɪsanɪdubaakananɪworrɪisraelɪlafaufɪtʃʼahaufaarɡateammalledʒiduworraisraelɪtifɪworrakananilelaftɪnaɡa?atatesamuelinɪhaɡalafaɡubadʒirutʃʼahaufadʒallabaisraelitɪtaheworramohateɡannatʃʼahaufainnɪɪmaltulafamarebethelɪɡɪlɡalɪmispadakʼelafasunɪtʃʼahaufakesadubɪkʼorenamawoltɪnaɡa?atoltʃedubaeɡeworraufɪkaramadʒɪrutɪɡaleatʃɪletɪdubɪkʼoreramakesatɪinnɪfullasorioitɪkʼalanɪabowakʼadʒaresamuelinɪdʒaredʒennanɪɪlmanɪɪsadʒallabotaisraelɪtoltʃeilmɪɪsakaanɡafamakʼanɪ?oelɪmanditʃamakʼanɪabɪ?aɪlmanɪtuninɪlamanɪdʒallababerʃebatateammoɪlmanɪtuninɪkaraabaɪsiɡulai??aneɡudobesedʒalateɡula?ateɡumbonamaɪrafudateduɡaɡuladubɪkʼorudidedʒennanɪdʒarolenɪisraelɪtʃʼahauftɪwoltɪbateɡarasamuelɪkaramadʒirudatewandʒetenɪatinɪamma?adʒarteɪlmanɪtantekarakankeɡula?autɪɪndʒirtutanafɪha??unudurademunutoltʃɪakanulenɪakaɡosadibɪha??ukʼabanukʼonkʼonɪworrɪha??unukennɪdʒedeisakadatesuninɪsamuelɪinɡammatʃimnetanafɪinnɪabowakʼakadateabowakʼɪwandʒedenɪwanbi??itɪsinɪdʒetutʃʼahaufadʒalakʼabɪɡutɪworrɪsiɪndinneammoanakaha??uworradidehaɡumalafamɪsirɪkesabaheworrɪnalakisewakʼadibɪkadateworrɪammawomakʼaranatoltʃesitoltʃudʒiratanafɪdubaammaatinɪworratʃʼahaakʼasɪammoworraɡorsɪwanha??otɪsuninɪworratoltʃituhubatʃisɪsamuelinɪwanabowakʼɪdʒedenɪtʃʼahaufabɪ??aha??uisakadatesunɪtʃʼahaufatɪhimewandʒedenɪwontɪha??unɪkesanɪɪsanɪtoltʃutanainnɪɪlmanɪtesanɪɡureaskartɪtoltʃataɡarɪɡarɪfardɪhirkɪsunɪhodʒatɪtaɡarɪ?abatufardatɪtaɡarɪfardaduraoritɪinnɪtaɡarɪfudeɡudanamakumtokotoltʃataɡarɪɡudanamaʃantamatoltʃaɪlmanɪtesanɪobruɪsakʼotefatʃaftehamtɪammotaɡarɪmihalolatifɪkaɡarɪsunɪmidasitɪdubritɪtesanɪkʼa??aɪsamidasitekʼɪtafɪsaɡaleledabdifɪinnɪobrutesanɪdadansatamidanɪtifɪtatsabɪbutifɪtaedʒersafudehodʒatuufitɪkʼodainnɪmɪdanɪkesanifɪtsabibutes ɪɡudodallanedʒennanɪinnɪkʼotɪ?olamafudekʼaleɡaraɡarɪtʃʼahairefonɪsunɪnamalafaisraelɪtʃʼahaufakesaerɡewandʒedenamasaulofɪsamuelɪhadisaɡulaɪndemnetʃʼahaufakʼotɪ?oɪsaakanatoltʃanɪworrɪisraelɪwanheɡerɪabowakʼɪtoltʃusodatenamɪtʃʼahauftɪhaɡumaɡahunɪwoltɪbahesaulonɪbetsekitɪworrawoltɪbasenamɪisraelɪkesakumadibasadɪka?udalenɪnamakumasodomadubawanerɡatu?abeʃɪtinɪdʒedanɪwanɪsanɪworrakesaninɪdʒetanɪborɪatoadunɪɡubaindufinuɲapakesanɪduraɪsanɪbasanɪworrɪ?abeʃɪdamsasunɪdaɡa?edʒennanɪakamaleɡammadanɪwannahaʃinɪdʒedanɪborɪharkaisanitɪkennannawanfetanɪnutoltʃaborɪ??atesaulonɪaskartɪɪsafullasaditɪɡaraɡarɪkʼodeɡanamahodʒdʒabɪftunɪbateollaɲapaworrakaamonitɪtʃʼahaabsanɪhadanɪ?oɡu??anɪwolkʼɪtae?ahobasanɪkafiɡelenɪɡarɡarɪbaheabukarumaufɪbakʼatedʒennanɪworrɪisraelɪwansamuelinɪdʒedemeworrɪsaulonɪha??ukennaɪntaudʒedekanɪharkatɪnukennaworrasunɪinhobafnaammosaulonɪwandʒedenamatokolearainɪdʒesanɪwontɪakanatifɪɡu??anɪkuninɪɡu??aabowakʼɪisraelɪbasedubasamuelinɪwanbi??anɪdʒedekotanu?asaɡɪlɡalɪdanneammalleakasaulonɪha??ukennadʒabesineakadansanamatʃʼahaufatɪhimnatanafɪworrɪtʃʼahauftɪɡɪlɡalɪdakʼefullawo??umatɪabowakʼaduratɪsaulonɪha??ukennadʒedanɪlalabanɪsoriowoldaɡetɪbasanɪsaulofɪworrɪisraelɪtʃʼahauftɪdʒilatolfatanɪdʒennanɪsamuelinɪwanworraisraelɪtinɪdʒedeaninɪ?a?uwanɪsanɪkadatanɪtʃʼahaufaisaniɡuteha??uisanikenneɪsatɪammatanaɪsanɪfideisaninɪdemaaninɪɡamaki??anɪ?a?udʒarearraeɪlmanɪti?alenɪtanumahaɡumakaɪmomaki??atɪasɪisanumadurademaaninɪammakunotɪhodʒdʒaaninɪwo?akeammatananahɪmadaabowakʼafɪha??uinnɪmudekanaduratɪaninɪtakalonifɪharre?a?unamairafudadeaninɪtakanamasobe?okhanɪ?adabseaninɪtaka?a?uɡumbonamairafudade?oaninɪwankanatokoletoltʃeanɪamumatanabasabi??itɪwandʒetelakɪatinɪtakanusobdenuindabsineatinɪtakanamatokoleirawantokoleinfudannesamuelinɪwandʒedenɪabowakʼafɪha??unɪinnɪfohatekuninɪaraduɡanatahanɪakaɪsanɪwollalanaradabdanɪbi??itɪwandʒetenɪeduɡumaabowakʼatɪduɡatennasamuelinɪammallewandʒedenamɪmusafɪharunɪfohateababotatesanɪlafamɪsirɪkesabaseabowakʼaammafullumadʒɪrtanɪtanaedʒandʒadubaaninɪabowakʼad nnɪdaudɪkʼufudideiladibɪtinɪlaleborɪ??atewakʼɪdʒinnɪsaulotɪerɡedʒɪnninɪsuninɪisakʼabatemanaisakesatɪmaratʃitedaudinɪakumaɡu??atʃʼahaufatoltʃekanɪkɪrarɪdaudʒiraammosaulonɪworanaharkakʼabadʒennanɪinnɪworanasunɪmarolamadarbewandʒedeaninɪdaudɪakanaworanemanatɪmatansaammodaudinɪmarolatʃumɪlikʼedurabahewanabowakʼɪisalakisedaudɪɡulabahefɪsaulonɪdaudɪsodatetanafɪsaulonɪdaudɪufɪbɪrabaseɡudaaskartɪkumatokotoltʃedaudinɪaskartɪisadulanɪdakʼewanabowakʼɪisawolinɪdʒɪrufɪwantʃʼahaufadabsatesaulonɪakainnɪwantʃʼahaufadabsatuarɡedʒennanɪhaɡakʼaraleiraisasodateammonamɪisraelifɪ?udakesadʒirutʃʼahauftɪdaudɪdʒalatewaninnɪnamadansanamadurademutahewantʃʼahaufadabsatefɪdʒennanɪsaulonɪwandaudinɪdʒedeɪntalatɪ??aɡudotamerabudʒedanɪtanasikennahodɪfudɪammohodʒdʒafuteaskartɪdʒannatateabowakʼahodʒatʃumaltesaulonɪwanufinɪdʒedeaninɪharkaki??anɪisaɪntukʼuhaworrɪfɪlistɪisaidʒesutɪdaudinɪwandʒedenɪaninɪenukʼaraworrɪkenalenɪisraelɪkesaenukaaninɪɪntalaha??ufuduammohodʒdʒanɪdaudinɪmerabufuduɡennanɪisalakɪsanɪnamitʃatokokaadɪrɪelɪdʒedanɪkaworrameholathitɪkennanɪdubaɪntaltɪsaulotamɪkalɪdʒedanɪɡudodaudɪdʒalatesaulonɪakasɪdaɡa?edʒennanɪɡudoɡammadewanufinɪdʒedeaninɪmɪkalɪdaudikennaakaɪsinɪtururaitɪtatedubaworrɪfɪlistɪisaɪdʒesudubamarolamesosaulonɪwandaudinɪdʒedeɪntalatɪ??afudɪdʒennanɪsaulonɪhodʒatuufɪ?amewandʒedenɪdaudɪ?amakobatɪhasanɪwandʒetaninɪha??unɪ?asimatʃehodʒatunɪisalenɪ?asidʒalatetanafɪammaɪntalaɪsafudɪdubadubɪtanadauditɪhɪmanɪdʒennanɪinnɪwandʒedeɪsanɪsodaha??utahitɪwandikʼosetanɪaninɪhi??esanamɪlenɪnaɪmbekhuworrɪhodʒatukanɪdubɪdaudinɪdʒedetanɪsaulotɪhimesaulonɪwandʒedenɪwanɪsanɪdaudinɪdʒetanɪwontɪkʼarataɪntalakaha??unɪsirafedumissadibalamakaatinɪworrafɪlistɪɪdʒeftemuratedubaakasinɪhalonabaftudʒedeakananɪsaulonɪakaworrɪfɪlistɪdaudɪɪdʒesumalatehodʒatunɪsaulodubɪtanadauditɪhimtedʒennanɪinnɪakasodaha??utahuɪraɡammadeatoɡu??anɪfudainɡainudaudifɪworrɪɪsa?aenamadibalamakaɡosafɪlistɪfitemissaworrakamuratekanɪtʃʼahaufafudeha??uduranɪdufeakaakasinɪsodaha??utahudʒennanɪsaulonɪɪntalaɪsamɪkalɪdaudikennesaulonɪakaabowakʼɪdaudɪwolinɪdʒiruarɡeammalleakaɪntaltɪɪsamikalinɪisadʒalatulearɡɪnanɪhaɡakʼarairadaudɪsodatehaɡadʒirutʃʼahaufaɲapaitɪtaheaskartinɪworrafɪlistɪakumakʼarakanɪworraisraelɪtinɪwolhatɪammohodʒdʒawolɪhadanɪsunɪtʃʼahaufadaudinɪaskartɪsaulotanɪtʃʼahaufairaworraballeseakananɪɡudobekhameɡurrabafatesaulonɪilmaisa?onathanifɪhodʒatuisatʃʼahaufawoltɪ?amewandʒedeaninɪdaudɪɪdʒesufedaammo?onathaninɪɡudodaudɪdʒalatatanafɪwandaudinɪdʒedeabonɪsiɪdʒesufedaborɪdɪramaufɪeɡadɪfullatokotɪdokhadɪatʃumataɪaninɪdemefullaatinɪitɪdokhatusunɪabobiraedʒewankankeitɪhasa?oaninɪwodaɡa?esitɪhima?onathaninɪdansumadaudɪsaulotɪhasaewandʒedenɪabohodʒatutantedaudɪwanhamtuintoltʃinɪwontɪinnɪtoltʃetʃʼahauftɪɡudosikʼarkʼarteinnɪlubuufɪdedeɡolɪathɪɪdʒeseakasinɪdubaabowakʼɪworraisraelɪharkaɲapakesabasedabsatʃiseatɪnɪlenɪwansunɪaɡartedʒennanɪɡammadeatinɪmanifɪammanamawomai??akinɪitɪtʃʼahaubamtefa??umatanadaudɪɪdʒesufetasaulonɪdubɪ?onathanɪtʃʼahaakʼasemakʼaabowakʼatinɪkakhatedaudɪinɪdʒesudʒededʒennanɪ?onathaninɪdaudɪ?amedubɪsunɪtʃʼahaufaitɪhimedubaisasauloduranɪdufedaudɪlenɪakumadurɪkanɪsaulohodʒateammalleworanɪworraisraelɪtifɪkafɪlistɪkanɪkaedaudinɪworrahadeakaduɡadabsatebakʼatʃiseɡu??atokoatosaulonɪmanaisakesataukainnɪworanaharkakʼabuatodaudinɪtaekɪrarɪdaudʒɪnninɪabowakʼɪerɡetanɪisairabutesaulonɪdaudɪworananɪhademanatɪmatansufedeammodaudinɪduramɪlikʼeworanɪsuninɪmanaworanekesatɪhafedubadaudinɪhalkanumasunɪkaebakʼatedʒennanɪsaulonɪnamamanadaudɪeɡuerɡeakaborɪ??ateisaɪdʒesuammonɪtinɪɪsamikalinɪwandʒetenɪ?oatinɪhalkanɪkanaimbakʼatinɪborɪɪndotadubaɪsinɪdereʃamanatinɪɡabufteinnɪkaebakʼatedʒennanɪɪsinɪwanharkanɪmidasanɪkakadatanɪfutesireɡubaketeboratɪrɪfensaretinɪmidasanɪmatadʒalaketewo?aitɪu?ifteworrɪsaulonɪerɡekanɪdaudɪkʼabudufedʒennanɪmikalinɪinnɪfa??anitɪdʒetenɪammosaulonɪworrakesadebisewandʒedenɪɪsanɪɪlumatesaninɪisaarɡasireɪsawolinɪbadakotanɪinɪdʒesaworrɪdufemanaolsenewanbotʃanɪkadatanɪkanɪkaboratɪrɪfensaretinɪmidasanɪmatasabatetʃʼahaisusireɪratɪarɡesaulonɪwanmikalinɪdʒedeatinɪmanifɪakananasobdeɲapakɪ??abakʼatʃifteɪsinɪwandʒetenɪɪsatɪ?oatinɪnaɡadisubatesiɪdʒesananɪdʒededʒetedaudinɪbakʼatesamuelɪkaramadʒɪrunɪbahewansaulonɪisatoltʃetʃʼahaufaitɪhasaedʒennanɪɪsafɪsamuelinɪna?othɪdakʼanɪatʃɪtanɪsaulonɪakadaudinɪna?othɪkaardaramakesadʒiruitɪhɪmanɪdʒennanɪinnɪnamaisakʼabuitɪerɡeworrɪraɡotatalalabdesɪrbutɪdʒirtukasamuelinɪɡudaworraarɡedʒennanɪlubunɪabowakʼadʒarasauloirabuteworrɪlenɪlalabesirbesaulonɪakasɪdaɡa?edʒennanɪnamadɪbileerɡeworrɪsunɪlenɪakasumalalabesirbeinnɪmarosadesolenamaerɡeworrɪsulenɪakasumatahedubaeɡeinnɪlenɪkaedemeramatɪitɪdabateelaɡudatokokadekudʒedanɪɡennanɪsamuelifɪdaudɪodefatedʒennanɪna?othɪdʒiradʒedaninɪatoinnɪatʃɪdemulubunɪwakʼaɪsaleirabuteinnɪkarana?othɪlalabesɪrbaitɪdabateinnɪwo?atʃʼahaufaufɪira?asesamuelɪduratɪsirbeɡu??asunifɪhalkanɪsunɪkʼullakʼunkʼumatʃʼahaiseakananɪdʒetʃɪsaulolenɪ?araɡatahedʒedanɪɡabahedʒennanɪdaudinɪdirana?othɪkaardaramakesadʒiruka?ebakʼate?onathaninɪbahewandʒedenɪaninɪmanɪ?akewollalɪkɪ??amanɪwontɪhamtunɪaninɪabakanketoltʃekainnɪnaɪdʒesufedufɪmanɪ?onathaninɪwandʒedenɪwakʼɪdusidɪdinnaabanɪkɪ??awantokoleatoɪsinɪdikʼotateɡudotatekanatɪinhɪminɪɪntoltʃutanafɪtantetanalenaɪndossudubinɪsuninɪɪndʒirtudaraammodaudinɪwandʒedenɪabeɪmbekhaakaatinɪnadʒalatutanafɪinnɪwannatoltʃufedukanasitɪhimudideakaatinɪhamennaɪraɪnɡarreaninɪmakʼaabowakʼadʒirutinɪkakhadaakadotɪdɪkʼolefaɡonaraɪndʒirre?onathaninɪwandʒedenɪwanatinɪfetutʃʼahaufaaninɪsitoltʃa?oabenadabeakaaninɪworrakennakabethlehemudakʼesoriowoɡadakʼabadudʒennanɪatinɪnaɡadifteitɪhimɪ?oinnɪha?ehademutɪdʒedeaninɪ?abaheammo?oinnɪdallaneakainnɪnaballesufedusuninɪbetaammoatinɪɡamakanketinɪnanahɪkakhudʒabdunuabowakʼaduratɪwoltɪkakhannedʒabesɪɡutɪammo?oaninɪwollalakʼabadeatumanɪnaɪdʒesɪmanifɪabetitɪnaɡesita?onathaninɪwandʒedenɪlakɪaboakasɪindʒedinɪ?oduɡumaaninɪakaabonɪsiballesebekheanɪsitɪɪnhimudʒennanɪdaudinɪwandʒedenɪ?oabedallansunɪsidʒaladubateenutɪnatɪhimadʒennanɪ?onathaninɪwandʒedenɪkotɪɡaraobrunu?asɪdʒennanɪworrɪwolinɪ?ae?onathaninɪwandaudinɪdʒedeabowakʼɪisraelɪduɡanutahinnaborifɪɪftanɪhodʒdʒatanaaninɪabakɪ??adubɪtanɪitɪhima?oaninɪakaɡaranɪɪsasitɪdansaarɡekʼonkʼosierɡa?oammoɡaranɪɪsasitɪhamaarɡeabowakʼɪnaidʒesinna?oaninɪsidosselubutanteimbasinɪabowakʼɪsiwolinɪdʒiratinnaakumainnɪabakɪ??awolinɪdʒɪratehaɡaaninɪdʒirukakhuatinɪkakhatedʒabesɪnanahɪammo?oaninɪduenasunaaɡarsifteworraki??aleɡarsisɪammalleeɡɪabowakʼɪɲapakennatʃʼahaufaballesekakhunɪnuwoltɪkakhannehaakumaufɪdʒɪratuhodʒdʒakakhunɪsuninɪtʃʼahaabdeabowakʼɪɡarɡalanɪsitɪdufaammalle?onathaninɪakahaɡumadʒirutʃʼahaufadaudinɪisadʒalatuisakakhatʃisewontɪakanatifɪ?onathaninɪakumaufɪdʒalatudaudɪdʒalatadʒennanɪ?onathaninɪwandaudinɪdʒededʒiltɪbatɪborɪ?ofullasaɡaletɪsidabanɪimbekhanɪakaatinɪartɪɪndʒirreɪftanɪdabisɪkankehaɡakaleleiramullatatanafɪfullaatinɪkʼaraitɪdokhatetanɪdakʼɪdakha?ewoltɪtulanɪdubatɪdokhadɪaninɪdubatɪ?asadinɪhadaakawanabirudubaaninɪɡurbatokoerɡebenɪtɪ?asunɪɡaɡurɪdʒedanɪhodʒdʒaaninɪɪlalɪti?itɪmoɡatantetanadʒirtɪɡurɪɪsanɪdʒedelaftɪnaɡa?aɡabahɪdʒetʃuaninɪmakʼaabowakʼadʒirutinɪkakhadawontɪatinɪsodatuɪndʒirtuammo?oaninɪti?itɪmoɡatantesunɪdʒirtɪdʒedenɪkaɪdemɪabowakʼɪ?asidemsiseammallekakhunuwoltɪkakhannetanɪkʼabadɪabowakʼɪduɡatennanafɪsidʒidudubadaudinɪobrukesatɪdokhatedʒiltɪbatɪɡennanɪha??itʃɪsaulonɪmanasaɡaleitɪɲatanɪdufefullumaɪsatadurɪtanɪmanatɪanetaeabɪnerinɪdatuɪsatae?onathanɪlenɪisadurataefullanɪsiladaudinɪtauduwaammosaulonɪɡu??asunɪwomaɪndʒennewontɪakanatifɪinnɪwandaudinɪwotaheakasinɪkʼulkʼullomadabedʒilahankʼateseheborɪ??ateleɡu??aadesalamafullanɪdaudinɪtauakumakanɪduwadubasaulonɪ?onathaninɪdaudinɪarafɪkalelemanifɪsaɡaledʒilaɲatʃuindufinɪdʒedeɡafate?onathaninɪwandʒedenɪinnɪaninɪbethlehemudemufedanaɡadisɪdʒedenakadateammallewannanɪdʒedewontɪaninɪdemumalefɪworrɪkennaarrasoriowoɡakʼalataobolesɪki??alenɪ?a?usiindabinɪdʒedekʼonkʼonatɪerɡetanafɪ?oatinɪdʒalakɪ??atatenaɡadisɪakaaninɪfitatɪ??aarɡudakʼunanɪdʒedewontɪinnɪfullasaɡaleindufɪnifɪtanasaulonɪakahama?onathanitɪdallanewandʒedenɪilmatʃʼahaabanaaninɪɪmbekhaakaatinɪdaudɪɡulabateufifɪhadasidalteletʃʼahaersituatinɪɪnɡartuakaatinɪha??ulafatanatɪɪntanehaɡada dinɪ?a?udiradakhanɪmarsanɪakanabodʒaranɪdakʼetururakesaufɪbusedʒennanɪsaulonɪaskartɪɪsatʃʼahaufawoltɪ?ameakaworrɪkeiladakʼedaudifɪworraɪsamarsehadudaudinɪakasaulonɪhadisaitɪmalatudaɡa?edʒennanɪwankʼallitʃaabɪatharinɪdʒedewo?aakakorbohidatanɪtaninɪkotɪdʒennanɪdaudinɪwandʒedeabowakʼaisraelɪaninɪakasaulonɪanahodʒatutantetitɪdʒedekeiladufeakahadeballesumalate?adaɡa?eworrɪkeilaharkasaulotɪnaɪnkennasaulonɪkaɪndufadʒedanɪduɡumaɪndufaeabowakʼaisraelɪnatɪhimɪabowakʼɪwandʒedenɪeɪnumadufaammalledaudinɪwandʒedeworrɪkeiladuɡumaanafɪdʒarakɪ??aharkasaulotɪkennaabowakʼɪwandʒedenɪɪnumakennadubadaudifɪdʒarɪɪsakanamadibadʒaɡahuhodʒumasunɪkeilakanɪkafullatokolekʼubatanɪitɪɪnturedurumatɪɡodananɪsaulonɪakadaudinɪkeilakesabakʼatedaɡa?edʒennanɪmalaitɪdatekanɪlakisedaudinɪlafaɡarenɪtalafaalotadatutsifukesakesatɪdokhateatʃumataesaulonɪɡu??atʃʼahaufaisabarbadeammowakʼɪdaudɪharkaɪsatɪkennudidedaudinɪkahoreʃɪlafaalotadatutsifukesadʒiruakasaulonɪisaɪdʒesufeduhubatedʒennanɪ?onathaninɪartitɪitɪdufeakawakʼɪdandaeisakʼarkʼaruitɪhimeɡaradʒabesewandʒedenɪinsodatinɪabanɪkɪ??asaulonɪdandaewomasiɪntoltʃuinnɪɪmbekhaakaatinɪha??uisraelɪtateaninɪsitɪanuworrɪlatʃuwakʼaduratɪwoldakʼewoltɪkakhatedʒennanɪdaudinɪhoreʃɪdakʼeammo?onathaninɪworraufitɪɡaleworrɪtokotsifubaheɡarasaulokaɡɪbeadʒirudakʼewandʒedenɪdaudinɪlafatennatahoreʃɪɡarahakilaɡubalafaalota?udeaɡamabɪtakesatɪdokhatudʒiranuɪmbennaeha??itʃaakaatinɪɡudoisakʼabufetutanafɪlafatennakotɪnuakainnɪɪmbanneisakʼamneharkaketitɪkenninasaulonɪwandʒedenɪabowakʼɪɪsanɪebɪsinnawanɪsanɪakananakʼabatanifɪbenaakadansakʼorkʼoradafullainnɪdʒɪrufɪnamaisaatʃitɪarɡeleakadansahubadawananinɪdaɡa?einnɪɡudomalakʼabafullainnɪitɪdokhatuakadansahubadamarotokotukotanabesisadubaaninɪɪsanɪwolinɪdeme?oinnɪlafasunɪkesadʒɪrateatolafa?udatʃʼahaufakesabarbadelekʼabumaleɪntaudubaworrɪsaulobɪra?aetsifudatʃaedaudifɪdʒarɪɪsaɡafasɪlafaɡamodʒɪtamaonɪdʒɪranɪbalealotalafaɡamodʒɪta?udeaɡamabɪtakesasaulofɪdʒarɪɪsadaudɪbarbadudakʼanɪammodaudinɪmalaworradaɡa?ekubɪdakha?elafaalotamaonɪdakʼeatʃɪtaesaulonɪ ruaninɪkʼoranɪtʃʼahaabsatʃuarmadufeakadubadebiewandikʼokʼabusunɪdabadeilmakɪ??awolinɪɲannewolumanɪdonuelɪ?anɪwanɪsinɪdʒedeinsodatinɪbenɪsaɡaletantedabaduammokʼarakʼitadikʼatokonadabɪnatinɪkotɪdubawanhafesifɪilmɪkankedabadawontɪakanatifɪabowakʼɪisraelɪwandʒedekʼorinɪtantedarɡa?edakhanɪɪndabdukillakankeledadanɪkesainhobauhaɡaaninɪboka?aisanirobutɪnɪtinɪhi??etinɪtanɪdemtewanelɪ?anɪdʒedenɪtʃʼahaufaɡuteɪsafɪworrɪɪsitʃʼahauftɪhaɡaɡu??ahedusaɡaleɲateakumaabowakʼɪelɪ?anɪdʒedekanɪkʼorinɪɪsidarɡa?edakhanɪɪndamneammallekillaɪsidadanɪkesainhobanedubaeɡɪsunɪilmɪnitɪhi??etɪsunɪfa??adabedudamelubudabeɪsinɪwanelɪ?anɪdʒetenamitʃawakʼakanaaninɪmanɪ?akekaatinɪakananatoltʃituatinɪtʃʼahaubutɪ??awakʼakʼabsifteakananɪilmakɪ??aɪdʒesudufteelɪ?anɪwandʒedenɪɡurbanatɪɡakennɪinnɪɡurbakanɪharkaɪsitɪfudemanaɡubakainnɪitɪɡaluɡesesireufɪiratʃʼahaɪfsisedʒennanɪabowakʼakadatewandʒedeeabowakʼakɪ??aatinɪmanifɪnitɪhi??etɪtanawanhamtuakanakanatoltʃitaɪsinɪɡudonakʼorkʼorateatinɪammoilmaɪsiɪdʒeftadʒennanɪelɪ?anɪmarosadɪɡurbaɡubatɪdirɪrfatewakʼakadatewandʒedeeabowakʼakɪ??aɡurbakanalubuitɪdebisɪdubaabowakʼɪkadatʃaelɪ?adaɡa?elubuɡurbasunitɪdebiseɡurbanɪdʒirennatɪdebiedʒennanɪelɪ?anɪɡurbafudeɡadinɪbuehadatɪkennewandʒedenɪmeɪlalɪɡurbanɪkeɪndʒiraɪsinɪwandʒetenɪaninɪamma?aduɡefadeakaatinɪduɡumanamawakʼaammalleakaabowakʼɪduɡumasinɪdubatu?aarɡeeɡɪbultɪheduɡannasadesokaolahamtusunɪkesaabowakʼɪwanelɪ?anɪdʒedebenɪahabuarɡudakʼɪdubaaninɪboka?anɪisanidufadʒennanɪelɪ?anɪahabuarɡudakʼeolanɪlafasamariakesatɪɡudodʒabatedʒennanɪahabunɪobadianamitʃahudʒɪmanaha??utɪɡuda?ameobadɪanɪnamaɡudoabowakʼasodatuɡafa?etsebelinɪraɡotaabowakʼafiteobadɪanɪraɡotadibatokofudeɡodadakhakesatɪʃantamaʃantamanɪdossesaɡalefɪbɪsanɪkennefɪahabunɪwanobadɪanɪdʒedememadafɪlaɡatʃʼahaufakesanu?asɪmarrafardolefɪɡanɡeledudowubarbannaakasinɪheɡerɪhorɪkennalububamnaworrɪlatʃuedʒedelafaaburudakʼuwolɡafateabukaraufɪitɪdabateatoobadɪanɪkarademuelɪ?anɪbaheisahubateduratɪɡadʒedewandʒedenɪaboelɪ?akuninɪduɡumasiinnɪwandʒedenɪeanumabenɪha??ɪtʃanɪelɪ?anɪ?adufedʒedɪob eaninɪnainsobinɪsinɪɪndʒennedʒennanɪelɪʃanɪwanɡehatsinɪdʒedemartɪfadɪhurrisɪuletɪ??afudadɪdemɪnamafulakesasidufelenaɡa?ainfudinɪ?okhanɪ?onaɡa?asifudaniledʒaladidɪbenɪmanaolsenɪuletɪ?atanamataɡurbasunɪiraka?ɪdʒennanɪnɪtinɪwanelɪʃanɪdʒeteaninɪmakʼakanketifɪkaabowakʼatinɪkakhadaakasibɪraɪndemnedubaworrɪlatʃukaewolinɪkedatʃaeɡehatsinɪworraduraitɪdabateuleeliʃatanɪmataɡurbairaka?eammoɡurbanɪsunɪdɪkʼoletʃotʃoeilakaɪsaleinɡarsimnedʒennanɪinnɪɡaraeliʃadebiewandʒedenɪɡurbanɪɪnkaneelɪʃanɪartinɪbahedʒennanɪɡurbadueufumasireɪsairatʃʼahaisuarɡedubainnɪitɪolsenebalbalatʃʼahaufateabowakʼakadatedʒennanɪinnɪɡurbairaɡatʃiseafanifɪɪlafɪharkaufɪkaɡurbairake?ateatoinnɪdirɪrfateɡurbairatʃʼahaisunafɪɡurbaowedʒennanɪelɪʃanɪkaemanakesadedemeammalledebieakumakʼarakanɪɡurbairatʃʼahaisedʒennanɪɡurbanɪmarotorbahatɪfateilabanatedʒennanɪelɪʃanɪɡehatsɪ?amebenɪhadaɡurba?amɪdʒedenɪɪsinɪduftedʒennanɪwandʒedenɪɡurbanɪkankekunokanafudadɪɪsinɪmilaelɪʃatɪdʒideɡalatadebɪftefɪɡurbaufɪfudatekateitɪdabatebaratokokalaftɪtʃʼahauftɪbelaelɪʃanɪɡilɡalitɪdebieatoinnɪɡumɪraɡotabarsisudʒiruinnɪwanhodʒatuisatinɪdʒedeokoteɡudoɪbidairadabɪworrakanasaɡaledabɪɡumɪraɡasunɪkesanamɪtokoakaurɡoɡuruobrudakʼedʒennanɪbukʼeufumanɪbatuarɡemɪdanɪwansunɪheduɡureɡalenɪkawanisɪɪmbennetʃʼahaatʃabseokotesaɡaletanitɪnakʼesaɡaletanɪraɡotabasanɪammoakumaworrɪafanɪke?atenɪworrɪɪ??ewanelɪʃanɪdʒedeenamawakʼasaɡalenɪtuninɪhadakʼabdɪdandennaɪɲannuelɪʃanɪmɪdanɪdakhanɪnatɪkennadʒedeokotekesabusewandʒedeammabɪ??aɡololtʃadʒennanɪsaɡalenɪsuninɪmɪdadeɡu??atokonamitʃɪtokobalʃaliʃadufekʼitadɪdamakamɪdanɪɡarbukakʼaramuranɪɪramidasanifɪmɪdanɪaʃedaleeliʃadufenɪelɪʃanɪwanhodʒatuisatinɪdʒedesaɡaletanaɡumɪraɡotatanakennɪammonamitʃɪwandʒedenɪatinɪwansaɡalenɪtuninɪnamadibatokoɡetusetaelɪʃanɪwandʒedenɪworrakennɪhaɲatanitɪwontɪakanatifɪabowakʼɪwandʒedusaɡaleɲatanɪkʼufanɪhambɪsanɪdubanamitʃɪhodʒatunɪkanɪsaɡaleworrakenneworrɪɲatekʼufehambiseakumaabowakʼɪdʒedekanɪaskartinɪʃamuɡafaisraelɪhatetokoɪntaladikʼotokobodʒiteɪntaltɪsuninɪeɡehodʒatunitɪnamanɪtateɡu??atokoɪs dikʼodemedʒennanɪɡehatsinɪhodʒatunɪeliʃawanufinɪdʒedebadɪabanɪkɪ??a?a?unamitʃanamanɪdʒedanɪkanakawomaɪrainfudatinɪɡadiseinnɪsilawannamitʃɪʃamusunɪɪsakenneɪrafudatʃumalewakʼɪnaidʒesinna?oaninɪhordofewansunɪirainɡuratinɪdubainnɪkaenamanɪhordofenamanɪnamaisaɡulautaluarɡedʒennanɪɡarɪɪrabuefulakesadebiewandʒedenɪisɪabomanɪlaftɪnaɡumaenaɡumaammoabanɪkɪ??anaerɡewannanɪdʒedekessumanɪlamataɡumɪraɡotataɡarenɪefraimutetuamumatananatɪduftetanafɪkʼarsɪkumasadɪtifɪwo?adʒɪlanɪtolfatanɪtanɪlamakesanakennɪnamanɪwandʒedenɪhaɡasɪnitɪkʼarsɪkumadʒafudadɪinnɪitɪdowekʼarsɪsunɪsubalamatɪnakʼefɪsubasunɪwo?adʒɪlanɪtolfatanɪtanɪlamanɪwolinɪhodʒatuɪsanamalamatɪkenneɡehatsɪduraerɡeworrɪɡaraelɪʃanɪɡubatɪɡalukanɪɡahedʒennanɪɡehatsinɪsubalamanɪsunɪworraɪrafudemanatɪɡalfatehodʒatunamanɪtanɪufɪraɡaltʃedubainnɪmanatɪdebiedʒennanɪelɪʃanɪatinɪesaduftedʒedeɡafateinnɪwandʒedenɪaboaninɪɡaru?uɪnɡalleammoelɪʃanɪwandʒedenɪhodʒdʒanamitʃɪɡarɪɪsaɪrabuefulakesasidufeaninɪhereɡaɡaraki??atinɪsiinaɡarrehodʒanɪtuninɪhodʒdʒanamɪbesefɪwo?afɪdadafɪtsabɪbufɪrefɪlonifɪhodʒatunamaɪrafudatunitɪammatanadukubɪnamanɪkanɪsikʼabatehaɡumadʒirusifɪdalotaketileɪraɪmbahuakumaɡehatsinɪisabɪrademenɪdukubusuninɪisakʼabatenafɪɪsaakadaraadateɡu??atokoɡuminɪraɡotataelɪʃanɪitɪɡudawanɪsanɪdʒetefullanɪnutennatuninɪ?anutɪdɪpateɡanudisɪɡalana?ordanɪdannemukhamananɪdʒaranɪtʃʼahairreatʃitɪdʒarrannaelɪʃanɪha??ebenadʒedenɪdʒennanɪworrɪnamɪtokowanɪsanɪdʒedekotɪatɪlenɪwolinɪnu?asɪdubainnɪedʒedekanɪwolinɪ?anɪworrɪɡalana?ordanɪtinɪbahedʒennanɪmukhatʃʼahaireatonamɪtokomukhamurudʒirudaɡaranɪɪsasukakesabahebɪsanɪkesabueinnɪwanelɪʃanɪdʒedeaboaninɪammamanɪtahadaɡaranɪkuninɪkabi??atɪelɪʃanɪwandʒedenɪdaɡaranɪesabuenamitʃɪfullaɡarsisedʒennanɪelɪʃanɪulemuratebɪsanɪkesabusedaɡarakanɪolbasebɪsanɪɡubademsiseinnɪfudɪdʒennanɪnamitʃɪɡadʒedebɪsanɪɪrafudeɡafatokokaworrɪʃamutifɪkaisraelɪwolɪhaduha??unɪʃamuworraaskartɪɪsatɪmatawoltɪ?ameeɡɪmalawolinɪdatanɪinnɪfullaworrɪkʼubatufohateammoelɪʃanɪkʼonkʼoɡaraha??uisraelɪerɡewandʒedenɪfullasunɪitɪindɪatinɪwontɪakanatifɪworrɪʃ akʼallitʃaetsradʒedanɪkawanseraɡudobekhulafadʒiraɡafanabodira?erusalemuebɪsanɪworralawɪtʃʼahaufafullaworrɪdʒirudufaninɪakaworrɪɡu??adʒilasunɪsirbaɡalatanɪdebɪsanɪbilbɪlafɪkɪrarɪdaesirbusirbɪtunɪworralawɪfullaworrɪdʒirutadatu?erusalemutifɪdatudiranetofathifɪbethɡilɡalifɪɡebafɪasmarethɪkesawoltɪduftekʼalolefɪworrɪlawɪufɪkʼulkʼullesanɪɡumifɪfulofɪnabodɪralekʼulkʼullesanɪdʒennanɪaninɪdʒarole?udanabosunɪɡubatɪwoltɪ?ameɡumɪɡudomummeɪnkʼamnetafullalama?atedirasuninɪmartesɪrbiteɡalatawakʼadebiftumatatoltʃeɡuminɪkʼaramirɡakʼadʒeltenaboɡubaɡarafullohura?atehoʃa?anɪworradubademedʒarolenɪ?udahaɡɪtokoisaɡula?atedʒarɪkʼalolekaworrasunɪɡula?aemaɡalatadaekanaatsariaetsrameʃulamu?udabendʒaminɪʃema?a?eremianamɪworratɪanutsekariailma?onathanɪkailmaʃema?aʃema?anɪkamataniamatanɪanɪkamika?amika?anɪkatsakurɪtsakurinɪkaasafuɪsaleworrabalbalaɪsatɪitɪanaʃema?aatsarelɪmilalaɪɡilalaɪmaɪnethanelɪ?udahananɪworrɪkuninɪtʃʼahauftɪmihasirbakamihadurɪha??udaudinɪnamitʃɪwakʼakanɪfakatunɪsirbanamitʃaetsradʒedanɪkawanserabekhukanitɪɡumɪtanadurademaworrɪfullomadoɡahedʒennanɪfanodiradaudɪtinɪsenanɪolkoremanadaudɪbiradabreɡamadirakailaborutinɪnabofullafullobisanɪtinɪdebieɡuminɪtanɪdɪbinɪtasirbaɡalatasɪrbutɪbitakʼadʒeltenaboɡuba?ateanɪlenɪbɪ??ahaɡaɡarɪwolinɪfanaworradufenudofɪɪbidadabarrenaboballonɪbaneartileitɪdabannefulloefraimutifɪfullo?eʃanatifɪtakʼurtumɪtifɪdofɪhananelɪtifɪdofɪdibatokodʒedanifɪfulloholɪ?eledabarredatufullomanawakʼaɡennanɪ?asumakennalakimneakananɪɡuminɪɡalatawakʼadebiftutanɪlamanɪfullamanawakʼatinɪbatedʒarolenawolinɪdʒirtumalelekʼalolenɪmaɡalatadoftutunɪlenɪnawolinɪdʒirtɪelɪakimumase?ami?aminɪmika?aelɪoenaɪtsekariahananiaammallemase?aʃema?aeleatsarɪutsɪ?ehihananɪmalkiaelemuetserɪsirbɪtunɪta?etsrahɪ?anɪitɪmatalalabdesɪrbiteɡu??asunɪsoriohedukʼalanɪbi??itɪlenɪɡudoɡammadewanwakʼɪworraɡammatʃɪsefɪnadenifɪidʒollelenɪɡammadelalabdesɪrbitekʼonkʼoworrafaɡoledaɡa?anɪɡafasɪfullawanmanawakʼatɪbasanɪitɪolka?anɪkʼodawakʼabasanɪtananɪmɪdanɪobrutifɪmɪdanɪmukhakakʼarabɪltʃatakaɡannatʃʼahaufawakʼabasanɪ u??aakanakanadʒedanɪha??itɪsitoltʃanɪennutɪbekhaestanɪkʼonkʼomordekaɪdaɡennanɪkʼonkʼodebiftewandʒetebenɪ?ahudɪdiraʃuʃanɪkesadʒirtutʃʼahaufawoltɪ?amɪmarotɪ??adʒedaɡu??asadɪhalkanɪɡu??aleɲataduɡatɪlakisaufɪaɡabsawakʼanakadadaanafɪhodʒatunɪti??alenɪakasumatanaeɡɪsunɪatoserɪnadoweleɡaraha??udakʼa?otanadʒededuehatatutɪdubamordekainɪkaedemewanestanɪdʒetenɪtʃʼahaufatoltʃeɡu??asadesoestanɪwo?aha??itɪke?atedemtebalbalaha??ukesafulabartʃumaha??utɪdefateedʒiteha??itʃɪfulaɪsabalbalatɪdefatebartʃumaufiiramanasunɪkesataha??itʃɪestaalaedʒituarɡedʒennanɪɡammadeuleɪsataworkʼɪɪsiolkʼabeɪsinɪdufteuletanɪfitekʼubanɪtuteha??itʃɪwandʒedenɪmanɪha??itɪestamanɪfetaatolafaaninɪfiduɡamatokofeteleaninɪsikennaestanɪwandʒetenɪwontɪanɪfedu?ositatesifɪhamanɪɡalɡalakanamanakɪ??awolinɪkotasaɡaleɲadadubaha??unɪwandʒedehamanɪhurrisaɡadɪ?amaakawanestanɪfetutoltʃinudʒennanɪha??ufɪhamaninɪsaɡaleestanɪmidasiteɲatʃudakʼanɪatodadɪduɡudʒɪranuha??unɪwanestanɪdʒedeatinɪmanɪfedatamanɪsitoltʃaatolafaaninɪfiduɡamatokotatelesikennaestanɪwandʒetewontɪanɪfedutaanɪkadadutana?oatinɪnaduɡefateeha??itʃaammalle?ositateborilehamanɪwolinɪmanakɪ??akotasaɡaleɲadahodʒdʒasunɪwanfedusitɪhɪmadahamaninɪkaɡammatʃuɪndʒirrekaeworrabɪrademeammoakamordekainɪkafulloworraha??utinɪsenanɪketauolkaeɪsasalfatʃudidearɡedʒennanɪakadʒabaɪsatɪdallaneammoufɪdoweɡaledʒallowanɪisatifɪnitɪɪsatatsereʃɪdʒedanɪ?ameufɪdadewandʒededuresaakakɪ??alafatanakesatɪinɡartanɪɪlmanɪtɪ??aheduha??unɪ?aɡudinnanadarehodʒatuɪsatanatʃʼahaufairanadabarseammalleinnɪwandʒedesunɪmaleleha??itɪestanɪnamadibɪlakiftenafɪha??utʃʼahaallasaɡale?amteborile?anu?amteammowontɪkuninɪmalnabatɪhaɡaaninɪ?ahuditʃɪmordekaɪdʒedanɪkanɪkafulloha??ukesatauarɡudʒennanɪnitɪɪsatsereʃifɪdʒallowanɪɪsawandʒetenɪmukhadederalamakaderinnɪdundumaʃantamaoldabɪmukhadibɪiradaɡaltʃɪborɪdɪramaha??unɪmordekaɪtururaka?ɪɪratɪfannisɪdʒedinɪdubaha??uwolinɪsaɡalesunɪɡammadanɪɲatʃudakʼɪdubinɪtuninɪhamanɪkʼufsiteakumadʒarɪsunɪdʒedenɪtoltʃemukhasunɪoldabanɪhalkanɪsunɪha??unɪrafudadabedubanama?amewandʒedekɪtabalafatɪ??ataoduwandurɪlafakesatɪtaheitɪtafanɪkotanɪnasomadubadufaninɪsomanifɪfullasomanɪsunɪkesatɪakamordekainɪdurɪdʒarasanɡotalamanɪkanɪkafulloha??itʃaeɡuha??uahasueroɪdʒetʃamalatedʒennanɪinnɪhimearɡanɪdʒarɪlamanɪsunɪbiɡthanafɪtereʃɪha??itʃɪnuɡudɪnnafɪ?okhanɪulfinnaakamɪmordekaɪmarowankanatɪdʒennekenninedʒedeɡafatedʒennanɪhodʒatunɪha??utahodʒdʒasunɪatʃɪdʒirtuwomatokoleinkennɪnefɪdʒetedʒennanɪha??unɪwandʒededʒarɪhodʒatutɪ??aɡuɡurdanɪnamɪtokolenɪentuarmadʒiradubahamaninɪ?osunɪtʃʼahaɪtʃanɪbahewontɪinnɪdufefɪakamordekaɪmukhamidasanifɪkanɪɪratɪfannɪsanɪkadatudʒennanɪhodʒatunɪwanha??unɪdʒetehamaninɪtʃʼahaɪtʃaedʒesiarɡufedaha??unɪwandʒedehaolsenudubahamaninɪolsennanɪha??itʃɪwandʒedenɪnamatokotɪdʒirakaakaaninɪulfeseɡudinnakennufɪfedunamakanamanɪtoltʃufɪmalehamaninɪɡaraufikesatɪhereɡewandʒedeenunamɪha??itʃɪulfinnakennufɪfedu?onatatemaledubainnɪwanha??ɪtʃanɪdʒedewo?aha??unɪke?atunɪkotanamakanau?isaammallefardaha??unɪ?abatunɪkotarufalematatɪmaradubahodʒatutantekesanamatʃʼahaufairadʒirutokobarbadɪakainnɪwo?afudenamasunɪu?isefarda?abatʃisedirakesanɪdemelalabewandʒedulalawanha??unɪnamaulfinnakennufɪfedutoltʃudʒennanɪha??itʃɪwanhamaninɪdʒedekaɪhurrisɪwo?afɪfardafudɪmordekaɪkaɡosa?ahudɪkanɪakumadʒetukanatoltʃifɪwanatinɪmakʼadoftetokoleillakɪsinɪtoltʃɪɡutifɪinnɪafanɪfullotanataatʃitɪisaaɡartadʒennanɪhamaninɪwo?afɪfardafudewo?atanɪmordekaɪu?ɪsefɪisafardairakaedirakesanɪdemelalabewandʒedelalawanha??unɪnamaulfinnakennufɪfedutoltʃumordekainɪfullafullomanaha??utɪdebieammohamaninɪkatʃʼahaerɪɪdʒesewo?amatatɪhaɡoɡatearɪfateɡaleinnɪnitɪɪsatsereʃifɪdʒallowanɪɪsatanɪwantahetʃʼahaufaitɪhimedʒennanɪnɪtifɪdʒallowanɪɪsakʼakʼaronɪtanɪwandʒetenɪmordekainɪ?aɡudinnasiraarɡateinnɪɡosa?ahudɪdandeteɪsanɪimorkituinnɪsɪumadabsataatoworrɪtaewankanahasauworrɪsanɡotɪkanɪarɪfatedufehamanɪfudanɪmanaestasaɡaleitɪ?amanɪtanitɪɡesanɪakananɪha??ɪtʃafɪhamaninɪmarolamesosaɡaleestawolinɪɲatʃudakʼanɪatodadɪduɡanuha??itʃɪwanha??ɪtinɪdʒedeatinɪmanɪfetamanɪsitoltʃaatolafaaninɪfiduɡamatokofetelesɪumakennadʒennanɪha??ɪtinɪestanɪwandʒete?onaduɡefateeha??itʃaammalle?ositatelubunabasɪɡosati??aledʒɪresɪanafɪɡosati??ale?akʼalmaɡurɡuranɪatosilaakatissetʃʼahaallanutoltʃanɪaninɪafanɪkʼabadaammowannukʼakʼalanɪnuhobasanifɪammadubadadʒennanɪha??unɪahasueronɪwanha??ɪtinɪdʒedeenunamɪwanakanakanatoltʃufeduinnɪmetɪestanɪwandʒetenamitʃɪnuɡarɡaltʃeɲapanutɪtahewonɪdabditʃahamanɪdʒedanɪkanadʒennanɪhamaninɪmudamelubunɪduftewantahudabeworramimɪlateha??itʃɪdallanemanakesaɡabaheobruɪsaseneammohamaninɪmanakesatɪhafeakalububasanɪha??itɪestakadatuwontɪakanatifɪakaha??unɪitɪdallanewanhamtuisatoltʃufedu?aarɡeinnɪsireestanɪiratetuɪratɪdʒiɡeakabahisaɪsikadatuammoha??itʃɪatoinnɪsɪrumairatʃʼahaisuobrukesaɡadebiearɡeɪ??ewandʒedenamɪkuninɪatoaninɪbiraedʒumanakɪ??akesatɪnitɪtɪ??aɪrrenɪbufataatoha??unɪdubumatanaafanɪkʼabuworrɪsasanɡanɪkanɪdufehamanɪwo?afulatɪhaɡoɡeworrasunɪkesanamɪtokokaharbonadʒedanɪwanha??unɪdʒedesunɪlakisɪbetahamaninɪ?a?umukhadundumaʃantamakamordekaɪkalubutebaseɪratɪfannɪsanɪmɪdasemukhɪsunɪammadatumanaɪsaedʒaha??itʃɪwandʒedeɪsumamukhasunɪɪratɪfannisadubahamanɪmukhainnɪufiftukʼaramordekaɪdʒedemɪdasekanɪɪratɪfannɪsanɪdʒennanɪha??itʃɪdallansuɡalfateɡu??asunɪha??itʃɪahasueronɪwanhamaninɪɲapa?ahudɪkʼabutʃʼahaufaha??itɪestakenneestanɪakamordekainɪfitaɪsiha??ɪtʃatɪhimtetanaɡulamordekainɪfullaha??itʃadufeha??itʃɪkʼubeɪsatabesisatainnɪhamanɪɪrafudeufɪrabasemordekaitɪkenneestalenɪmanafɪwanhamaninɪkʼabutʃʼahaufaharkaɪsatɪkennitedʒennanɪestanɪammalleha??usarbatɪdʒidebotekadatewandʒetemalahamakahamaninɪkaɡosaaɡaɡɪ?ahuditɪmalateballesɪhankʼisɪha??itʃɪuleworkʼɪestaolkʼabedubaestanɪkateha??uduraedʒitewandʒetenɪ?ositate?onaduɡefateammalle?owontɪkuninɪduɡasifakateseraɡabasɪakadubɪhamaninɪkʼaradʒedetanɪtahudowartudubinɪsunɪtatabeilmɪhamedathakaɡosaaɡaɡɪtafeta?ahudɪlafaha??unɪfidutʃʼahaufakesadʒirtufitadʒetuaninɪakamɪdandaebadɪɡosatɪ??aballesanɪobsa?okhanɪaninɪakamɪdandaeakafitatɪ??aballesanɪhobasanɪobsadʒennanɪha??unɪahasueronɪha??itɪestafɪmordekaɪkaɡosa?ahudɪwandʒedenɪɪlalaaninɪ?a?uwanhamaninɪɡosa?ahuditɪmalatefɪisafanniseam hodʒatudʒallabatananɪmakalatananɪsodamordekaitɪdʒedanɪ?ahudɪkʼarkʼaranɪwontɪakanatifɪlafaha??unɪfidutʃʼahaufakesaakamordekainɪdʒabateɡurrabafatenamatʃʼahaufairaɡudinnaarɡateakadansabekhanɪduba?ahudinɪwanfetetʃʼahaufaɲapaufitoltʃiteʃeftinɪhateballesitefitediraɡudaʃuʃanɪtʃʼahaallakesatɪ?ahudinɪnamadibaʃanɪfiteworrafɪtanɪsunɪkesaɪlmanɪdiratahamanɪilmahamedathakaɲapa?ahudɪkudanitɪdʒiramakʼanɪɪlmanɪsunɪkanaparʃandathadalfonɪaspathaporathaadaliaarɪdathaparmaʃtaarɪsaɪarɪdaɪwaɪtsathaammohatatumihaworratokoleɪnsamneɡa??umasunɪnamadirasusakesatɪfɪtanɪhaɡaɪsaha??utɪhɪmanɪdʒennanɪinnɪwanha??itɪestanɪdʒede?ahudinɪdirasusatʃʼahaallakesatɪnamɪdibaʃanɪfiteɪlmanɪdirakudannanɪhamanɪtinɪwoltɪ?oatinɪsetuworɪardakanɪdibɪkesatɪwantoltʃeammamanfetawanfetuinarɡatawandibɪfetunatɪhimɪinarɡataestanɪwandʒetenɪeha??itʃa?ositate?ahudinɪdirasusakesadʒirtuhaborilewanarratɪltʃitekanatoltʃituammallerefaɪlmanɪhamanɪkudannanillemukhaɪratɪfannisadʒededʒennanɪha??itʃɪwankanatʃʼahaufatoltʃadʒededubɪsunɪdirasusakesatɪlalabanɪrefaɪlmanɪhamanɪkudannanɪnamatʃʼahaufaduratɪfafannɪsanɪɡu??akudanɪafresokadʒiaadarɪdʒedanɪ?ahudinɪdirasusawoltɪbateammallenamadibasadɪkadirasunɪfiteammohatatuwantokoleɪnsamne?ahudinɪlafadibɪha??unɪfidukesadʒirtuwoltɪbateɲapaufɪradowartedabsatenamakumatorbatamɪʃanɪkaworradʒibefiteammohatatutɪmihaworratokoleɪnsamneɡu??anɪsunɪɡu??akudanɪsadesokadʒiaadarɪborɪ??aɡu??akudanɪafresohafurabafatanɪwoltɪbahanɪɡammadanɪdʒilatolfatanɪammo?ahudinɪdiraʃuʃanɪkesadʒirtuɡu??akudanɪsadesotifɪkudanɪafresohadisaɲapatɪwoltɪbateɡu??akudanɪʃanesohafurabafateɡammadanɪdʒilatolfatetanafɪ?ahudinɪdiradɪdikʼakesatetuɡu??akudanɪafresokadʒiaadarɪdʒedanɪkʼabatedʒilatolfateɡu??awoɲatanɪsaɡalewolɪkennanɪtolfatɪmordekainɪdubɪtanatʃʼahaufatafsisetatabeɡara?ahudɪlafaha??unɪfidutʃʼahaufakesatafaɡofɪdiodʒirtuletɪerɡewandʒededʒiaadardarɪɡu??akudanɪafresotifɪkakudanɪʃanesolekʼabadaɡannatʃʼahaufakesaolumatolfadaɡu??anɪlamanɪsunɪɡu??a?ahudinɪɲapaufɪdabsatehobaftedʒisuninɪkʼaradʒialalalatifɪufɪdʒɪbataammoeɡeɡaraɡaledʒiaɡammadati ɪlmanɪɪsatʃʼahaufakʼulkʼullesusoriokʼalawontɪinnɪakasɪtoltʃufɪwanɪlmanɪɪsaheɡerɪɡarakesatɪwakʼaabartufasehesodataabowakʼɪwanʃetananɪdʒedeɪsiaboatinɪesadufteʃetanɪwandʒedenɪaninɪlafumatanakesaolɪɡadɪmaraatomaruarmanɪbaheabowakʼɪwandʒedenɪatinɪakahodʒatunɪtɪ??aa?ubunɪnamaduɡakʼadʒelawakʼasodatewanhamtulaɡatuaɡartelafakesanamɪakaisaɪndʒiruatinɪɪsafɪworraisatifɪwaninnɪkʼabutʃʼahaufadʒabesiteintɪssineatinɪhudʒɪharkaɪsatʃʼahaufaebiftehorɪɪsalafairaindabarsineammo?oatinɪwaninnɪkʼabutʃʼahaufaharkaketinɪɪrafutemalaketɪinnɪsiinabarudubaabowakʼɪwanʃetananɪdʒede?osɪaninɪammaisasitɪlakisawanɪsatʃʼahaufawanfetutoltʃɪammonafaɪsahankʼadɪdʒennanɪʃetanɪkaeabowakʼabɪrademeɡu??atokokaɪlmanɪa?ubudʒilatolfatemanaobolesaɪsanɪɡudakesatɪtetesaɡalesoratedadɪdudunamɪtokokʼonkʼonɪa?ubutɪdufewandʒedeatonutenneobrukʼonnukaharrelenɪtennanudatudeduworrɪɡosasebadufetassanuhadehorɪnurafudateanamalehodʒatutantetʃʼahaufafitenamɪfiɡekaodunɪsidufeanumatʃʼahaallaatoinnɪtaedubatunamɪdɪbinɪkʼonkʼonɪdufewandʒedekʼawenɪwakʼa?arefɪnamaisɪtɪssuletʃʼahaufairabutehobaftenamɪfiɡekaodusuninɪsidufeanumatʃʼahaallaatoinnɪtaedubatunamɪdɪbinɪkʼonkʼonɪdufewandʒedeworrɪɡosakalda?okadulɪworrafullasadɪ?audufenuhadeɡalatʃʼahaufafudateanamalehodʒatutantetʃʼahaufafitenamɪfiɡekaodunɪsidufeanumatʃʼahaallaatoinnɪtaedubatunamɪdɪbinɪkʼonkʼonɪdufewandʒedeatoɪlmanɪtantetetemanaobolesaɪsanɪɡudakesatɪdʒilatolfatesaɡalesoratedadɪdudububenɪdʒabdunɪtokolafaalotɪduftemanasunɪɡamatʃʼahaufadofteɪlmanɪsunɪɪratɪkʼariftehobaftenamɪfiɡekaodunɪsidufeanumatʃʼahaalladʒennanɪa?ubunɪakamalelalefatewo?aufitarsasematahadatelafanɪufɪdaewandʒedeaninɪkʼullumadaladeɡafadullekʼullumaduawankanaleabumawakʼatɪnakenneammalleisumatɪfudatemakʼaɪsahafarsanɪatowontɪkuninɪtʃʼahauftɪɪsatɪduftelea?ubunɪwakʼahalateɪsatɪintʃubamneɡu??anɪmalaɪkanɪabowakʼaduratɪmullatuammalleɡennanɪʃetanɪlenɪworrawolinɪdufeabowakʼɪwanʃetananɪdʒedeisɪaboatinɪesadufteʃetanɪwandʒedenɪaninɪlafumatanakesaolɡadɪmaraatomaruarmanɪbaheabowakʼɪwandʒedenɪatinɪakahodʒatunɪtɪ??aa?ubunɪnamaduɡakʼadʒelawakʼasodatewanhamtulaɡatuaɡartelafakesanamɪakaisaɪndʒiruatoatinɪnasobatekainnɪwomaintahinɪakanumatɪitɪnakafteleinnɪakumakanɪnadʒalatenasalfatadʒennanɪʃetanɪwandʒedenɪnamɪwankʼabutʃʼahaufalubunɪbɪtataatinɪakasɪbetaammo?oatinɪammanafaɪsatuteinnɪfulumakeduraedʒesiabaradubaabowakʼɪwanʃetananɪdʒede?osɪaninɪammaisasitɪlakisaammolabutʃʼahaallakesaimbasinɪdʒennanɪʃetanɪkaeabowakʼabɪrademenafaa?ubumamadanɪkʼabatehaɡumaɡanafanatɪfudeɡubematatɪdabea?ubunɪtʃʼahaatʃabaokotefarafudefulladaraitɪharanɪtaemadanɪhokʼatenɪdʒennanɪnɪtinɪɪsawandʒetenɪatinɪakumakanɪwakʼadʒalateɪsasalfataɪsaabartedotehoa?ubunɪwandʒedenɪatinɪakanadenɪwomaɪmbennedubatanudansumatʃʼahaallawakʼaɪraeɡannahamennaleineɡannuɡarɡalakanatʃʼahaufakesaa?ubunɪtakawomadubatewakʼainhalannedʒalanɪa?ubusadenɪelɪfatsɪkaworratemanɪtifɪbɪldadɪkalafaʃuhɪtifɪsofarinɪkalafanamathɪakainnɪɡarɡaledaɡennanɪwolɪɡalanɪwaninnɪkesadʒiruɡafatʃudakʼanɪatofullaɪsainɡahinɪfaɡotuarɡanɪfulawollalanɪdubaeɡeisahubannanɪlalefatanɪakamalebohanɪwo?atatarsasanɪbɪ??ematatɪufɪnakʼanɪdʒennanɪhalkanɪtorbafɪɡu??atorbaɪsawolinɪlafatatanɪɡarɡalaisaɡudakanaarɡanɪɪralalefatanɪafanɪkʼabatanɪufumatʃʼahaɪsanɪwandʒedeɡu??anɪaninɪdaladehabadutɪhalkanɪɡurbanɪ?adalatedʒedanɪlenɪhabadanitɪɡu??anɪsunɪhadukanatahutɪwakʼɪɡubaɡu??asunɪdebieinkʼabatinɪɪfsanɪdebieitɪinɪfsinɪɡu??anɪsuninɪhaɡandɪdaedukanautɪdumansɪhairataheadudossedukanesutɪhalkanɪsunɪhadukantɪlikʼɪmsɪtutɪhabultɪwoɡatifɪtadʒɪaletʃʼahaufakesakutanitɪhalkanɪsunɪhaduwatanitɪkʼonkʼoɡammadakesatɪindaɡa?inɪworrɪɡu??aabarukaɡordʒamakasuhaɡu??asunɪabarutɪbakaltʃɪɪsakaɡanamahadukanautɪɡu??asunɪbɪftunɪbatelaftɪinɡu??ainɪwanɡu??anɪsunɪdalotakɪ??aoltʃeilatɪ??aɡarɡalaarɡuindowɪnifɪaninɪmafɪakumadaladenɪinduinɪ?okhanɪmafɪɡarahadatɪ??akesabahuindɪdinɪhatɪtɪ??amafɪufiranatesifteɪsinɪmafɪharmanahosifteatoɡafasɪdueammasila?ahafurabafadeaninɪsila?a?uakaha??otafɪdʒaroledurɪtamanaha??ukaammabadeonatahekanadʒarterafeaninɪsilakʼalolemanaufiworkʼifɪkʼarsinɪɡuteufiraraftefakada?okhanɪdaimaɡaratɪduekawomatokolekʼubaɪnkʼamnefakadaawalakesatɪnamɪhamanɪɡarɡaladurabahenamɪdadabɪkʼabuhafurabafataatʃɪkesatɪworrɪhɪdansakesadʒirulenɪɡammadei??ananamaworrahodʒatʃisudʒalabahaatʃɪkesanamɪdɪkʼafɪɡudalenɪfullumatakatatisselenɪatʃitɪbaltʃumaarɡatɪnamaufiftuɡarɡalakesadʒirumafɪdemaninɪnamadipudesadʒirumafɪifsaitɪkennanɪbesebɪ??ekesaolke?atanɪiraawalakʼotanɪbarbadanɪworrɪhaɡadueawalanitɪinɡammaduwakʼɪmafɪnamakaranɪitɪhɪdamelaftɪitɪdufatedʒɪrennakennafɪfullasilawoɲadutaebohahodʒdʒatʃʼahaufawadeimɪmanɪnakesa?anɪwontɪaninɪsodadunadakʼabdetaaninɪdedulenɪnatɪdufteaninɪnaɡa?aɪnkʼabuhafuraimbafaduɡarɡalɪkɪ??aindumatudʒennanɪelɪfatsinɪkaworratemanɪwandʒedeabo?onamɪsinɪdubateindallantaaninɪammadandaeintʃallisumeɪlalɪatinɪnamahedubarsiftenamalalafaledʒabesitedubinɪtantenamaɡufatekibdenamalafedʒabesiteammaɡarɡalɪsikʼabannanɪobsudadabdeinnɪsitɪdufnanɪirahafudadabdeatinɪkʼarawakʼasodatetʃʼahaubulaɡatetanafɪsilaakanateteɡarahamatʃuhɪmmallenamɪduɡatakaɡarɡala?aarɡatemehereɡɪnamakʼadʒelataka?aidʒesanɪnamɪtʃʼahaubukʼotehamennafatʃasuwomasunɪmurataworrahafurawakʼatinɪballesanɪdallansuisatinɪworrafɪtanɪtʃʼahaubitʃɪakaɲentʃaɪtanedanɡadaammowakʼɪtʃʼahaallɪsiseɪlkanɪtʃʼahaatʃabsaakumaɲentʃawanɪdʒeseɲatuɪnkʼamnehobanɪɪlmanɪɪsanɪfirfɪrfamtɪdurɪkʼonkʼonɪlatodufteɡurrɪkɪ??ahasasadaɡa?ehɪribanadowarteaninɪakamalemudameholadelafelenɪnatʃotʃotekʼɪllensɪfulairanabaherɪfensɪmatakɪ??aʃɪlkaeolkakaeaninɪwanatʃɪedʒaarɡemɪlladehubatʃudadabelaftɪtʃʼahaakʼalɪdʒetedʒennanɪkʼonkʼodaɡa?ekʼonkʼonɪsuninɪwandʒetenamɪdandaewakʼaduratɪnamaduɡataha?okhanɪdandaenamaisaumeduratɪkʼulkʼullotahawakʼɪhodʒatuɪsainduɡefatumalaikaɪsalewollalaitɪmuramalaketɪwaninnɪnamadokʼeɪramidasanɪkadandanɪakabɪllatʃatʃʼahaarasanɪduɡefatusetanamumadɪramalubukʼabutɪkanamɪkʼubaɪnkʼamnesafatʃʼahaitʃawaninnɪkʼabutʃʼahaufaisaɪrafudanɪatoinnɪkʼalbɪinarɡannetʃʼahaitʃa?ofetu?amɪammoenutɪsɪdʒalaowatamalaɪkanɪatinɪkʼarkʼarsaɪraarɡatudʒirtɪlalefatʃanɪdalleɪdʒeftɪdɪbinɪsirɡoballesitɪaninɪdallekʼutumadansakʼabduarɡɪnanɪmarotokotuisaabareɪlmanɪɪsamarotokotukʼarkʼarsadabdeɡadisadubitɪnamaworradubatudabanɪnamɪbelakʼabumɪdanɪdalleɲatamɪdanɪkʼoratɪkesatɪbahelenamɪdebukʼabulenɪhorifɪisadibɪfatahamennɪbɪ??ekesaɪndufuɡarɡalɪlenɪlafakesaɪmbahuakumakʼankʼenɪtʃʼahaetʃetunamɪlenɪɡarɡalatɪdalata?osilaaninɪsitateaninɪwakʼa?amadeɡarɡalakɪ??aitɪhɪmadainnɪwandʒabdumamakanamɪdandaeinhubannetoltʃainnɪboka?anamarobeobrunamadʒisakanamairreɪnkʼamneolfudenamabohuɡammatʃisuwakʼumainnɪmalamaltitʃaballesaakaharkɪɪsawomainarɡannehereɡaworraledanfaworrasunɪɡu??anɪdukantɪirabuteɡu??aɡudanɪakanamahalkanɪdemudʒondʒanɪammowakʼɪhi??esaduakesabaseharkanamaworradabsulekesabasaakananɪhi??esɪabdɪarɡatetʃʼahaubɪtʃaleafanɪkʼabatʃɪsanɪ?owakʼɪɡudanɪsikʼadʒeltʃuintufatinɪinnɪwositoltʃeharkumaufɪtinɪsifa??isainnɪmaroheduɡarɡalakesasibasedubadebieɡarɡalɪsiinkʼabatu?oolanɪbuteinnɪdusidoweɡu??aworanalelubusibasainnɪnamasiarabsusiradowehodʒdʒabadinɪduftudurasibasaatinɪ?oworanafɪbeltɪduftuinkofaltabɪnensaalaleinsodatuobrunɪatinɪkʼotatulenɪdakhaɪnkʼabdubɪnensɪalallenɪdebiesiɪnhaduɡafasɪatinɪnaɡa?umanɪmanaketitɪɡalta?oretantetoatuletokolekesaɪndabduhaɡumabu?onɪɡetuɪlmanɪtetɪlenɪlafairadabartehaɡasɪɡetɪakumadarɡa?enɪbatefullaɡetebillatʃatuatɪnɪlenɪdʒartefullaɡetedotanudʒarolewankanaɡannahedutenetɪbarannedubinɪtennaduɡafudadɪdʒennanɪa?ubunɪwandʒedehodʒdʒasiladɪpufɪɡarɡalakɪ??abɪmanɪɪsinɪmansaɡalanaletʃʼahaufairaulfatɪtanafɪdubinɪakanumatɪnakesa?atutuninɪɪsanɪimamsɪsinɪwakʼɪɡudanɪ?atɪ?aufɪtinɪnaworanehadanɪɪsi?anafatʃʼahaufanakʼabatewakʼɪ?awannamamudamsisafulanatɪdebiseharrenɪdida?obu?okʼuftuimbarodɪkʼotɪ?onɪ?ookha?akʼabduimarratɪammoenutɪdandaesaɡalesodaɪnkʼamnesorataenutɪdandaeotaokhokanɪmiefateɲataaninɪsaɡaleakasɪdandaeinsoradufa??anadowartɪwakʼɪmanifɪwananinɪfedunakennudidainnɪmafɪkadatʃatɪ??aindaɡenneatoinnɪnatʃʼahaaraseɡarɡarɪnatʃʼahaireɡudodansaatosilaakainnɪakasɪtoltʃubekheoltʃetʃeɡammadaatoɡudodukubsatʃudʒiradeleaninɪɪmbekhawakʼɪkʼulkʼulloanɪlenɪtakadubɪisatinɪimorkineaninɪɪrremanɪkʼabatadʒiradunɪkadabuwomatuɪnkʼamneakamɪtaeobsaaninɪdakhanafakɪ??asibɪlanɪmidasanɪɪrrenɪaninɪufinɪbasunakesatɪɪnh ʼamparɪhirbaɪsakʼabeisatʃotʃoudowalafaɪratɪtururadossanɪkʼamparakarakesaka?anifɪɡamatʃʼahaufawanisamudamsɪsutɪisaeɡatefullainnɪdemutʃʼahaufaɡulademainnɪdurɪduresaammoamma?awodabeɡarɡalɪdatutaeisaeɡatadukubɪhamanɪnafaɪsakʼabateharkafɪmilaɪsaʃamseadʒesawaroinnɪnaɡa?anɪkesatahukesahirkɪsanɪboladuatɪɡesanɪammatanaabanɪfeduhawaroɪsatɪɡalutɪeɡɪdilloitɪnakʼanɪkʼulkʼullesaninɪhidɪɪsadʒalatɪɡoɡoɡedamenɪɪsaɡubatɪkʼantʃoratɪɡurrɪɪsalafakesabademakʼaɪsalafakesadabanɪisalafakesabasanɪifsakesadukanatɪɡesanɪinnɪɡosaɪsakesaɪlmanɪɪnkʼabunamɪɪsakahafeɪndʒirunamɪilaborutifɪkailaadutʃʼahauftɪbadɪɪsadaɡennanɪmudameholatasuninɪbadɪworratʃʼahaubɪtʃatɪworrɪwakʼaɪmbennefullasunɪ?adʒennanɪa?ubunɪwandʒedenɪɪsanɪ?omɪdubɪtesanɪdertutananɪnaɡarɡaltʃulakɪftanɪmarohedunaarabsɪtanɪarabanaarabsɪtanɪɪratʃʼahaerudɪdanɪatoaninɪduɡumawollalatoltʃelemaninɪɪsanɪɡarɡaltʃaɪsanɪwannaradʒɪrtanɪsetanɪmaroaninɪɡarɡalaarɡadefɪtʃʼahaubitʃanasetanɪɪsanɪakanamɪwankananatoltʃewakʼainɡartanɪinnɪ?atururanahideakanakʼabu?oaninɪ?anadabsanɪdʒedei??elenamɪnadʒalakʼabuɪndʒiruatoaninɪkʼarkʼarsakadadeleduɡainarɡaduwakʼɪ?a?ukaranatɪhideaninɪdandaeɪndabruinnɪ?akarakɪ??adukanakesatɪdosseinnɪhorɪkɪ??atʃʼahaufanarafudeɡurraki??aleballeseinnɪɡamatʃʼahaufanadaenatʃʼahaatʃabseinnɪabdɪtɪ??aakamukhabukʼiselafatɪnalakisewakʼɪakahamtuɡuɡubatenatɪdallaneɲapaufitɪnahereɡeinnɪdulaufihadisanatɪerɡeworrɪbolakʼotatewarotɪ??amarsainnɪ?a?uobole?anɪtɪ??anarafaɡeseworrɪdurɪnabekhu?aɲapanatɪtahefɪtanɪtɪ??a?analakiftedʒalanɪtɪ??a?anabɪra?atekessumanɪtɪ??a?anadetedubritɪnahodʒatuakakessumafɪɲapanaheredɪhodʒatunɪtɪ??aatoaninɪ?amelenadʒalainowatuatoaninɪsobadelenadʒalaɪnkʼabdunɪtinɪti??alenɪadʒati??afunatɪindɪatuobole?anɪti??alenɪtanuwolinɪdallannenadʒɪbitenarafaɡatɪidʒollelenɪnaɡo?esite?onaɡartunatufatɪdʒalanɪti??alenɪtaaninɪɡudodʒaladunadʒɪbitɪnamɪaninɪnamatʃʼahaufairadʒaladu?anatɪɡarɡaleaninɪ?a?uɡoɡafɪlafetʃʼahaallataheammohatatulubunɪ?aarmaɡahedʒalanɪtɪ??ananahaharkɪwakʼa?anadaeɪsanɪmafɪakumawakʼɪɲatenafiteɲatanɪnafɪtanɪɪsanɪfonɪkɪ??ainkʼuftanɪatonamɪsiladubɪtɪ??atanakʼabatekɪtabakesatɪtafeaninɪakamɪfeda?okhanɪatoinnɪdubɪtɪ??aakaɪsinɪhaɡadʒirudʒɪrennatetudakhaɪratɪsibɪlanɪkʼoreakamɪdʒaladaaninɪɪmbekhaakanamɪnakaltʃuɡubadʒiruammalleakainnɪɡu??amummedufenadubatuatodukubɪnafakɪ??aballeseleaninɪnafumakananɪwakʼaarɡaanumatɪilati??anɪisaarɡanamadibɪnitɪwanɪsanɪnuakaminɪisaɡarɡaltʃinedʒetanifɪɡaranɪnalafeɪsanɪwannanɪhalatanɪbarbadanɪammoammatanaɡoradesodadawontɪakanatifɪwakʼɪɡafadallaneɡoradenɪnamaballesadubaakasinɪakanamawollalanamatɪmurudʒirubetanɪdʒennanɪsofarinɪkaɡosanamathɪwandʒedenɪaboatinɪ?anadallansiftetanafɪaninɪammahurrisewosinɪdʒetʃufedawontɪatinɪnanɪdʒetearabaammokʼalbinɪtɪ??awansinɪdʒetʃumalanɪ?anaɡarsifteduɡumaatinɪɪmbetahaɡumadurɪnamalafaɪratɪumanɪɡammadɪnamatʃʼahaubitʃaɡababaɡammatʃunɪnamawakʼaimbennelenɪhaɡunitɪatoinnɪderatematanɪwakʼatukʼeleakumaawarabadanamɪdurɪisabekhuinnɪmedʒedeɡafatainnɪakumaobdʒudabreakumada??ahalkanɪbadadebɪanɪinarɡanɪnamɪdurɪɪsaarɡedebieɪnarɡufulladurɪinnɪitɪɡaluleindabanɪɪlmanɪɪsawaninnɪhi??esaɪrahatedebɪsumaltenafɪɪsaɡafainnɪdurɪkaimadʒabennakʼabaammoammadɪotubɪ??etahaatohamennɪɡudoafanɪɪsatɪmɪaeinnɪafanɪkesafudatʃudadabelesaɡalenɪɡaraɪsakesatɪhadoftehadabofaitɪtatɪinnɪhorɪkaradabatinɪsoratedidɪfatewakʼumatɪwansunɪisadidɪsisewontɪtʃʼahaubitʃɪlɪkʼimsehadahadanɪsunɪakumahadabofaisaɪdʒeftɪinnɪdadalafairadabreakaɡalana?aufɪlaɡaananifɪdammɪke?auleɪnarɡuinnɪwanhodʒatearɡateinsoratu?okhanɪtirfɪdaldalaufɪiraarɡateɪɲatuwontɪakanatifɪinnɪhi??esadabsehi??omseammallemananamɪdɪbinɪdʒaratelesameinnɪsabdɪwomaɪnkʼufuammallewomaolɪinke?atuinnɪ?owoɲatuwomainhambisutanafɪhorinɪɪsahobaatoinnɪkʼufuɡarɡalɪisakʼabatebadinɪisadakʼabdɪ?oinnɪhaɡafeduɲatekʼufelewakʼɪakamaleɪsatɪdallanetontomonɪdaelafabusahodʒdʒainnɪworanadurabakʼatʃunɪfedutɪ?asibɪlatɪisaworanati?itɪnafaisakesalitefɪtenɪɪsidiɡaɪsadudeinnɪakahamamudamawaninnɪolke?atetʃʼahaufaballesanɪɪbidɪnamɪharkanɪimbobesinɪɪsafɪworraɪsaletʃʼahaufaɡubaɡubanɪtʃʼahaubuɪsamuliftelaftenɪisahɪmatɪhodʒdʒawakʼɪitɪdallanumanaisatifɪwaninnɪkʼabutʃʼahaufalolanɪballesanɪakɪwakʼɪtʃʼahaubitʃaballesuakasɪsuninɪbadɪwakʼɪtʃʼahaubitʃahereɡedʒennanɪa?ubunɪwandʒedenɪdubɪtɪ??aakadansatʃʼahaakʼasaakɪɪsanɪɡaranadʒabesɪtanɪhahaɡasumatahutɪkʼomnɪaninɪdubadunɪnakennadubaeɡɪaninɪdubadehaɡafetanɪnaɡo?esaaninɪnamadubɪmanɪɪrakʼaba?oaninɪobsubademanɪnarakʼabdanɪnadawadamamaafanɪkʼabadahodʒdʒaaninɪwannatoltʃanɪhereɡuaninɪakamalenaheholadatʃʼahaubitʃɪmanifɪlububuledʒarehorɪhorataworrɪidʒollefɪakhakhowanɪdaleɪlmanɪsunɪtaolɡudatuarɡawakʼɪmanaworraimballesuworrɪsodawomatuɪnkʼabukorominɪworrabaratʃʼahaufaɡobdelonɪworralenɪkainsalesineakadansadalanɪɪlmanɪworraburateakaɪlmoleholatabatɪkirarifɪfulludodoftesɪrbitɪworrɪnaɡa?anɪtaeɡarɡalamaleduefullaekheradakʼaworrɪwanwakʼaɡudanɪdʒedunulakisɪnukarakankebekhuɪmfennuatinɪkʼaramanɪkanusihodʒannu?onusikadannumanɪnubataworrɪwandʒedunuɪrrumatennanɪarɡannaammoaninɪdandaehereɡaworrasunɪeɪndʒeduifsetʃʼahaubitʃataka?adamfanɪworrɪakasɪsuninɪtokolenɪtakaɡarɡala?aarɡatewakʼɪtakaworratʃʼahaubutɪdallaneakabu?okʼɪllensɪfudufude?okhanɪakaawarabubenɪfutu?afudeɪsanɪwandʒetanɪwakʼɪmarowollalaabatifɪɪlmanɪdanaammodubinɪsuninɪakasɪnitɪwakʼɪhanamawollalatoltʃewotoltʃutɪnamɪwollalatoltʃuhaakamarowollalaufitɪɡarɡalaarɡatubekhutɪnamɪwollalatoltʃuhaɡarɡalaufiarɡatedallansuwakʼaɡudaarɡutɪnamɪhodʒdʒaɡu??anɪɪsaɡahewanɪlmanɪɪsai??alanamɪdandaewakʼakaha??otalekʼoruimbarsisanamɪɡarɪatofa??afɪdʒabennakʼabukʼufafɪɡammadakesaduakanafɪɪsaɡabinnakʼabuammohaɡɪtokoɡammadaɪnkʼabuɡarɡalanɪtaeɡarɡalakesaduaammonamɪtʃʼahauftɪakumatakadueawalanɪramonɪɲatɪaninɪhereɡakesanɪkaɪsanɪmalahamanatinɪdatanɪɪmbekhaɪsanɪwandʒetanɪmanɪnamitʃaɡudakanɪmetɪkadurɪhamennatoltʃeɪsanɪidemtunɪwolɪinhasoftanɪɪsanɪoduworrɪdufunɪindaɡenneɡu??awakʼɪnamatɪdallanenamadanunamɪlububasanɪtʃʼahaubitʃatʃʼahaallanamɪtʃʼahaubitʃahɪmatewaninnɪtoltʃeɡulaɡatɪkennufɪɪndʒiruhodʒdʒaawalatɪisaɡesanɪawalaɪsaleakadansaeɡanɪnamɪhedunɪisadurafɪdubale?abi??enɪlafalenɪɪsatɪmɪoftɪammoɪsanɪmafɪdubɪwomakesaindʒɪrrenɪɡaranadʒabesufetanɪdubɪɪsanɪnanɪdʒetanɪtanadaramaleduɡanɪkesaɪndʒirtudʒennanɪ akainnɪnadʒalakʼabubekhufedawakʼɪirreufitʃʼahaufanɪnadidaakasɪnitɪinnɪdubɪtɪ??aintʃakʼasaaninɪnamaduɡatɪdandaewankɪ??awakʼatɪhɪmadainnɪdubɪtɪ??akʼoreduɡanamura?oaninɪbarbadaɪsailaborudemeinnɪatʃɪɪndʒiru?oilaadudemeleatʃitɪɪnarɡuhodʒdʒainnɪmɪrɡafɪbitaletɪwotoltʃeaninɪisadandaeɪnarɡuammowakʼɪedʒatakɪ??atʃʼahaufaɪmbekhahodʒdʒainnɪnaɪlaluaninɪakaworkʼɪkʼulkʼullesanɪitɪfakadafantɪtɪ??aedʒataisaɡulademtɪaninɪkaraisatakairaɪnɡorreaninɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufaseraɪsaɡutefedɪtɪ??alakisetaɪsatoltʃainnɪindʒɪdʒɪramunamɪtokolenɪdandaewaninnɪfeduimorkunɪinnɪwannahereɡeɪnɡutahereɡasunɪmaleleinnɪhereɡahedudibɪkʼabatanafɪaninɪhodʒdʒawankanakʼabaduisaduratɪmudamawakʼɪɡudanɪ?aɡaranalafisenamudamsisenamɪnasodatʃisesuninɪdukananitɪwakʼaatodukantɪilanadowartelewakʼɪɡudanɪmafɪɡu??akʼorsummaintoltʃinɪnamɪisabekhumafɪɡu??asunɪbarbadedabanamɪakalafaufɪballɪfatudakhaseraɡurarebɪ??ahatanɪtaufitɪnakʼatanɪharreleɪlmanɪhi??e?ɪɪrafudatanɪsanɡahadahi??esalekʼabdofudatanɪhi??esaduɡadowanɪnamawomainkʼamnelebakʼatʃɪsanɪtanafɪhi??e?inɪakumaharredidalafaalokesasaɡalebarbadatɪatʃɪmaledandanɪfulladibɪɪlmanɪworratɪsaɡaleinarɡanɪhi??e?inɪobrubɪ??amurteobrutʃʼahaubitʃakesamɪdanɪtsabibuɡurtɪhalkanilewo?amalekʼullabulanɪwandamotʃaɪradowadabanɪbokenɪɡarenitɪrobuworradʒisseworrɪdakhadʒalatɪbakʼateakakʼobatutʃʼahaubitʃɪdaimaabaɪnkʼamnetissetolfateɪlmanɪhi??esakʼabdofudataammohi??e?inɪwo?adabdekʼulla?atekawomaɡaraɪnkʼamnemɪdanɪbɪ??aɡaltʃitɪworrɪmɪdanɪedʒersadadakesabasemɪdanɪtsabɪbuledadɪkesabasakaufiftudebuɪndʒirredirakesatɪnamɪmadakʼabufɪkadudʒiruɪ??ekʼarkʼarsakadataammowakʼɪkadatʃasunɪindaɡa?unamaɡaritɪdʒirakaifsadiduworrɪifsainhubatu?okhanɪɡarainnɪdemuɡulaɪndemuɡanamanamɪwoɪdʒesulafakaehi??esaɪdʒesudakʼahalkanɪdakʼewohatanamɪnadenɪbɪ??adakʼudiaadueɡenamunaɪnarɡudʒededokhateitɪdabatahalkanɪhatunɪmanatʃʼahaabsitɪammoɡu??adokhateifsadidɪworrɪifsaɡu??asodatedukanahalkanɪdʒalataatɪwandʒetunamatʃʼahaubitʃabisanitɪfatʃaefudatalafaɪsale?awakʼɪabareinnɪdebieobruisatatsabibukesainhodʒatuakumawontɪkʼabanoftunɪhodʒdʒaadunɪowitebatuakasumatʃʼahaubitʃɪduelafaɪrabadahatɪisalenɪdebiteisainkʼabaturamonɪisaɲateinnɪakumamukhakʼariebadawontɪisaakasɪtoltʃanifɪwaninnɪnadenɪhi??e?ɪdabsenadenɪwomaindalɪnilenahudɪdefɪwakʼɪirreisatinɪworradʒadʒababallesetʃʼahaubɪtʃalewotoltʃehobasawakʼɪ?ofedenaɡa?anɪisatesiseammohodʒdʒatʃʼahaufaɪlanɪɪsakʼorkʼoratabultɪdikʼotokotʃʼahaubitʃɪwohorataammoeɡeakarafukʼantʃorateakumaɡumabadalakabukʼɪsanɪbadanamɪwankanamormuɪndʒiranamɪdubɪtɪ??atananɪdaradʒeduɪndʒiradʒennanɪbildadinɪkaɡosaʃuhɪwandʒedenɪwakʼɪdʒabennakʼabanamɪtʃʼahauftɪisasodatʃumaleinnɪɡubanaɡa?atoltʃeakadansafidanamɪmalaikaɪsahodʒatuhaɡabekhuɪndʒirafullanɪɪfsanɪwakʼaitɪinɪfsineɪndʒirtɪnamɪakamɪdandaewakʼaduratɪduɡakʼabanamɪuwidaluakamɪdandaekʼulkʼullotahaisaduratɪdʒika??oɪnkʼabuurdʒɪlenɪkʼulkʼullonitɪnamɪmanɪrekaufifturamofɪbukʼatafakatuwakʼaduratɪnamɪmanɪkesadʒiradʒennanɪa?ubunɪwandʒedenɪkʼarkʼarsɪatinɪnamahi??esalafaakakɪ??akanakennitukanaatinɪdalleakakɪ??akanaakanaɡorsitekʼaromakankeɡarsiftaatinɪmalaketɪwannamɪdubɪtantetanatʃʼahaufadaɡa?udʒirusetaenutɪdubɪtanasidubɪsisebɪldadɪekheranɪbɪsanɪlafadʒalakesadʒirtuholatefullanɪekheranɪtetuwakʼaduratɪimbanamtɪwontɪtokolenɪkafullaekherasunɪwakʼadossaɪndʒirtuinnɪɡubaɡamamirɡaballiselafaakanumatɪkawomatɪinfannɪsinɪrarasenamɪdumansabisaninɪdudufesuwakʼainnɪdumansaulfinnabisanɪtinɪtarsaudowainnɪɡobanadumansanɪdossenannobarinɪɡubatɪmɪdaseakasinɪɪfsafɪdukanaɡarɡarɪkʼodeutubanɪɡubatʃotʃoeholatahodʒdʒainnɪmudamsisuɪrrenɪɪsabarinɪdabsatekʼalbinɪɪsaɡordʒamarahabudʒedanɪɡarɡarɪtʃʼahairtehafuraɪsatɪɡordʒamabarinɪkabakʼatuɪdʒeseammotuninɪdʒabennaɪsahaɡumadikʼatokonuɡarsiftɪwontɪɪsakanuindaɡi?inɪɡudotɪhafeenutɪdandaeduɡumadʒabennawakʼahaɡabekhadʒennanɪa?ubunɪammalledubɪfudewandʒedeaninɪmakʼawakʼaɡudadʒirutinɪkakhadakaduɡanadowedʒɪrennanatɪhadesehaɡawakʼɪhafuranakesainfudinɪafanɪkɪ??awanhamtuindubatanɪarabɪki??alenɪhaɡadʒirudaraindubatuaninɪhaɡadʒiruɪsanɪduɡakesadʒɪrtanɪɪndʒeduaninɪhaɡadutɪwollalakʼabaufinɪɪndʒeduaninɪdandaeduɡaɪnkʼabuufinɪɪndʒeduɡaranɪkɪ??aakaaninɪwollalakʼabuɪnarɡ ɡaisawomaɪmbatuinnɪworkʼɪiradʒiradokʼafɪwontɪworkʼinɪmidasanɪlenɪhaɡaisaɪnɡetukʼaromɪdakhaadifɪdakhatʃʼahaulukʼafɪdakhadimatʃʼahaulkɪtʃaleiradʒiradakhahadɪtʃafɪworkʼɪkʼulkʼulloledandanɪkʼaromanɪwolbirainkʼabanɪkʼaromɪesabaharehubatʃanɪesatɪɡaltɪwontɪlubukʼabakadandaekʼaromaarɡaɪndʒirtuwontɪɡubabarɪsalenɪdandeteinarɡitubadifɪdotɪlenɪoduɪsatʃʼahaalladaɡennedʒetɪwakʼatʃʼahaallatɪkaraɪsahubatefullainnɪbahufɪbekhawontɪakanatifɪinnɪmummelafatifɪwanlafaɡubadʒiratʃʼahaufaɪnarɡaɡafawakʼɪbubeirrekennebarɪnilebimemɪdaseɡafainnɪseraboka?aka?ekaramandɪsunɪɡulademtulemɪdaseɡafasɪinnɪkʼaromaarɡeilalatedansumaɪsaarɡekʼufesodanɪwakʼakʼaromatʃʼahaubulakɪsɪtinɪhubatʃadʒennanɪa?ubunɪammalledubɪfudewandʒedeatosilafinnɪkɪ??aakadurɪɡafawakʼɪnakʼorkʼoratukanɪdʒɪrateakamɪdansaɡafasɪwakʼɪnawolinɪdʒirainnɪatoaninɪdukanakesademuifsanakenneɡafasɪɡafaaninɪdʒabennakʼabukawakʼɪdʒalanataheworrakɪ??aebisewakʼɪɡudanɪɡafasɪnawolinɪdʒiraɪlmanɪti??aletʃʼahaufaɡafasɪwolumanɪtennaɡafasɪaninɪananɪkʼufekʼodaworrakɪ??atʃʼahaufaitɪtunɪɡutemukenɪtɪ??ataedʒersalenɪdakhaletʃʼahaufaɡubatɪbatɪ?oaninɪkoradʒarolediradakʼekesataenamɪdɪkʼanɪtʃʼahauftɪolkaenaduraɡoradʒarolelenɪnaulfesiteolɪnakatɪnamɪnamadura?aulenɪtʃʼahaalliseafanɪkʼabatanamɪɡurrakʼabulenɪtʃʼahauftɪakanumatɪtʃʼahaalliseufumatʃʼahaisanamɪnadaɡa?edansumatɪ??adubatenamɪnaarɡelenɪkʼufakɪ??adubate?ohi??esɪnatɪboheaninɪinkʼarkʼareɪlmanɪhi??e?ileɡarɡalakesabasenamɪdudʒirulenɪnaebiseanɪlenɪhadahi??esaleɡammatʃiseaninɪduɡaakawo?au?ɪfadeakasurematatɪmaradeaninɪballailatahenafamilataheaninɪhi??esaabatahenamafulaimbenneletʃʼahaufakʼarkʼareaninɪirrenamanamadabsuballesenamainnɪdabsulebaseaninɪwanɡu??anɪkɪ??aderatenaɡa?anɪworrumakɪ??akesatɪduseheaninɪakamukhahidɪɪsabɪsanɪkʼufedʒirakadamenɪfitesoftunamɪtʃʼahauftɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufadansumatɪ??adubateɡu??anɪtokokaaninɪdʒabennadabeɪndʒiruhodʒdʒaaninɪbɪ??aɡorsebi??itɪtʃʼahaallifteakadansadubɪtɪ??atʃʼahaakʼafte?oaninɪdubɪbufadenamɪdebiedubatuɪndʒirudubinɪtɪ??aakumabokaɪlafasenukʼalbɪnamasentenamɪtʃʼahauftɪdubɪtɪ??adʒalateeɡeakumanamɪobruboka?aɡannaeɡatuɡafaworrɪɡaralafeaninɪworratɪkʼumadeɡaradʒabeseaninɪɡudaworratahekaraworrɪdemufohadeakumaha??unɪdulaufɪtinɪdemuworranɪdemehodʒdʒaworrɪufɪdʒɪbateɡaraworradʒabeseammoammatananamadikʼaharɪ?atɪ??aintahɪnitɪnaɡo?esaaninɪworrasunɪdurɪabotɪworratufadesareretɪ??atissɪtuletɪɪndaruworrɪsuninɪufiftu?ahobaemanɪnabahaworrɪhi??omatebelaehidaɡoɡesahalkanɪlafaalotɪɲatʃufedaworrɪmukhalafaalobubukʼiseɲatehidaɡurbɪkaimɪomnelenamɪtʃʼahauftɪworratɪɪ?eɡusseakumahatuitɪi??anɪɡussanɪworrɪɡodadakha?etifɪboladakha?ekesakʼotanilekesatɪɡalalafaalokesatɪakaharrebarodanɪɡurbɪdʒalatɪwoltɪmamatanetʃʼahaisaworrawomaɪmbennekamakʼaɪnkʼamnelafakesaɡussanɪdubaammaɪlmanɪworrasunɪduftenakofaltɪworrɪwomanaɪnsehutanafɪnaɡo?esaworrɪnatufatenatɪdɪatʃudidehantʃufafulatɪnatufawanwakʼɪnalafiseirrenadowefɪworrɪakamalenatɪdallaneworrɪseseɡɪakanakuninɪnalakisudidenaɡusselafairanaballesufedaworrɪfiɡunadowenaballesufedanamɪnaradowuɪndʒiruworrɪfullatʃʼahaufanɪnatɪbafatenarabuenaballesaaninɪakamalemudameɡurrɪkɪ??aakakʼɪllensabadeduromɪakadumansa?anaradabreaninɪammaladuɡaheɡarɡalɪkɪ??a?anatɪɡudatenalakisudidehalkanɪtʃʼahaufalafenɪnadukubdedukubɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufataenaɲatunarabadudidewakʼɪfitewo?anakʼabewo?atɪ??amɪtʃireakaɪraɡorsedarbedokʼekesanabuseaninɪawarafɪdarataheewakʼaaninɪsi?amadaammoatinɪnadʒaladida?oaninɪsikadaduleatinɪnadʒalaɪnkʼabduatinɪakahamanasumalenadabsitaatinɪɪrretantedʒabdunɪnaɡarɡaltʃitaatinɪbubenatɪerɡiteɪsinɪnabutebubenɪsuninɪnadoftelafanamarsitɪaninɪɪmbekhaatinɪduɪsatɪnaɡesudʒirtafullanamɪtʃʼahauftɪdakʼuatinɪnamabadeufiftutaenasutʃʼahaallakadatumafɪtetehataaninɪdurɪnamaɡarɡalakʼabuwolinɪbohehi??esaɪnnanehodʒdʒaaninɪwandansabarbadewanhamtuarɡadehodʒdʒaaninɪifsaeɡadedukanatɪnatɪdufedɪpufɪhereɡɪ?alafanahobaseɡu??atʃʼahaufaɡarɡalumatɪnatɪdufalaftɪnatɪdukanofteaduarɡudadabeaninɪɡumɪduraedʒekʼarkʼarsakadadawahelɪkɪ??aɡedalafɪɡutʃɪɡoɡanɪkɪ??aɡurataenaralukʼaenafɪlenɪtʃʼahauftɪnakʼandatefulladurɪsirbaɡammadaitɪdaɡauammatanaoannafɪbohadaɡa?aaninɪ?a?ukakhadeakaatodubraarɡeleindaran ʼahauftɪɪntoltɪinnɪdandaekʼorsumawakʼainhubatuinnɪɲapaɪsatʃʼahaufatufateɡo?esainnɪwanufinɪdʒeduwontɪnatʃotʃosaɪndʒirtuaninɪhaɡumadʒiruɡarɡalainarɡadudubɪnamasodatʃɪftutɪkesabahainnɪ?osudubɪtʃʼahaubuhamtudubatainnɪollowanɪkesatɪdokhatenamawomai?akinɪɡadeɪdʒesainnɪnamaufɪindandenneakaɲentʃaɡodakesatɪeɡatainnɪhi??esaɡadetururakesatɪkʼabehɪrkiseɪtinɪdabatanamɪufɪindandennesunɪɡaɡabeufumatʃʼahaisanamahamairrekʼabutɪakasɪisatoltʃetʃʼahaubitʃɪwanufinɪdʒeduwakʼɪwananinɪtahekanai??aluinnɪfuladofatewantahelaludidaeabowakʼakaɪtʃʼahaubitʃaɡarɡaltʃɪtʃʼahaubitʃasunɪɡarɡaltʃɪnamaɡarɡalakʼabukʼabadɪtʃʼahaubitʃɪmafɪwakʼatufatewakʼɪdandaewomanaɪntoltʃuufinɪdʒedaammoatinɪɪnumaaɡartaatinɪɡarɡalafɪlalalaaɡarte?otʃʼahaufakurfodʒirtaakanamakʼarkʼartunamɪkʼarkʼarsaɪnkʼamnesitɪufɪkennaatinɪhaɡumaduritɪdɪpatakʼarkʼarteirretʃʼahaubɪtʃatifɪtadabditʃatʃʼahaatʃabsɪmarohamennaworrɪtoltʃefɪworraɡarɡaltʃɪhaɡaworrɪɪradebɪutɪabowakʼɪha??uhaɡadʒirudʒirennatɪnamɪwakʼadibɪkadatulafaɪsakesabadaeabowakʼaatinɪkadatʃahi??esadaɡeteɡaradʒabesitaatinɪbohanamadabsanɪtifɪtaɪlmanɪhi??e?ɪdaɡetaatinɪworradubateakasinɪnamɪkaufiftuwomaufiɪmbanedebieworraimudamsisuaninɪabowakʼatɪdedaatinɪmafɪdalloftedubɪtanananɪdʒetaakasɪmpirreɡaratɪbarrisɪtʃʼahaubitʃɪ?a?utɪ?afudateɡubeɡuredukanakesatɪnamaduɡakʼadʒelaabirehada?owontɪtʃʼahauftɪhammatenamɪduɡakʼadʒelanɪmanɪtahaabowakʼɪmanaɪsakʼulkʼullokesatabartʃumanɪɪsakaɡudinnaɡubadʒirainnɪilaufɪtinɪnamatʃʼahaufaɪlalewanworrɪtahubekhainnɪnamaduɡakʼadʒelafɪtʃʼahaubɪtʃaleinɪlalaɡaranɪɪsanamawoɪ?akuɡudodʒibainnɪtʃʼahailebobetufɪaraɡubaɡabusetʃʼahaubitʃaɡubatɪrobabubewoɪɡubdunɪworraɡubeballesaabowakʼɪkaduɡatɪinnɪwanduɡakakʼadʒeladʒalatanamɪduɡafɪkʼadʒelumaɡulademuɪsaɪnarɡaeabowakʼanukʼarkʼarɪnamɪsibekhulafakesatɪɪnhamnenamaduɡaɡulademudebɪanɪlafakesatɪinarɡanɪnamɪtʃʼahauftɪwoltɪki??ibedubɪdaratinɪwolsobaarabanamasobukanaabowakʼɪhatʃʼahaallɪsisuafanɪki??ibadubatakataedubɪtennanɪwanfenuarɡannewanfenudubannanamɪdandaenuɪndowudʒedahatʃʼahaufutɪabowakʼɪwandʒeduwanhi??esadabsanɪdipatanɪtaeoufɪa fedutʃʼahaufanakennitawontɪaninɪtahutʃʼahauftɪharkakankekesadʒirtɪwontɪatinɪnakennitetʃʼahauftɪakamɪdadansafinnɪatinɪnafidutʃʼahauftɪɡudomɪdaɡaaninɪabowakʼafarsawaninnɪnaɡorsehalkanilenakʼadʒeltʃufɪwaninnɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufanawolinɪdʒɪrufɪnamɪtokolenɪdandaenaintʃotʃosutanafɪɡaranɪkɪ??aɡammadekʼilɪtamanafɪki??alenɪwomainsodatunamaatinɪdʒalatubolaekheratɪinɡesituatinɪkaradʒɪrennanaɡarsifte?ofullatantedʒiruaninɪɡammadakʼabaatinɪhaɡadʒirudʒɪrennanamatʃesitaeabowakʼanatʃʼahaakʼasɪduɡanaɡaltʃɪakaaninɪtaekʼarkʼarsasitɪbohudaɡa?ɪkadatʃatɪ??ataduɡalenadaɡa?ɪatinɪduɡaɪmbetatanafɪduɡanaɡaltʃitaatinɪɡarakɪ??aɪmbetahalkaninɪnatɪduftenaɪlaltedarahamtutokolenakesadabdeaninɪakanamadibɪwanhamtuindubaduaninɪserakanke?aɡutekaranamahamawoɪballesuɡulaɪndemneaninɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufadandɪtanteɡulademetakaɪraɪnɡoreewakʼawanatinɪnatʃʼahaakʼaftufɪaninɪsi?amatanafɪammadubɪtɪ??adaɡa?ɪɡurraketinɪnatʃʼahaakʼasɪdʒalalatantetaindumannenuɡarsisɪnubasɪ?onufullatantedʒiruatinɪɲapakennaduranubaftaakumaatinɪilatantekʼorkʼoratunukʼorkʼoradɪkolakankedʒalatɪnadossɪworrahamanahaduduranabasɪɲapɪhamanɪ?anamarseworrɪnasuɪnkʼabudubɪkesaɡudoufɪsadaworrɪfullaaninɪdemutʃʼahaufafananadaenaɡadenamarselafanabusufedaworrɪɲentʃafakataɡadenaeɡateɡarɡarɪnatatarsasufedaabowakʼakotɪɲapakɪ??ahadɪballesɪɡoradetetinɪharkatʃʼahaubitʃakesanabasɪnamalafatanakesatɪkʼufudʒalanabasɪɡarɡalaatinɪworraheredenɪworraɡarɡaltʃɪɡarɡalɪsuninɪhaɪlmanɪworratifɪɪlmanɪɪlmanɪworraletʃʼahaufadakʼabutɪammowananinɪtʃʼahaubuintoltʃɪnifɪaninɪsiarɡahodʒdʒaaninɪhirɪbakaesiarɡuaninɪinɡammadaeabowakʼaatinɪirretɪ??aaninɪakamɪsidʒaladaabowakʼɪdakhakɪ??asidadʒabakaaninɪdʒalatɪdokhaduwakʼɪkɪ??asidakɪ??akaaninɪdʒalatɪdeduinnɪwontetɪ??anakʼorkʼoratenabasaaninɪabowakʼa?amadainnɪharkaɲapakɪ??akesanabasaabowakʼahafarsanɪɡarɡalɪduanamarsedotɪakabɪsanɪnatɪfatʃatenalikʼɪmsitehadɪdualubutɪnamarateirresɪlenɪtururaɪsanahideɡarɡalakɪ??akesaaninɪabowakʼa?amadenakʼarkʼarɪdʒedenɪmanaɪsakesainnɪkʼonkʼotɪ??adaɡa?ei??antɪtɪ??aɪsanɪbatedʒennanɪlaftɪholatetʃotʃotewanwakʼɪdallanefɪɡarenile?a?abɪroraetʃotʃoearɪfunnanɪkesa?aeɪbidawoɪɡubeballesufɪtʃʼahaɪlenɪbobetuafanɪkesa?ateinnɪɡubaɡarɡarɪtarsasedumansaɡuratʃamilaufidʒalaka?eɡadɪbueinnɪwankolatinɪɡubabarisedufekolabubeɡubademeinnɪdukanau?ɪfatedumansaboka?atinɪufɪmareboka?adakhanɪrobufɪɪbidɪbibɪlikʼuanɡasuisaduradʒirtukesabahedumansaɡuratʃakesadabredʒennanɪabowakʼɪɡubamandiekʼonkʼowakʼaɡudadaɡa?anɪinnɪtɪ?aufidarbateɲapaɪsaɡarɡarɪfɪrfirseanɡasuisatinɪworraufɪduraɡussebɪsanɪbarinɪfokʼatanɪbi??enɪɡodunɪmullate?a?abɪlafalenɪdɪdatɪbaheɡafaatinɪeabowakʼaɲapakankedallansunɪlolteitɪmanditeabowakʼɪɡadʒedeharkanakʼabedimmubɪsanɪkesanafudeinnɪharkaɲapakɪ??adʒadʒabakesanabasenamanadʒɪbufɪkanarairrekʼabuleɡafaaninɪdibakesadʒiruɲapɪnahadeammoabowakʼɪnaradoweinnɪɡarɡalakesanakʼarkʼarenadʒalatelubunabaseabowakʼɪwananinɪduɡatoltʃufɪnakʼarkʼarewananinɪtʃʼahaubuinkʼamnefɪnaebisaaninɪseraabowakʼa?aɡutetakakaraɪsaɪraɪnɡorreaninɪseraɪsatʃʼahaufa?adʒabeseadaɪsatokoleillakimneaninɪisaduratɪkʼulkʼullowanhamtutʃʼahaufa?aufɪhankʼisedubawananinɪwanduɡatoltʃufɪinnɪnaebisawananinɪisaduratɪtʃʼahaubuinkʼamnenɪeabowakʼaatinɪamantɪnamasiamanuammallenamasitɪintʃubamneatinɪitɪintʃubamtunamakʼulkʼulloatinɪitɪkʼulkʼulloammonamahamaɲapaitɪtatanamaufɪɪnsanebaftenamaufɪsadulafabuftaeabowakʼaatinɪifsanakennitedukananaraballesitaatinɪhumnaaninɪɲapaki??anɪhadufɪirreaninɪdallaɲapaki??atinɪkurupadulenakennitawakʼakanakaranɪɪsaakamɪkʼadʒeladubɪɪsaakamɪduɡefatʃumalanɪinnɪnamaɪsatɪdɪatuwontetahafɪabomalewakʼɪdɪbinɪɪndʒiraisamalesidadʒalatɪdokhannudibɪɪnkʼamnanamɪirrenatahuɪsumaisumatɪkaranaharaɡaraɡubatɪnatisseinnɪharkakɪ??ahudʒɪworanabarsiseakaaninɪti?anɪwoɪhadueabowakʼaatinɪwontenatatenabafteharkɪkankemɪrɡitʃɪnadʒabeseɪrrenɪtantelenɪnakʼorkʼorateatinɪkaranabaliftemilakɪ??aɡufatʃudowarteaninɪɲapakɪ??arebedabsadahaɡaballesutɪ?alaɪmbahuaninɪworradaebuselafakaudoweworrɪdʒiɡemilakɪ??adʒalatʃʼahaisaatinɪhumnaworananakenniteɲapakɪ??anadabsatʃiftaatinɪɲapakɪ??anadurabakʼatʃifteanɪnɪlenɪnamanadʒibuballesaworrɪkʼarkʼarsabarbadeammonamaworrabasudabaworrɪabowakʼa?amateammoinnɪworradʒaladideaninɪworradakhebullesebɪ??ebubenɪfututoltʃaammalleakadokʼekarakesatɪirasirbaatinɪworrakɪ??akanatɪɡamuduranabaftefinnaɡosadibɪtʃʼahaufaharkaki??atɪdebiftaworradurɪaninɪimbennelenɪammanadʒalatɪbulasɪdinɪdibɪlenɪnaduratɪdʒilbɪfatekʼonkʼotɪ??adaɡennanɪnatʃʼahaakʼaftɪworrɪnaheholatefulladʒadʒabdukesatɪdokhateleɡa?aeabonɪwakʼadʒirusidakɪ??ahafarsanɪwakʼanabasuɡudinnaɪsaodesainnɪɲapakɪ??anadabsatʃisesidɪdibɪnadʒalatɪbultʃeɲapakɪ??adʒalanabaseeabowakʼaatinɪɲapakɪ??anadabsatʃifteworrahamamadʒalanabaftemakʼakankeɡudisawakʼɪdabsatʃaɡudoha??uɪsatɪkennaammallenamafohatemudehaɡadʒirutʃʼahaufadʒalatadaudifɪdalotaɪsatʃʼahaufaɡubanɪɡudinnawakʼanamaɡarsiftewaninnɪharkaufɪtinɪmɪdasenamatɪhimtɪɡu??anɪɡu??aitɪanutɪwoɪhimahalkanɪlenɪhalkanɪitɪanatɪwoɪodesanɪworrɪafanɪɪnkʼabu?okhanɪwomaindubatukʼonkʼoisanileindaɡa?anɪdubinɪworralenɪmummelafadakʼabdewakʼɪaduɡubakʼubsiseɪsinɪdɪramaakumanamadubrafudeɡammadubateakumakʼoltʃanamakaɡammadanɪtʃʼahaeuutaltɪɪsinɪilaborutinɪɡabateilaɡaltʃutinɪditɪwontɪowaisɪduradokhataɪndʒirtuserɪabowakʼakʼiteirrenamatɪtoltʃadubinɪabowakʼa?oduɡefatanɪnamawoɪimbenneleinkʼaromsitɪadanɪabowakʼakʼadʒeltukaɡulademulenɪinɡammadadʒetʃɪabowakʼakaduɡatɪkʼalbɪnamalewoɪhubatʃisaabowakʼasodatʃanɪwandansasodanɪtuninɪhaɡadʒirudʒɪrennatetɪmuranɪabowakʼataduɡatɪdɪkʼolewollalaɪnkʼabdumuranɪsuninɪworkʼɪtʃʼahaufairamɪdadɪdammaleiramɪoftɪɪsinɪanahodʒatutantetɪɡorsatatɪ?oaninɪdʒabeselewoɪnabatɪenunamɪdandaewollalaufiarɡueabowakʼawollalakɪ??akanamɪɪnɡarrenaararamɪammalletʃʼahaubuaninɪbekhatoltʃeleduranabasɪisɪnamohatʃudowɪdubaakananɪaninɪkʼulkʼullaetʃʼahaubuɪrafaɡadadubɪti??afɪhereɡɪkɪ??ahasiɡammatʃisueabowakʼasidaki??afɪbafamakɪ??aɡu??aatinɪɡarɡalakʼabduabowakʼɪhakadatʃatantedaɡa?uwakʼɪ?akobohasikʼorkʼoratuinnɪhamanaufikesakʼarkʼarsasierɡeɡarasɪonɪɪradufesibasutɪinnɪhawanatinɪɪsabaftutʃʼahaufafudatesoriotantetʃʼahaufaɪraɡammadutɪinnɪhawanatinɪfetutʃʼahaufasikennemalakanketʃʼahaufasiɡututɪdubanuhodʒdʒaatinɪnamadabsatuɡammannemakʼawakʼakennatinɪbanderakennaoldamnaabowakʼɪfedɪtantetʃʼahaufahaɡututɪammaaninɪɪmbekhaakaabowakʼɪha??uinnɪfohatemudebasuinnɪfullaɪsakʼulkʼulloɡubatɪisatʃʼahaakʼasedʒabennaisatinɪwanheduisadabsatʃisanamɪɡarɪɡarɪufiduɡefatakaɡarɪfardoleufiduɡefataammonumakʼaabowakʼakennaduɡefannanamɪakasɪsuninɪɡufatetɪlafadaammonuolkanedʒadʒabanneedʒandʒinaeabowakʼaha??udabsatʃakennɪhodʒdʒanusi?amanunudaɡa?ɪeabowakʼaha??unɪɡammatʃukʼabawanatinɪdʒabennaɪsakennɪtefɪmaroatinɪisadabsatʃɪftefɪinnɪakamɪɡammadakʼabaatinɪwanɡaranɪɪsafeduɪsakennitewaninnɪkadatuɡutefɪatinɪdufteebaɡudokennɪtefɪsureha??umataworkʼɪmataɪsaɡubaketeinnɪdʒɪrennasikadannanɪdʒɪrennahaɡumadʒiruindumannekennɪtefɪmarokʼarkʼarsaketɪtifɪɡudinnɪɪsa?a?uɡudateatinɪ?a?uɡurrafɪulfinnaɡudakennɪtefɪebitɪtantetahaɡadʒirudʒɪrennaisawolinɪdʒirtɪwanatinɪisawolinɪdʒɪrtufɪinnɪinɡammadaha??unɪabowakʼaɡudaabdatamarodʒalalawakʼataindumannefɪha??uleintʃotʃomneha??itʃɪɲapaufitʃʼahaufakʼabenamaisadʒɪbuletʃʼahaufakʼabainnɪhodʒdʒadufuakaɪbidabobauɡubeworraballesaabowakʼɪdallansuɪsakesaworralɪkʼimseibɪdɪlenɪworrahobasaɪlmanɪworratokolenɪɪmbatutʃʼahaufaha??utɪhobasaworrɪatomalafɪmalteitɪtoltʃeleisaindabsatuinnɪtɪ?aisatinɪworrahadeworrɪɡaraɡalebakʼataeabowakʼanudʒabennakankefarsinaammallesirbɪnetɪirretantelefarsinaatinɪmafɪnalakifteaninɪsitɪbohekʼarkʼarsasikadadeammoatinɪnabasudideewakʼakɪ??aaninɪɡu??asi?amadaammoatinɪnatʃʼahaakʼasudidahalkanilesi?amadaammobokʼotainarɡaduammoatinɪwakʼakʼulkʼullokabartʃumaɡudinnaɡubatetunamɪworrɪisraelɪfarsusiababotɪtennasiabdatesihereɡatedubaatinɪworrabafteworrɪsi?amateɡarɡalakesabahesiabdatedʒennanɪtʃʼahaerudowarteaninɪramonamanitɪnamɪtʃʼahauftɪnatufatenaɡo?esanamidematanatɪɪrbeatinɪwakʼaabdateinnɪhasibasu?oabowakʼɪsidʒalateinnɪhasikʼarkʼarutɪnamɪnakʼorkʼorateɡarahadatɪ??akesanabaselenɪsiharmahadati??alesiumatɪnahosiseaninɪhaɡumadaladesumahereɡadewakʼɪkɪ??ahaɡumaduritɪsinarainfaɡatinɪɡarɡalɪ?anatɪdɪatenamɪnakʼarkʼarudɪbinɪɪndʒiruɲapɪakakoromɪlonɪnamarseakakoromɪlafabaʃanɪdʒadʒannadatutɪ??aendʒandʒaworrɪakaɲentʃaafanɪbanenatɪɪtaneɡadenɪna
