akawakʼa?akobobarbadeitɪdufufullotʃʼahaufanadurafudabalbaladullatɪbanaakaha??unɪɡudinnaolsenuha??unɪɡudinnakuninɪenuinnɪabowakʼakadʒabennafɪirrekʼabuabowakʼakaɲapaufɪdabsatufullotʃʼahaufanadurafudabalbaladullatɪbanaakaha??unɪɡudinnaolsenuha??unɪɡudinnakuninɪenuinnɪabowakʼaɡudakaɲapaufidabsatueabowakʼaaninɪsikadadaewakʼakɪ??aaninɪsidabadaakaɲapɪkɪ??anadabsatenatʃʼahaersenainɡo?esinetahunadowɪworrasihereɡatunamɪdandaeindabsatuammokahurreɡaraɡalesididuɪnumadabsatanɪeabowakʼakarakankenaɡarsisɪdandɪtantenabarsisɪduɡatanteɡulanakʼadʒeltʃɪwandansanabarsisɪatinɪwakʼakɪ??akanabasuaninɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufasidabadaeabowakʼanasufɪdʒalalatantetaindumannetaatinɪhaɡumaduritɪnaɡarsiftekʼabadɪtʃʼahaubufɪwollalaɡafaaninɪkaimatoltʃebɪranademɪdansumafɪdʒalalatantetaindumannenɪnakʼabadɪabowakʼɪdansakʼadʒelatanafɪinnɪnamatʃʼahaubukaratɪkʼadʒelatʃainnɪnamaufɪinɡudimnekaraduɡakʼadʒeltʃefedɪufiɡarsisainnɪnamawoldakʼisaɪsadʒabeseseraɪsaɡututʃʼahaufaduɡafɪdʒalalaindumannenɪdʒabesamakʼaketɪdʒedɪeabowakʼatʃʼahaubutɪ??ahedunaararamɪnamɪabowakʼasodatuenuwakʼɪnamaakasɪsunɪkarafohatefɪaɡarsisanamɪsuninɪwoɪhorataɪlmanɪisalenɪlafadaltɪabowakʼɪnamaisasodatudʒalatahewoldakʼisainnɪworrawolinɪtolfatedʒabesaaninɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufakʼarkʼarsaabowakʼairabarbadainnɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufaɡarɡalakesanabasaeabowakʼanatɪdebɪnanahɪaninɪnamalafawahelaɪnkʼamneɡarɡalakɪ??anarafudɪdiputɪ??akesanabasɪdɪpufɪɡarɡalakɪ??aɪlalɪtʃʼahaubutɪ??atʃʼahaufanaararamɪakaɲapɪnatɪhedateɪlalɪakaworrɪnadʒibuhubadɪnakʼorkʼoradɪnabasɪtʃʼahaeranadowɪaninɪsitɪdedadansumati??afɪkʼadʒelumtɪtɪ??ahanabaftunamɪaninɪhereɡadusiewakʼaworraisraelɪɡarɡalatʃʼahaufakesabasɪeabowakʼaduɡanamurɪwontɪakanatifɪaninɪ?awanduɡatoltʃesitʃʼahaalladabadeeabowakʼanaɪlalɪnaarɡɪɡarafɪkʼalbɪtɪ??ahubadɪdʒalaltɪtantetaindumannehodʒdʒatʃʼahaufakaranaakhetɪaninɪduɡatantekesademaaninɪnamadaratɪiwaheltʃuki??ɪbaleitɪindɪaduaninɪnamawanhamtutoltʃuwaheltʃuɪnfedutʃʼahaubɪtʃalewomairaɪnkʼabuabowakʼaaninɪharkadɪkʼadeakatʃʼahaubuɪnkʼamneɡarsisewansorioɪratɪsibasaninɪmaraaninɪfaruɡalatanɪsid ʼahaufadʒalanabasenamɪdabsanɪ?owakʼadabatuinɡammadaworrɪhaɡumadʒiruɪntʃeru?ohi??esɪɪsatɪboheinnɪindaɡa?afɪɡarɡalaɪsatʃʼahaufakesaɪsabasamalaɪkanɪabowakʼanamaisasodatuedeɡarɡalakesabaftɪa??anaɪsatɪkaɪsatɪdetunamɪabowakʼaduɡefatutʃʼahauftɪisasodadanamɪɪsasalfatutʃʼahauftɪwomafuirakatuɲentʃɪlenɪsaɡaledabeɪmbelaammonamɪabowakʼabarbaduwandansatokoleɪndabuɪlmanɪtɪ??akotanatʃʼahaakʼasaakawakʼasodatanɪɪsanɪbarsisaɡammadelubutantetaderatufeta?osɪhamennaindubatinɪ?okhanɪinkɪ??ɪbinɪtʃʼahaubuiradebɪwandansatoltʃɪɡarakanketʃʼahaufanɪnaɡa?abarbadɪabowakʼɪnamaduɡakʼadʒelaɪlalehodʒdʒaworrɪisa?amuledʒalaowataammonamatʃʼahaubuhodʒatuɪndidadubaakasinɪhodʒdʒaworrɪdudebɪanɪinkʼabatanɪhodʒdʒanamɪduɡakʼadʒelanɪabowakʼa?amatuinnɪdʒalaowateɡarɡalaɪsatʃʼahaufakesabasanamaufɪdʒɪbateabowakʼɪitɪdɪatekaabdɪwomatuinkʼamnelebasanamɪdansanɪɡarɡalaheduarɡataammoabowakʼɪɡarɡalasunɪtʃʼahaufakesaisabasalafeisatokoletʃʼahaabudowatʃʼahaubitʃatʃʼahaubumaɪsatɪɪdʒesanamanamaduɡadʒibuwollalaitɪmuranɪɡarɡaltʃanɪabowakʼɪɡumɪufibasenamaɪsatɪbakʼatutʃʼahaufalububasaeabowakʼanamananɪmorkunɪmorkɪnamanahaduhadɪwontetantefudadɪkotɪnakʼarkʼarɪworanafɪdaɡarakankefudadɪkotɪnamanarebuduranabasɪlubuti??anɪanumatɪsibasadʒedɪnamanaɪdʒesufeduhatʃʼahaersanɪballesanitɪnamɪwanhamtunatɪmalatuhanaradebiewantahuwollalutɪhodʒdʒamalaɪkanɪabowakʼaworrarebduworrɪhabuabu?otabubenɪfutefakatutɪkaranɪworrahadukanaemutʃutʃatemalaɪkanɪabowakʼalenɪhaworradoftelafabuftutɪworrɪfa??umatanatururanamɪdaseakanakʼabubolalenakʼoteammoatoworrɪɪmbennebadinɪhadufteworrakʼabatutɪtururanɪworrɪnaka?elenɪhaworrakʼabeworraballesutɪdubaaninɪmaroabowakʼatifɪɡammadewaninnɪnabasefɪkʼilɪtamaaninɪɡarakɪ??atʃʼahaufanɪwanabowakʼanɪdʒedueabowakʼanamɪakaketɪɪndʒiruatinɪnamalafanamadʒabadʒalabaftehi??esalenamaɪsadabsudʒalabaftanamɪtʃʼahaubukʼabudaranɪnahɪmatewanhamtuaninɪɪmbennekesanabusadansumaaninɪworratoltʃeworrɪhalonafudewanhamtunatoltʃadubaakananɪaninɪufɪdʒɪbadewantahuwollalaammo?oworrɪfa??adabeaninɪufɪaɡabsetʃʼahaarkʼɪnakʼadeɡadʒedeakumanamadʒalafɪobolesaufɪtiwakʼakadatukadadefɪaninɪakumanamahadaufitɪbohumataɡakʼabadebohefɪammoɡafaɡarɡalɪnakʼabateworrɪtʃʼahauftɪɡammadewoltɪbahenaɡo?esenamɪaninɪfulaɪmbennenadanenalakɪsudideakumanamanafaɡo?esuworrɪnadʒibenamideeabowakʼaatinɪhaɡa?omɪkawomaintoltʃinewankanaufumateteɪlaltaharkaworradʒalanabasɪɲentʃakanatʃʼahaufaduranabasɪdubaaninɪɡumɪtanteduratɪɡalatasidebisenamatʃʼahaufaduratɪsifarsakataebadɪtɪ??adʒedekʼilɪtamukʼilɪtamudowɪnamafa??umatananadʒɪbulekataemarolalalati??atɪdʒedenamidunaradowɪworrɪnaɡa?aindubatuammonamanaɡa?akʼabuwanɪsakadaradubataworrɪnahɪmateɪ??ewandʒedulelewanatinɪtate?aaɡarreammoeabowakʼaatinɪwankana?aaɡarteewakʼakɪ??aafanɪkʼabatenarainfaɡatinɪeabokaɪnabasɪewakʼakɪ??akotɪnadubadɪeabowakʼaatinɪkaduɡatɪduɡanamurɪɲapakɪ??anaɡo?esudowɪworranu?aisaballesinewanfenuarɡannedʒetʃudowɪnamaɡarɡalakɪ??aarɡeɡammaduhatʃʼahaersanɪballesanɪnamawannaradʒiruufɪsehuhatʃʼahaerafɪfokodowanɪnamɪakaduɡanamuranɪarɡufeduhaɡammadeɡu??atʃʼahaufaɪ??ewandʒeduabowakʼɪakamɪɡudainnɪwanhodʒatunɪɪsahodʒatearɡatuɪraɡammadadubaaninɪduɡatanteodesehalkanɪɡu??asifarsainnɪwakʼadidedɪkʼoleinsodatumaroinnɪki??ibaufɪtifɪufɪolfudufɪinnɪwanwakʼɪtʃʼahaubuisaarɡewollalaitɪmuruɪnsehudubinɪafanɪɪsakesabatutʃʼahauftɪtatʃʼahaubutifɪtadaraammalleinnɪwandansakʼadʒeltudebieɪntoltʃuinnɪhodʒdʒasireɡubatʃʼahaɪsulewanhamtumalatawontɪinnɪtoltʃutokolenɪdansanitɪinnɪwanhamtutokoleɪndidueabowakʼadʒalaltɪtantetaindumanneɡubaleɪnɡetɪduɡanɪtetɪlenɪdumansalebiradabartɪduɡanɪtanteakumaɡaraderatɪduɡanɪatinɪkʼortewoinɪmurtulenɪhaɡadimmubarinɪɡadɪfaɡatɪnamafɪhorɪlenɪharkumakankekesadʒiraewakʼadʒalaltɪtantetaindumanneakamɪdansanukolakankedʒalatɪɲapakennaduradokhannanusaɡaleɡudoatinɪnukennitesorannedansumatantetaakaɡalana?atudunnaatinɪmadadʒirennatɪmaroifsaketɪtifɪnuifseaɡarranamasibekhuakumakʼaradʒalatekanɪdʒaladɪnamaduɡakʼabuleakumakʼarakanɪwanduɡatoltʃifɪnamaki??ibanahadudowɪtʃʼahaubɪtʃalenaɡussudowɪfullanamɪhamanɪitɪdʒiɡelalɪworrɪatʃumatʃʼahaisadandaeolɪnkauwannamɪtʃʼahaubutahumamteheredeufɪinɡarɡaltʃinɪnamawanhamtutoltʃuleindɪbefatinɪworrɪ?osuakabu?oɡodubadeakamukhaɡoɡoɡeduaabowakʼaduɡefadɪwandansatoltʃɪlafalenaɡa?anɪkesataɪɡammadakankeabowakʼairabarbadɪdubainnɪwanɡaranɪkankefedutʃʼahaufasikennaabowakʼaufɪkennɪɪsadabadudubainnɪsikʼarkʼaradubaakumaadunɪɡu??alafaɡu??asiftuinnɪduɡatantemullisaobsɪtaɪwanabowakʼɪsitoltʃueɡadɪnamawoɪhoratuka?okhanɪmalaufɪhamanɪwoɪarɡatuwanɪsamamteheredeufɪinɡarɡaltʃinɪdallanteufɪinɡarɡaltʃinɪwontɪsuninɪɡarɡalasɪtinɪduftɪnamɪabowakʼaeɡatulafadalaammotʃʼahaubitʃakesaɡussanɪtʃʼahaubitʃɪ?osubadaatinɪ?obarbaduleinaɡartulafadalewoɪhoratenaɡa?anɪtatʃʼahaubitʃɪnamadansatɪmalateisadʒibeilahamtunɪlalaammoabowakʼɪwanakatʃʼahaubitʃaballesanɪbekhufɪisakoblatʃʼahaubitʃɪɡoradefudatetɪ?aɡubetɪdabehi??esawomaɪnkʼamneɪdʒesenamaduɡatoltʃufitaammoworrɪɡoradumaufɪtinɪhobaeɡubeworraletʃʼahaatʃabsanɪwontɪdɪkʼonɪnamɪduɡakʼabuwanɡudonamɪtʃʼahaubukʼabuiradʒirtɪwontɪakanatifɪabowakʼɪtʃʼahaubitʃairreɪsaɪrafudaammonamaduɡadʒabesekʼorkʼorataabowakʼɪnamaɪsasalfatudʒabeselaftɪhaɡadʒirudʒɪrennataworratatɪhodʒdʒabarɪhammatuleɡarɡalainarɡatuhodʒdʒaolanɪbutuleworrɪdɪkʼolesaɡaleɪndabuammotʃʼahaubitʃɪɪnumabadaɲapɪabowakʼaakumadarara?osubuebadeakaara?osudabratʃʼahaubitʃɪlikʼefudebasudadabaammonamɪduɡaardʒomanɪwoɪnamakennanamɪabowakʼɪebiselafadalaammokainnɪabarekesaɡussanɪabowakʼɪedʒatanamakʼadʒeltʃenamaisaɡammatʃɪsuledʒabesekʼorkʼoratainnɪ?odʒɪɡeleatʃitɪɪnhafuwontɪakanatifɪabowakʼatɪisakasaaninɪamma?adʒareɡannɪkɪ??a?aderateammotakanamaduɡakawakʼɪlakiseɪlmanɪɪsasaɡalekadatuɪnɡarreinnɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufaakanumatɪwoɪnamakennewoɪnamalɪkʼesaammalleɪlmanɪisalenɪtaebatɪwanhamtuiradebɪwandansatoltʃɪdubaakananɪdalotɪkankehaɡadʒirudʒɪrennalafatanakesatawontɪakanatifɪabowakʼɪduɡadʒalataɡumɪɪsakʼulkʼulloleillakisuinnɪhaɡadʒirudʒɪrennaworrakʼorkʼorataammoɪlmanɪtʃʼahaubitʃalafakesaɡussanɪnamɪduɡalafadalehaɡadʒirudʒɪrennakesataafanɪnamaduɡakʼaromatʃʼahaalladubatanɪarabɪisalenɪdubɪkʼadʒeltutʃʼahaalladubatainnɪserawakʼadʒabesekʼalbɪkesake?atahaɡumadʒiruiraɪnɡorutʃʼahaubitʃɪnamadansaɡadeɪdʒesufedaammoabowakʼɪharkaɲapaɪsatɪillakisu?okhanɪhodʒdʒadubɪisakʼoranɪakawollalaitɪmuranɪeɪndʒeduabowakʼadabadɪdubɪɪsaɡulademɪinnɪlafasikenneakasinɪɡurrasitɪtoltʃadubaatɪnɪlenɪworratʃʼahaubukalafasunɪkesaɡussanɪaɡartatʃʼahaubitʃatokotɪdʒirakadurɪnamadabseakahɪndesɪlebanonɪmukhatʃʼahaufairaderatunamatʃʼahaufabiradabreammoeɡe?oaninɪdatudabreinnɪatʃɪɪndʒiruaninɪisabarbadeammoarɡudadabenamadansalalɪnamaduɡahubadɪnamanaɡa?aɪlmanɪinnɪdaletɪmakʼaɪsabadidowaammotʃʼahaubitʃaballesanɪɪlmanɪinnɪdalelletʃʼahaufafɪtanɪabowakʼɪnamaduɡakʼadʒelabaseɡu??aɡarɡalaworrakʼorkʼoratainnɪworrakʼarkʼareɲapaworradurabaseammallewanworrɪkʼarkʼarsaɪsatɪbakʼatefɪinnɪharkatʃʼahaubɪtʃaledʒalabasaeabowakʼadallansutantekesawollalanatɪmurtenainɡarɡaltʃinɪatinɪtɪ?atetinɪnaworantelafanɪnadoftemarodallansutetɪtifɪfa??adabadʒabatɪharkanakʼabamarotʃʼahaubuti??atifɪnafakɪ??atʃʼahaufa?adukubɪkʼabatetʃʼahaubunɪtɪ??a?a?uakafatʃabɪsanɪnalikʼɪmsiteɪsinɪ?a?ubaulfoaninɪbatʃuindandennenatɪtatemarodallummati??atifɪmadanɪtɪ??ahamateʃamteaninɪ?a?uɡadʒede?alafatɪnamatʃarsanɪhalkanɪɡu??aaninɪbohademaaninɪ?a?ukʼannonɪnakʼabatelubunɪdɪkʼumanakesaimbahinɪaninɪ?a?ulafeufɪdʒɪbadelafatɪnatʃʼahaarasanɪɡaranɪkɪ??anahamatetaedukubsadewadaeaboatinɪwananinɪfeduɪmbetawatʃati??aletʃʼahaufaindaɡetaonnenɪnatʃotʃotehumnitɪnarahobateiltɪti??alenɪwoɪarɡudadabdedʒalanɪti??afɪollanɪki??alenɪmaromadati??atifɪnatɪdɪatʃudideworrɪki??alenɪ?anabakʼatenamɪnaɪdʒesufedutururanaka?enamɪnaɡarɡaltʃufedubadɪtɪ??adubataworrɪmalanatɪdatʃuillakisuaninɪdudaɡurranɪwomaindaɡennekaafanɪlenɪwomaindubannefakadaaninɪnamawomaindaɡennekahodʒdʒa?amanilenamadʒalainowannefakadaammoeabowakʼaaninɪsidabadaeabowakʼakɪ??anamɪnadʒalaowatusɪumaakaɲapɪkɪ??abaditɪ??aarɡenainɡo?esinetahudowɪammalleakaworrɪbaditɪ??aarɡeɪnkorretahudowɪaninɪdɪkʼumaindʒɪɡinɪdukubɪlenɪnaillakisuaninɪdabakɪ??alalefadetʃʼahaubutɪ??ahɪmadaɲapɪkɪ??adʒabahamanamɪfa??umatananadʒibulenɪakabɪ??etanadʒiranamɪaninɪwandansatoltʃe?anatɪɡarɡaleɲapanatɪtahewananinɪduɡaɡulademufɪeabowakʼanaillakɪsinɪewakʼakɪ??anarainfaɡatinɪhurrisɪnakʼarkʼa kɪ??akesatɪindossineaninɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufaduɡatantetifɪkʼarkʼarsakankeodeseɡumɪtanteduratɪaninɪwandʒalalatantetaindumannetifɪduɡatanteindossineeabowakʼaaninɪɪmbekhaatinɪhaɡadʒirtunanahuɪndidudʒalalafɪduɡanɪtantehodʒdʒatʃʼahaufanakʼorkʼoratɪɡarɡalɪhedunɪmummeɪnkʼamne?anakʼabatetʃʼahaubunɪtɪ??a?anadakʼabdedandaelafaleɪnarɡuɪsinɪhennaɪnkʼabdurɪfensamataki??aleiradʒirtɪaninɪ?a?uufɪdʒɪbadeeabowakʼanabasɪhurrisɪnakʼarkʼarɪnamanaɪdʒesufeduhadabsatanɪballesanitɪnamamaroɡarɡalaki??atɪɡammaduhadudadubatɪdebɪsanɪtʃʼahaersanitɪnamanaɡo?esulehamudamsɪsanɪtʃʼahaersanɪnamɪsitɪdufutʃʼahauftɪhaɡammadekʼilɪtamutɪnamɪbafamakankedʒalatutʃʼahauftɪhaɡu??atʃʼahaufaabowakʼɪakamɪɡudadʒedutɪeaboaninɪhi??esalafairreɪnkʼamneammoatinɪɪnumanakʼabataatinɪbafamaki??afɪwakʼakɪ??ahurrisɪkotɪnakʼarkʼarɪa??anaɪsatɪkahi??esanahuhodʒdʒainnɪɡarɡalakʼabuabowakʼatɪɪsakʼarkʼarainnɪɪsakʼorkʼoratelubuɪsabasalafainnɪkesatahukesatɪɪsaebisaammalleharkaɲapaɪsatɪisaɪnkennuhodʒdʒainnɪfa??adabesirekesatʃʼahaɪsuleabowakʼɪisakʼarkʼarefa??isedʒabesaaninɪwandʒedeeabowakʼaaninɪ?asitɪtʃʼahaubamenanahɪnafa??isɪɲapɪkɪ??ahamennakɪ??adubatewandʒeduinnɪ?omɪduemakʼanɪɪsabadanamɪtokolenɪduɡanɪnaarɡuɪndufuammoworrɪnamatʃʼahaufairaodutɪ??atahamennaɡurefullatʃʼahaufademeodesanamɪnadʒibutʃʼahauftɪwankɪ??awoltɪɡunɡumehamennakɪ??amalatewandʒedudukubɪhamanɪ?aisakʼabateinnɪsireɪraɪnkahuɪraleɪnhafukaaninɪɡudodabadekanusaɡalewolinɪɲannulenɪ?anatɪɡaraɡaleeabowakʼananahɪnafa??isɪakaaninɪɲapakɪ??asunɪhalobafadudubaakananɪworrɪnaindabsatuammalleakaatinɪnaɡammatʃɪftelebekhamaroaninɪwanduɡatoltʃufɪatinɪnakʼarkʼartehaɡadʒirudʒɪrennafullatantenatesiftaammafɪheɡerilefarsaaminɪaminɪakumahɪdinɪbɪsanɪkʼabanaodududaratuanɪnɪlenɪakasumasidaraewakʼaewakʼadʒiruaninɪsitɪdebodaaninɪ?omɪdemesiarɡesikadadaaninɪhalkanɪɡu??aboheimɪmanɪkɪ??atʃʼahaallasoradakaɲapɪkɪ??ahodʒdʒatʃʼahaufanaɡafatewakʼɪkankemenanɪdʒeduhodʒdʒaaninɪwandabrekʼabaduɡafaaninɪɡumɪɡudowolinɪmanawakʼadakʼeɡumɪɡammadakʼabdutasɪrbitewakʼafarsa?atudurademeɡaranɪnahamateaninɪmafɪakanatahelalefadeɡ totʃʼahaubitʃɪtururakesanabuseleaninɪserakankeiwollaluaninɪhalkanɪɡudodamakʼekaemarokʼorsumanɪtantewanduɡatifɪsifarsaaninɪdʒalanamasisodatukaserakankeɡututʃʼahaufaeabowakʼalaftɪ?a?udʒalalatantetaindumannenɪɡutamteadatantenabarsisɪeabowakʼaatinɪ?a?ukakhutanteɡutehodʒatutantewandansatoltʃitewananinɪserakankeduɡefadufɪbekhafɪkʼalbɪnakennɪɡafaatinɪkʼaranainkʼadʒeltʃinɪaninɪwollalatoltʃeammoammatanaaninɪdubɪtanteɪnɡutaatinɪakamɪdansaakamɪnamanataadatantenabarsisɪnamɪki??ɪbanɪ?adaradubateɡurranaballeseammoaninɪɡarakɪ??atʃʼahaufanɪserakankeɡutadʒarɪkuninɪhubatʃawomatuɪnkʼabuammoserɪkankenaɡammatʃisaɡarɡalɪatinɪnaɡarɡaltʃitenadansaserakankenabarsiseserɪkankekaatinɪnabarsiftekʼarsifɪworkʼiletʃʼahaufairawoɪnabahaatinɪkanaumtenakʼorkʼoratehubatʃanakennɪakaaninɪserakankebaraduwananinɪkakhutanteabdadufɪnamɪsisodatunaarɡɪnanɪɡammadaeabowakʼaaninɪɪmbekhaakadubinɪtantetʃʼahauftɪduɡaammalleakaatinɪduɡaɡulaɡarɡalanatɪerɡitedʒalaltɪtantetaindumannehanadʒabesituakumaatinɪanahodʒatutantetɪkakhatewananinɪserakankedʒaladufɪnanahɪnadʒɪresɪwannamɪki??ɪbanɪdaranɪnahimatefɪhaisatʃʼahaersanitɪammoaninɪwanatinɪnabarsiftutahehereɡanamɪsisodatutʃʼahauftɪhanatɪdufutɪworrɪserakankehubatutʃʼahauftɪserakankeakadansanaɡutʃɪsisɪakaaninɪintʃerfanneeabowakʼaaninɪ?aufɪdʒɪbadeatotaebafamakankeeɡaduaninɪwantʃʼahaufakesadubɪtanteabdadaatoaninɪtaeakaatinɪnakʼarkʼartueɡuiltɪnaɡoɡodedubaaninɪwansinɪdʒeduatinɪ?omɪduftenakʼarkʼartaaninɪɡordʒodadɪtahudʒɪɪnkʼamnetaɡatanɪfakadaammoaninɪserakankeɪndeneaninɪhaɡa?omɪeɡumaleatinɪ?omɪnamanaɡarɡaltʃuɡarɡaltʃitadʒarɪki??ɪbanɪkaserakankeɪnɡunne?a?ubolanakʼotenakʼabufedaserɪkanketʃʼahauftɪkaduɡefatanɪnamɪ?adaranɪnaballesenakʼarkʼarɪworrɪdɪkʼumanaballesenainɪdʒesinɪammoaninɪserakankeillakimnemarodʒalalatantetaindumannetifɪlubunabasɪakaaninɪserakankeɡutueabowakʼadubinɪtantehaɡaheɡerɪtetɪɪsinɪhaɡadʒirtutʃʼahaufaɡubadʒirtɪduɡanɪtantehaɡadʒirtuindumatuatinɪlafafullumaɪsitɪmidasiteɪsinɪdebiteintʃotʃotuwontɪtʃʼahauftɪmarodubɪtetɪtifɪammallemarosihodʒatufɪhaɡaarraledʒirtɪatosilaserɪkankeɡammadakɪ??atahubateaninɪ?aɡarɡalakɪ??akesatɪdueaninɪbarsisatanteɪndeduwontɪakanatifɪsitɪwansuninɪnadʒɪreseaninɪkanketɪnabasɪaninɪakaserakankeɡutu?aitɪɡameworrɪtʃʼahaubuɡadetɪnaɪdʒesufedaammoaninɪdʒetʃakankehodʒdʒatʃʼahaufainkʼabadaaninɪ?a?ubaradeakawontɪtʃʼahauftɪhaɡaufikʼabduammoserɪkankehaɡaɪnkʼabuewakʼaaninɪserakankeakamɪdʒaladaaninɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufataewanɪsahereɡaserɪkankehodʒdʒatʃʼahaufanawolinɪdʒiratanafɪaninɪɲapakɪ??atʃʼahaufairakʼalbɪkʼabaaninɪnamanabarsisetʃʼahaufairakʼalbɪkʼabawananinɪbarsisatanteɡu??atʃʼahaufahereɡufɪwananinɪserakankeɡutufɪaninɪdʒaroleirakʼalbɪkʼabaaninɪwanhamtutʃʼahaufa?airaufɪdoweakaakasinɪdubɪtanteɡutuaninɪbarsisatanteiraɪnɡorrewontɪakanatifɪnamɪnabarsisusidubinɪtanteakamɪmɪoftɪɪsinɪdammaɪralenatɪmɪoftɪaninɪkʼaromaserakankeiraarɡadetanafɪwanhamtutʃʼahaufadʒibadubinɪtanteifsetɪ??aɪsinɪkaranaɪfsitenanɪdemtɪaninɪakaserakankekaduɡaɡutukakhutɪ??adʒabesaeabowakʼaɡarɡalɪkɪ??aɡudaakumaatinɪnatɪkakhatedunadowɪnadʒɪresɪwanɡalatakaaninɪsikennunarafudadɪeabowakʼaserakankelenabarsisɪaninɪlubutɪ??a?adʒɪbadeammotatuleserakankeɪndeneworrɪtʃʼahaubu?atururanaka?eammoaninɪserakankeɪraɪnɡorreaninɪadatantehaɡadʒirudʒɪrennaindʒabesaɪsinɪwanɡarakɪ??aɡammatʃɪsatɪaninɪ?akutadeakaserakankehaɡadʒirutʃʼahaufaɡutuaninɪnamaɡaralamaɡudodʒibaammoserakankeindʒaladaatinɪwontetɪ??aammallefullaaninɪitɪbakʼaduaninɪdubɪtanteabdadaɪsanɪworrɪtʃʼahaubunabɪrafaɡadaaninɪserawakʼakɪ??aɡutaakumaatinɪnatɪkakhatenadʒabesɪakaaninɪdʒɪraduwananinɪabdadunadowartenaintʃersinɪdʒabesɪnakʼabɪɡarɡalakesanabasɪdubaaninɪadatantehodʒdʒatʃʼahaufadʒabeseɡutaatinɪnamaserakankeɡutudiduɪndidamalɪworrakasobawomakesaɪndʒiruatinɪnamatʃʼahaubutʃʼahaufaakumahuralafatɪdʒɪssitatanafɪaninɪwanatinɪnabarsiftudʒaladamarotetifɪaninɪsodademaroseraketilemudamaaninɪwanduɡakʼadʒeltu?a?utoltʃeharkaɲapaki??atɪnaillakɪsinɪakaanahodʒatutantekʼarkʼartukakhadɪnamaki??ɪbanadabsudowɪiltɪtɪ??a?abafamakankeeɡadateufɪdʒɪbatekʼarkʼarsaatinɪnakakhatedʒalalatantetaindumannenɪnadʒaladɪserakankenabarsisɪaninɪhodʒatutetɪhubat inɪhubatʃafɪɪrreleɪnkʼabaha??otɪlenɪananɪlafamohatedʒallabɪlenɪaninɪdubɪmurakʼarkʼarsaki??anɪnamɪlafafidufidedʒarolenɪlafalenɪananɪdubɪmurtɪaninɪnamanadʒalatudʒaladenamɪnabarbadulenɪnaarɡaaninɪduresaɡurrakʼabuanumatɪhormatafɪbultumanamakennawontɪnamɪnaraarɡatuworkʼifɪkʼarsɪdansatʃʼahaufairadʒirtɪaninɪkaraduɡaɡulademadandɪkʼadʒelumaɪraɪnɡoruaninɪnamanadʒalatuhorsisemanaworralewandansanɪɡutawontɪkʼarakainnɪmɪdaseanakʼarafiteatolafaleinuminunaumanɪbarɪnifɪmadabɪsanɪtʃʼahaufaduratɪaninɪdaladeɡarenifɪkubɪleletʃʼahaufaanumatɪduradʒiraatowakʼɪlafafɪardaobrutifɪbi??eleinuminɪaninɪdaladeaninɪɡafainnɪɡubadɪrirsemummewakʼafɪlafafullaɪsinɪbarɪninɪwoltɪedʒɪtutɪdabedumansalemɪdaseburkʼabarinɪbanebɪsanɪbarɪnilehaɡainnɪitɪseredabrudowelafumadʒiraɡafainnɪlafa?a?abeleaninɪartumadʒiraaninɪhudʒɪsunɪkesaleakumaoɡesaɪsawaheltʃeɡammadɪɪsakaɡu??atʃʼahaufanarabahaanɪnɪlenɪhodʒdʒaisawolinɪdʒiruinɡammadawontɪaninɪɪraɡammadulafafɪnamaisɪkesatauɪlmanɪtɪ??aammanatʃʼahaakʼasadubɪtɪ??adʒabesadubaɡammadaarɡatanɪwanɪsanɪbarsɪsanɪtʃʼahaakʼasakʼalbefadadʒabesanamɪtʃʼahaakʼasukahodʒdʒatʃʼahaufamanakɪ??aduraedʒebalbalakesatɪnaeɡuɡammadaarɡatanamɪnaarɡate?adʒɪrennaarɡatenamɪakasɪsunɪebaabowakʼaɪraarɡatanamɪnadabe?aufɪballesekanadʒibulenɪduadʒalatakʼaromɪ?a?umanadʒarateutubatorbanɪutubeinnɪ?a?uhorɪkʼaledʒilatoltʃedadilewanurɡesaninɪitɪnakʼesaɡaleɡololakurfeseinnɪdubraisahodʒatu?amebenadirakesa?akubɪkorakotaɪsanɪnamɪwomaɪmbennedʒedanɪammallenamadallelenɪwandʒetanɪkotasaɡaletɪ??aɲadadadɪaninɪurɡeseduɡanamawomaɪmbennebɪra?adʒɪrennaarɡadakarahubatʃaɡula?anamɪki??ɪbaɡorsuarabaarɡatanamɪnamahamaɡorsudanitʃaarɡataki??ɪbainɡorsinɪ?oɡorsiteinnɪsidʒibaammo?okʼaroɡorsiteinnɪsidʒalatawontɪatinɪnamakʼarotɪhimtutʃʼahauftɪkʼaromadartifɪwontɪatinɪnamakʼadʒelatɪhimtutʃʼahauftɪbekhaisadartɪkʼaromɪlubusideresa?okʼaromakʼabatenamɪinnɪwoɪbahufɪsiammo?oisadidenamɪɡarɡalusɪumadallumtɪnitɪdallitɪtʃʼahaeraɪnkʼamnetalalabademtufakatɪɪsinɪbalbalamanaɪsiduratete?okhanɪbartʃumafudatekubɪdirasunɪɡubatetenamaufumahudʒɪufɪ?aukawanbɪ??ak deresitɪammobultinɪtʃʼahaubitʃainɡababatɪwontɪnamɪduɡadabatuɡammadanɪduftɪammotʃʼahaubitʃɪwomainhereɡatuabowakʼɪnamaduɡakʼorkʼorataammotʃʼahaubitʃaimballesanamɪduɡafullaitɪbahukʼabaammotʃʼahaubitʃɪfullaitɪbahuɪnkʼabunamɪduɡadubɪkʼadʒeltudubataammoarabawanhamtudubatuinkutanɪnamɪduɡadubɪfakatudubataammotʃʼahaubitʃɪɡu??atʃʼahaufawaninfakannedubataabowakʼɪnamamɪsanawoinɪbimukesanamadabsuɪndʒibaammonamamɪsanakʼɪtesewoɪbimuindʒalatanamaufɪɡudisuintʃersanɪammonamɪufɪinɡudimnekʼaromaarɡatanamadansaduɡaɪsatɪkʼadʒeltʃaammonamɪnamɪinduɡefannetʃʼahaubuufɪtinɪbadaduromɪɡu??aduawomasiɪmbahuammoduɡanɪlubutantebaftɪnamatʃʼahaubuɪnkʼamneduɡanɪbultɪɪsamidasitɪammotʃʼahaubitʃɪhamennumaufɪtinɪbadanamaduɡakʼadʒelumaɪsatɪbasaammonamɪnamɪinduɡefannedubumaufɪtinɪdɪbamahodʒdʒatʃʼahaubitʃɪdudabunɪisalenɪɪsumawolinɪdotɪwontɪinnɪhereɡate?amummebatenamakʼadʒelaɡarɡalakesabasanɪammotʃʼahaubitʃaɡarɡalasunitɪkʼabatanamɪwakʼaɪmbenneafanumaufɪtinɪollaufɪballesaammonamɪduɡakʼaromumaufɪtinɪufɪbasa?onamɪduɡawoɪhoratudirɪinnɪkesataulenɪinɡammada?otʃʼahaubitʃɪdunamɪwoltɪbaheɡammadesirbelalaba?onamɪduɡakʼadʒelanɪdiraebisudirɪsuninɪɡurrahorataammodʒetʃɪtʃʼahaubitʃadirasunɪimballesanamɪnamatufateɡo?esudalleammonamɪwoɪbekhuafanɪkʼabatanamawomaindossinekahamtunamadubatuwomaitɪhimuhɪmmalleammonamakʼufanɪwandossaleitɪhɪmanɪɡotʃitɪnamadurademuɪnkʼamneɪmbadɪɡorsɪdʒarsahedunaɡa?anɪdufanamɪnamafulaɪmbenneɡatɪkenneufiɡaba?owansunɪufɪhankʼifteirasidʒirtɪnitɪtʃʼahaerafokokʼabduinsalfatanifɪammonɪtinɪtʃʼahaeraɪnkʼamnewanfokotɪnamɪlafanɪwomainhodʒannehaɡadʒiruwomainhoratuammonamɪɪrrenɪwoɪbarbaduhorɪhoratanamɪnamanahuwoɪufɪmɪdasaammonamɪnasuɪnkʼamnewoɪufɪdura?akatʃʼahaubitʃɪwomainhoratuammonamɪkʼadʒelumaɡulademuwandansaarɡatanamɪduɡatʃʼahaallaɡulademuindʒɪrataammokawanhamtutoltʃuɪnduaabowakʼɪnamahereɡahamakʼabudʒibeammonamawandansaɡulademuindʒalatawankanahubadatʃʼahaubitʃɪɡarɡalaɪnumaarɡataammonamɪduɡaɡarɡaladurabahamidaɡumtɪnitɪwomaɪmbennekʼubeworkʼɪtafunnanɪbo??etɪka?anɪfakatɪwontɪnamɪdansanɪfedudansumatatɪ?onamɪhamanɪwanfeduarɡatenamɪtʃʼahauftɪindallananamɪɡarɪardʒatahesunumaɪranɪhoraammohaɡɪɡarɪhorɪɪrabahudidesunumaɪranɪhi??umtɪkʼabatɪardʒatahadubawoɪhoratanɪnamakʼarkʼaraisanileinkʼarkʼaranɪnamamɪdanɪdosseɡatɪɡudonɪeɡatuinabaranɪammokaɡurɡuruinfarsanɪnamɪwandansabarbaduɡurradansaarɡataammonamɪwanhamtubarbaduwomasunɪarɡatanamɪduromaufɪdabatuakumabalamukhaɡoɡoɡelafatɪdʒiɡaammonamɪduɡaɡulademuakumamukhadotɪbahebosonanamɪwanhamtuworraufɪtinɪdufutakatanalewomahamtutahadallenɪɡu??atʃʼahaufakʼarohodʒatɪduɡanɪdʒirennanɪduftɪammololɪdʒɪrennasunɪimballesanamɪɡorsadiduwomaimbaratuɡorsadidɪtɪlenɪdallumanamɪdansanɪabowakʼairaebaarɡataammoinnɪnamawanhamtunamatɪmalatuwollalaitɪmuranamɪhamanɪdʒɪrennaɪsakesadʒadʒabateɪnedʒuammonamɪduɡaintʃotʃoudʒadʒabatetɪedʒanɪtinɪdansanɪɡadadɪrsatɪammonɪtinɪhamtunɪdirsaɪntʃeredukubahamalafakesatɪhereɡɪnamaduɡakamaduɡatɪammohereɡɪtʃʼahaubitʃawandaratɪdubinɪtʃʼahaubitʃawannamaidʒesatɪammodubinɪduɡalubunamabaftɪtʃʼahaubitʃɪɪnduadaraleinhoratuammonamaduɡaworrɪɪsahaɡumadʒirutʃʼahaufaɪndʒiranamakʼaromumaisatinɪsadanɪammodalledallumumaisatinɪtufatanɪnamanamaɡudaufɪsehukaammoɡaratʃaɪmbulleiranamaɡudinnaɪnkʼamnekaharkaufɪtinɪhodʒatebulutɪɡomanamɪdansanɪhorɪufɪkʼorkʼorataammohamanɪdabseballesanamɪobrukʼotatusaɡaleɪndabuammonamɪwanwomakesaɪndʒirreɡulademuwomaimbaratunamɪhamanɪwomahamtutoltʃutʃʼahaallabarbadaammonamɪduɡaduɡaɪraintʃotʃoutʃʼahaubitʃɪafanumaufɪtinɪtururasenaammonamɪduɡaafanumaufɪtinɪwanhamtukesaufɪbasanamɪwomadʒedufɪwomatoltʃuɡulawanmalefɪarɡatadallenɪ?otʃʼahaufakʼaroufɪsetɪammokʼaronɪɡorsatʃʼahaakʼasadalledallansunɪ?osuɪramullatɪammonamɪwoɪbekhuarabaleɪnobsanamɪduɡadubatudubɪdʒirtuduɡesaammokadaradubatudubɪɪndʒirreduɡesadubinɪhereɡamaledubatanɪakumaworananamaworantɪdubinɪhereɡanɪdubatanɪnamafa??iftɪdartɪ?osudabartɪammoduɡanɪhaɡumadʒirtuindabartunamɪhamennamalatuhereɡanamanɪsobuɡarakesakʼabaammokawandansamalatuɡammadaarɡatawontɪhamtunɪnamaduɡainkʼabatuammotʃʼahaubitʃɪɡarɡalamalewandibɪɪnkʼabuabowakʼɪki??ibadʒibaammonamadubɪufɪɡutuɪraɡammadanamɪwoɪbekhubekhaufɪtinɪtʃʼahaallisaammodallenɪafanɪinkʼabatunamɪwoɪhodʒatudʒabennaarɡatanamɪwoɪinhodʒannetissetaha?adonɪnamaɪdʒeftɪammodubinɪdansanɪnamaɡammatʃiftɪnamɪduɡadʒalaufɪkʼadʒeltʃaammokaranɪtʃʼahaubitʃaworraballesanamɪwomaɪnɡunnewanbarbaduinarɡatuammonamɪdʒabatehodʒatuwoɪhorataduɡanɪkaradʒirennatɪammotʃʼahaubunɪkaraduɪsatɪilmɪwobekhuɡorsaabaufɪdaɡa?aammoki??ɪbanɪwollalaufɪinfudatunamɪduɡadʒetʃaufɪtinɪwandansaarɡataammodartitʃɪlolabarbadanamɪarabaufɪkʼorkʼoratulubuufɪtissaammonamɪafanɪɪnkʼabnebadiufɪtinɪdufanamɪwomaɪnɡunneatohaɡafeduwanhoratubarbadeleitɪɪmbahuammonamɪdʒabatehodʒatuwanfedutʃʼahaufainarɡatanamɪduɡadaradubatʃudʒibaammodubinɪtʃʼahaubitʃawantʃʼahaerafokotɪduɡanɪnamakʼadʒelakʼorkʼoratɪammotʃʼahaubunɪnamadabaɡalafatɪnamɪɡarɪkawomaɪnkʼamneduresaufɪtoltʃaammokaɡarɪkahorɪkʼabuhi??esaufɪtoltʃaduresɪhorɪufɪtinɪlubuufɪbasaammohi??esaɪrawontɪfudanɪɪndʒirtunamɪduɡaakaɪfsaifsaammotʃʼahaubitʃɪakaifselilɪpisedamaki??ibɪɡarɡalamalewomanuɪndufuammokʼaromɪɡorsaɪradufahorinɪatinɪhodʒateitɪindanfinɪ?osusɪradumataammohorinɪatinɪitɪdɪbamtearɡatesihora?owontɪatinɪhereɡatesitahudideɡaratɪsihamataammo?owontɪatinɪhereɡatesiɡutamtedʒɪrennasitatɪnamɪɡorsafudatʃudiduɡarɡalaufɪtinɪdufaammonamɪɡorsafudatuebaarɡatabarsɪsanɪkʼaroburkʼadʒɪrennataboladuakesasibaftukʼalbinɪdansanɪsalanɪnamaduftɪammonamɪnamɪinduɡefannekarabadikesadʒiranamɪwobekhuatowomaintoltʃineduratuhereɡaammodallenɪafanɪinkʼabatunamɪerɡaɪnɡunne?oerɡatanɪdɪbanɪnamatɪdufaammonamɪerɡaɡutuwoldakʼɪsanɪdufanamaɡorsadiduhi??umafɪtʃʼahaeratɪdakʼabaammokaɡorsafudatuɡudinnaarɡatawanbarbadanɪarɡatʃanɪakamɪdansaammodalletʃʼahaubuiradebɪtinɪɡudoitɪdʒabatɪnamɪkʼarowaheltʃukʼarotahaammonamɪdallewaheltʃudibaarɡataɡarɡalɪtʃʼahaubitʃahordofaammonamɪduɡahormataarɡatanamadansahorinɪɪsaakhakhowanɪɪsaleindakʼabaammohorinɪtʃʼahaubitʃakanamaduɡatahaobrukʼotɪɪnkʼamnetasilahi??esɪkʼotatesaɡaleɪraarɡatutʃʼahaubitʃɪdabsekʼotatʃudowanamɪilmaufɪdaneinkʼadʒeltʃineilmasunɪindʒalatuammonamɪilmaufɪdʒalatukʼadʒeltʃetɪɡorsanamɪduɡawanɲateduɡuɪndabuammotʃʼahaubitʃɪwanɲateduɡuɪnkʼabunɪtinɪkʼaronɪnamakʼubsiftɪammoɡowanɪkʼutumaballesitɪnamɪkʼadʒelanɪabowakʼasodataammonamɪkʼadʒelumaɪnkʼamneisatufatadallenɪdubɪderateharkabi??atinɪufɪɡetɪammokʼarodubumaɪsatɪisakʼorkʼorata?okʼotɪ?olafanɪkʼotatuɪnkʼamnekhodonɪtanteduwaammonamɪsanɡalafanɪkʼotatukʼabuakadansamɪdanɪarɡatekhodoɡutanamɪduɡa?oduɡa?amatanɪdaraindubatuammodartitʃɪ?oduɡa?amatanɪdaratʃʼahaalladubataki??ɪbanɪdandaekʼaromainarɡatuammobekhanɪ?osuwobaratadalleirafaɡadɪwansibarsiftuɪnkʼabdunamɪwoɪbekhuwantahubekhatanafɪkʼaromakʼabadalledallumumaɪsatɪisasobadallenɪtʃʼahaubutoltʃituwomatuɪndartuammonamɪdansanɪararamabarbadaabumatɪɡarahamennafɪɡammadaufilebekhanamɪdɪbinɪdandaewanɪsakesaɪmbekhuatomanɪnamaduɡaoledʒukatʃʼahaubitʃadʒiɡakoblɪhodʒdʒaɡarɪɡarahamennafadossa?oɡammatʃuɪnkʼamnelalalaɪndabdutʃʼahaubitʃɪwanɪsamalearɡatanamɪdansalenɪwomadansaɪsamalearɡatadallenɪwantʃʼahaufainduɡefatɪammonamɪwobekhuedʒataufɪeɡatanamɪkʼaronɪufɪkʼorkʼoratewanhamtukesabudidaammodallenɪwomai??alearɪfatewotoltʃitɪnamɪmiradikʼadallanewandallenɪtoltʃitutoltʃaammonamɪkʼaronɪobsumanɪtanamɪbekhaɪnkʼamnewandallumaɪsatɪmalearɡataammonamɪbekhanɪbekhumaufɪɡulahubatʃadaratanamɪtʃʼahaubukʼabunamaduɡakʼadʒeladuratɪsalanɪdʒilbɪfatanamadibɪi??alinɪhi??esanamɪollaisalenɪɪnfeduammoduresɪdʒallowanɪhedukʼabanamɪnamadibɪtufatunamadabatɪammonamɪhi??esanahunamaebatɪnamawandansahodʒatubi??itɪdʒalatesalfatifɪammonamɪwanhamtutoltʃuwollalatoltʃahudʒinɪhodʒatanɪtʃʼahauftɪwoɪnamabatɪammonamɪwomainhodʒanneufumataehasauɪnumahi??omatanamɪkʼaronɪhodʒatehoritɪbahaammodallenɪdallumaufɪtinɪhafanamɪduɡa?amatanɪ?oduɡadubatelubunamabasaammo?oinnɪdaradubatenamaballesanamaabowakʼasodatuɪsafɪidʒollenɪisalenɪfullaitɪbatukʼabdɪsodanɪabowakʼasodatanɪmadadʒirennatinɪnamaduftɪakaakasinɪnamɪtururaseneɪndoneɡudinnɪha??unamainnɪmohatuɪradufa?onamɪɪndʒirreinnɪlenɪɡudinnasunɪɪnkʼabuufumalafatɪhafa?oatinɪnamamiraɡudatateatinɪkʼaroammo?oatinɪmiradɪkʼateufumadallumatebɪ??aɡarsiftanamɪhereɡadansakʼabunafalefa??akʼabaammodɪbinɪakumadukubanamaɲatenamafitɪna hamadʒibaammohereɡadansaindʒalatanamɪkaradabatinɪwoɪhoratuworraufɪballesaammonamɪɡumbodʒibuindʒɪratanamɪduɡahereɡetɪwoɪdubataammonamɪtʃʼahaubuhereɡamalelafumakaehamennatʃʼahaalladubataabowakʼɪnamatʃʼahaubukʼabuɪrafaɡodʒiraammokadatʃanamaduɡaindaɡa?afulɪɡammadakʼabunamadɪbileinɡammatʃisaodunɪdansalenɪɡaramidasitɪnamɪɡorsafudatukʼarotahanamɪwobaratʃudiduufumaufitɪdʒalataammonamɪɡorsafudatubekhadarataabowakʼasodatʃanɪkʼaromadaratʃanamɪɡudinnabarbaduufɪɡudɪsitɪlakisumaleatonamɪwoɪmalatelemalɪsuninɪwakʼumanɪkʼadʒelanamɪkaraufɪtʃʼahaufakʼadʒelasehaammoabowakʼɪhereɡanamatʃʼahaufaɪmbekhawantoltʃitutʃʼahaufaabowakʼairake?adɪdubahereɡɪkanketʃʼahauftɪsiɡutamaabowakʼɪwanmɪdasetʃʼahaufawoumafɪmɪdasetʃʼahaubɪtʃaleakaballesufɪumeabowakʼɪki??ɪbatʃʼahaufaɪndʒibabekhainnɪworraakasɪsunɪtʃʼahaufainɡarɡaltʃanamɪwakʼadʒalatesalfatufɪararsaisairaarɡatanamaabowakʼasodatutɪtʃʼahaubuɪraɡoranamɪwanabowakʼaɡammatʃisatʃʼahaallatoltʃuɲapaɪsalewoldakʼanɪnaɡa?anɪwolinɪtanɪnamɪ?owandikʼokaraduɡatinɪarɡatenamahorɪhedukaradabatinɪarɡateiradʒiranamɪɡaraufɪtinɪwoɪhereɡaammonamɪkaradansatɪisakʼadʒeltʃuwakʼumaha??unɪkʼaromawakʼɪkennefinɪdubɪmuramuranɪisalenɪkʼadʒeltuabowakʼɪwanwoinɪbɪmanɪmisanafɪdundumalekʼadʒeltunamanɪindabsinefedaha??otɪwandabakalafakesatɪtoltʃanɪdɪkʼoleinobsituwontɪakanatifɪwontɪfinnaha??unɪnamanɪfidudʒabesaduɡatʃʼahaallaha??unɪdubɪduɡafedaammallenamaduɡasunɪdubatuleindʒalataeɡɪha??unɪdallanedotɪnamaɪnoltuammokʼaronɪsosobetɪisaɡammatʃisaɡammadɪha??unamadʒɪrennaebitɪisadumansaɡannafakatɪbekhafɪkʼaromɪkʼarsifɪworkʼɪiranamadʒirakaranɪnamɪkʼadʒelanɪdemuhamennaɪraɡoratanafɪkaraɡulademtulaladɪlubuufɪbasɪufɪsadɪtinɪbaditɪnamaɡesitɪki??ibɪlenɪduanɪnamaɡahanamɪhi??esɪkaufɪinɡudimneki??ɪbahorɪsamekʼodatuiraɡomanamɪwanbaratudʒabesuwandansanɪbahanamɪabowakʼaduɡefatulenɪebakʼabakʼaronɪbekhaufɪtinɪɡurrabafatadubumaɪsamioftunɪnamaufɪɡuladebisakʼaromɪnamɪkʼabumadadʒirennatɪammonamɪdallewobarsisuufumalafatɪhafanamɪwobekhuhereɡedubatadʒetʃɪworralenɪufɪɡulanamadebisadubinɪdansanɪakadamnamɪoftɪmɪanɪɪsiafanitɪkʼuntuloftenafasimidasitɪnamɪbelaufɪdowadʒedehudʒɪhodʒatudʒabatehodʒatatʃʼahaubitʃɪkaranamanɪballesubarbadadubinɪisalenɪɡubdenamaballesitɪnamɪhamanɪnamahamatuhamaufɪtinɪnamawoltɪnakʼedʒallowanileɡarɡarɪbasanamɪdɪbanɪdemudʒallowanɪufɪsobebadinɪitɪdufanamailasitɪkʼisesitɪtʃʼahainɪnatueɡadɪnamɪsunɪhamennaɡarasikʼabanamɪlububulearrɪbasenamaduɡakawakʼɪebisemiraɡudinnɪdʒannomairadʒiranamɪobsaɡudanamadiraheduhadedabsatuiradʒiranamɪhitabufatewanitɪdemulalaammowontɪtʃʼahauftɪabowakʼanɪtatɪnamanaɡa?anɪkʼitaɡoɡesaɲatutɪnamamanaufɪkesatɪdʒilatolfatedʒilasunɪkesatɪwoldiduiradʒiratɪssenɪwoɪbetuilmaseseɡawomaɪnɡunnemohateobole?anɪɪsawolinɪhorɪdaltɪworkʼifɪkʼarsɪibɪdanɪbassanɪilalanɪabowakʼɪlenɪakasumaɡaranamalalanamɪhamanɪwanhamtutʃʼahaakʼasaki??ibalenɪki??ibatʃʼahaakʼasanamɪhi??esakoblunamawakʼaisaumetufatunamabadɪnamadibɪfeduufilebadɪinhankʼatuakumailmɪabaufɪtinɪkhorunamɪdʒarellenɪakhakhowanɪufɪtinɪkhoradubinɪdansanɪdalleinfakatuki??ibɪlenɪnamaɡurrakʼabuinfakatunamɪnamaɡumbesuwannamasunɪfalfalewanfedutʃʼahaufairaarɡatuufɪsehanamɪwollalabɪranamademunamanaɡa?abarbaduammonamɪhalofudunamawanhamtubarbadedʒalanɪufɪlenɪwoldabunɪnamɪwobekhudʒetʃatokonɪwobarataammodalleulenɪdibatokolenɪwoɪimbarsiftunamatʃʼahaubitʃawanhamtubarbaduwanhamtuisaɪdʒesaitɪerɡanɪfullanamadalletaewanakaɪndʒirrehodʒatuarɡanɪnamaɡordʒamaɪlmanɪdʒalafɪtanɪarɡutɪiradʒira?onamɪwandansawanhamtunɪdebisehamennɪhaɡumadʒirumanaɪsakesaɪmbahuwoldɪdanɪnamɪkʼarawoldiduharotʃʼahaabtefakatɪtanafɪarɪfadɪdubɪsunɪkʼabanesɪabowakʼɪnamanamaduɡaɡulademudabsufɪ?okhanɪnamanamahamabasuledɪkʼoleɪnfeduhorinɪwoɪbaratʃadʒedanɪdalletɪbasanɪkainnɪufiftukʼalbɪɪnkʼamnemalɪbahadʒallowanɪ?otʃʼahaufawolɪdʒalatɪobolesɪ?oatinɪɡarɡalakʼabdusiinkʼarkʼareobolesamanɪnamumakʼalbɪɪnkʼamnetʃʼahaallatɪɡatɪnamadibɪfudeufiraka?anamɪwoldidafedutʃʼahaububarbadanamɪɡu??atʃʼahaufaufɪsadudibaufitɪbarbadanamɪwanhamtuhereɡewomahamtudubatubadɪmalewandansainarɡatuilmɪdallitʃɪababotʃeɡara?akaɡammadɪfa??asikennaammomirahamennɪnafasiɲatadʒarsɪtʃʼahaubitʃɪdossanɪɡumbofudateakasinɪduɡanɪbadɪnamɪwoɪbekhukʼaromatʃʼahaallaɡulademaammodallenɪwantokotʃʼahaallairaɪntetuolumaɡadɪmarailmɪdallenɪababotʃehadaɡara?akanamɪwomai??akinɪkakarramataitɪmuranɪdabanamɪduɡaɡulademukadananɪlenɪdɪkʼoledansanitɪnamɪwobekhuwanufɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufataeindubatunamɪhubatʃakʼabulafumakaeakanumatɪindubatudallelenɪ?oafanɪkʼabatetʃʼahaaliftetetunamawobekhusehanɪnamɪnamanɪwolɪindaɡennetʃʼahauftɪufoufumatʃʼahaalladʒalatainnɪwankʼadʒeltubi??itɪaɡartutʃʼahaufaɪmormadallenɪhubatʃafɪhubatʃadabalewomairaɪnkʼabuammoakakʼaromakʼabutʃʼahaallaufɪɡarsisufedatʃʼahaerafɪtʃʼahaubunɪwolɪwahelanamasalaɪnkʼamneinɡo?esanɪdubinɪnamamadakʼaromatɪɪsinɪkʼileakabarinɪammallekʼulloakabɪsanɪɡalananamawo?akeiratʃʼahaɪsanɪnamaduɡakʼabuduɡadowɪtinɪdabadallewomoromtudanumalanɪdallenɪafanumaufɪtinɪufɪballesitetururakesaufɪbuftɪhamtɪafanitɪɡudomɪoftɪtanafɪnamɪlɪkʼimseɡaratɪkʼabatanamɪwomaɪnɡunnewahelanamawo?akuabowakʼɪdofɪdʒabdunamɪduɡadeteitɪbahufakataammoduresɪwanhorinɪɪsaakanabodʒabdudertumarsanɪdɪranɪdʒaranɪisabasusehanamaufɪinɡudimnenamɪinsalfataammonamɪufɪolfudukarabadɪkesadʒiraatowomanamanɪɪndʒennekʼaratʃʼahaakʼasɪ?oakasɪtahubateatinɪdallenamatufatu?oatinɪfa??adabdelubuufɪdindɪsiteɪnumadotaammo?odɪndisubateinfa??itanamɪwobekhuɡu??atʃʼahaufakurfodʒiraakakʼalbɪtokonɪwobaratu?oatinɪnamaɡudanɪdubatʃufetewoɡesifɪakasɪtʃʼahaalladandetedubatanɪnamɪkʼarakorakesatɪnamahɪmatuwanduɡakʼabufakatahaɡanamɪinnɪhɪmatukanɪkaewoɪɡafatutɪhodʒdʒanamɪɡuɡurdanɪlamakorakesatɪwoldabehɪtabusanɪtʃʼahaallatɪworraɡarɡarɪbasaobolesakankekʼarkʼarɪinnɪakumanabodʒabdudɪranɪdʒaranɪsikʼorkʼorataammo?oɪsanɪwoldabdanɪinnɪsiseratebalbalaufiledurabahusidowanamɪdubumaufɪtinɪdue?okhanɪdʒɪratadubinɪatinɪdʒetusiɪdʒeftɪ?okhanɪsidʒiresitɪtanafɪwandubɪtanteirasitɪɡadufahamtufɪtoltuletʃʼahaufafudadɪnamɪnadenɪfude?awandansataheabowakʼɪlenɪinebɪsafɪhi??esɪ?onamanɪdubatulanumadubataammoduresanamanɪloladʒalanɪnamahaɡɪtokoobolesaleiranamadʒirtɪammohaɡɪtokonamaballesitɪhi??esatʃʼahaubuinkʼamnetɪdalleki??ibduiraɡomanamɪhubatʃaɪnkʼamnekawoɪow laɡulademaammowontɪkuninɪtʃʼahauftɪdabanamɪmalakʼabuwanheduarɡataammonamɪarɪfatewotoltʃuwanɲateduɡuleɪndabahorinɪkaratʃʼahaubutinɪarɡatanɪɪmbadaammoatoɪmbanneboladuakesasibusatʃʼahaubitʃɪkaraduɡadidehamennumaufɪtinɪufɪballesanamawollalakʼabukaranɪisalenɪkʼadʒelanitɪammonamɪwomai??akinɪkarakʼadʒelakesadʒirafullanitɪdɪbditɪnamaɡarɡaltʃɪtunɪmanatakatɪwolinɪɡalanɪnamabɪrabaheɡosetɪɡalutɪiradʒiratʃʼahaubitʃɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufahamennabarbadainnɪnasunamatokoleɪnkʼabuhodʒdʒaki??ɪbanɪɡarɡalaarɡatunamɪwoɪimbennelenɪirawobaratakʼaronɪwanbarsɪsanɪirawoɪbaratawakʼɪduɡawanworratʃʼahaubitʃakesatɪtoltʃanɪtʃʼahaufabekheworraɪsasunɪballesanamabohahi??esatʃʼahaakʼasudideatoinnɪkʼarkʼarsaboheleisaintʃakʼasanɪnamasitɪdallanuwontɪdossatɪkennanifɪintʃalɪsiftɪ?okorakesatɪduɡadubatanɪnamɪduɡainɡammadaammotʃʼahaubitʃɪinɡunɡumanamɪkarahubatʃaɪraɡoreduetɪbolaekheratɪɡalanamɪmatʃɪdʒalatuinhɪ??omataammallenamɪdadifɪdadadʒalatuhaɡumadʒiruwomainhoratunamɪtʃʼahaububadɪinnɪnamadibɪtinɪdufufeduufɪtinɪdufafullanitɪdɪbditɪhaɡumadʒirtuteteɡunɡumtunɪwoltɪɡalanɪ?obɪrademanɪalatɪɡalanɪiradʒirtɪnamɪwoɪbekhusaɡaledansaolke?ataammodallenɪhorɪufɪakumaarɡatunɪɲatefitanamanasufɪduɡaɡulademulubunɪderatenamɪlenɪɪsasalfataabanɪdulakʼaronɪdiranabodʒabdunɪdʒaranɪhadedabsatenaboworrɪdabatuletʃʼahaabseballesa?oatinɪdibakesaufɪbusuɪnfenearabaufɪtissɪki??ibanaɡarsisɪanɪnɪlenɪnamaufɪsadeufɪolfudenamadibɪtufatusiɡarsisanamɪlafanɪwomahodʒatʃuɪnfeneufumaufɪɪdʒesainnɪɡu??akanatʃʼahaufawomadaraufɪtʃʼahaallataehereɡaammonamɪduɡawomanamaindowatuɡaratokonɪwonamakennasorioworratʃʼahaubuabowakʼɪɪndʒibakesuma?oworrɪhereɡahamanɪbasufainnɪakahamadʒibanamɪdaraduɡesuɪmbadaammodʒetʃɪnamawohubatuɪmbadunamɪduɡaufɪindarefatuammotʃʼahaubitʃɪwantʃʼahaufakesaufɪtoltʃa?oabowakʼɪsidʒibewontɪtokolenɪtaatinɪkʼarkʼarsaɪraarɡatuɪndʒirtukʼaromatananɪbekhatananɪmalalletananɪnamɪfardanɪɪndulaammokanamadabsatʃisuabowakʼaɡurrɪdansanɪhorɪɡudairadʒiramakʼanɪdansanɪworkʼɪ?okhanɪkʼarsileiradʒiraduresafɪhi??esaleabumawakʼatɪumeakananɪworrɪwolfakatanamɪwobekhu?odibaitɪdufuarɡuduraɡoraammonamɪwoɪɪmbennedibakanakesaseneeɡeufiɡabaabowakʼasodadɪufɪinɡudɪsinɪdubaduromafɪsalafɪdʒɪrennaarɡata?oatinɪlubutedʒalateɡufufɪkʼoratɪkaratɪworratʃʼahaububallesituɪraɡorɪidʒollenɪ?oatinɪkarakʼadʒelabarsifteɡafadʒartuleɪraɪnɡortuduresɪhi??esamohatanamɪnamadibɪɡatɪirafudulenɪ?atisseɪsatahenamɪsaɲɪdabafatʃasebadɪmuratadebiedandaenamaɪndabsunamɪtolanɪhi??esasaɡaleufɪkʼoduebaarɡataki??ibaufɪbɪraɡussɪdubamoromafɪwoldɪdafɪarabɪdebiesiɪnɡahunamaɡaranɪɪsakʼulkʼullokadubɪdansadubatutɪha??udʒalataabowakʼɪki??ibadareseakasinɪduɡadʒabesaabebɪwomaɪnɡunneɲentʃatɪnaɲatadʒedeworrabahudidaafanɪʃarmutakʼileakabolanamɪabowakʼɪitɪdallanɪkesasenaidʒollenɪidʒollumafɪwanakaɪndʒirretoltʃitewo?akitɪammowontɪisɪmɪdasaulenamɪduresahorɪkenneammohi??esadabseakasinɪufɪwohoratueɡeinhɪ??omatawankʼaronɪdʒedeɪsanɪbarsisatʃʼahaakʼasadubɪworrabaradaɡarakesake?adaindedinanamatʃʼahaufatɪhasaaninɪakaɪsanɪabowakʼaduɡefatanɪfedatanafɪdʒetʃakʼarokanatʃʼahaufaammaɪsanɪbarsisaaninɪ?adʒetʃasodomakakʼaronɪdʒedeisanitafekabekhafɪɡorsadansakʼabuammallekadubɪduɡakʼadʒeltuɪsanɪbarsisudubaakananɪ?oɪsanɪerɡanɪdubɪduɡabarbadaisaninɪdʒedanɪɡartanɪɪtinɪɡaltanɪnamɪkunɪhi??esadʒeteindabsinɪnamaɡadisakorakesatɪnamadubatufɪɪnkʼamneindabsinɪabowakʼatɪworradubatenamaworradabsuleballesanamamiradikʼaka?osudallanudʒalaintolfatinɪheɡerɪfinnaworrabarateɪradebinɪsidibdɪɡatɪnamadibɪanatɪsibasadʒeteufirainka?inɪheɡerɪ?oatinɪbasudadabdesiretelesidʒalafudanɪseralafakaababotɪtesanɪdurɪmidasiteindɪɡinɪnamahudʒɪdansatoltʃunaɡarsisɪdubaanɪnɪlenɪnamanamatʃʼahaufairadansakaha??ulehodʒatusiɡarsisahodʒdʒanamaɡudinnakʼabuwolinɪɡololfatanɪwanɡololfatanɪsunɪakadansalalɪ?oatinɪnamaɡudowoɲatutateufɪeɡadɪɡaraɡulaimbadinɪsaɡaledansainnɪsinɪɡololtʃusunɪsabdofteinfɪtinɪheɡerɪinnɪsiilalatafadallofteduromabarbadadʒeteufɪinɡarɡaltʃinɪheɡerɪhorinɪkankekolabaseakarisabarsise?osusirabadanamawomaɪraɪmbanekʼotʃotʃamasaɡaleɪsaiɲatinɪatoinnɪsaɡalemɪoftusikenneleitɪindarainɪinnɪkaɡaraɪnkʼamneafaninɪkotɪɲadɪduɡɪsinɪdʒedaatinɪwanrefuɲatekanɪdɪdidedubɪdansarefudʒetenɪtanɪleɡabitadallekʼaromakankeinɡarsɪsinɪheɡerɪsiɡo?esesitufataseralafakadurɪdʒarolenɪmidasiteindɪɡinɪ?okhanɪobruhi??esaleirainfudatinɪwontɪakanatifɪnamɪworrakaltʃuabowakʼawansibarsɪsanɪtʃʼahaakʼasɪkʼalbefadɪsodateɪlmanɪdanuillakɪsinɪulenɪlubuinɪdʒeftu?oulenɪdanteɪsumaduairadowartailmakɪ??a?oatinɪkʼarotateaninɪɡudoɡammada?oatinɪdubɪkʼadʒeltudubatuɡaranɪkɪ??ainkʼɪlɪtamatʃʼahaubitʃainhaltʃinɪammohodʒdʒatʃʼahaufaabowakʼasodadɪ?oakasɪtatewandansatɪbatailmakɪ??atʃʼahaakʼasɪkʼalbefadɪkarakʼadʒelaɡulademtudʒabesɪnamafarsoduɡematʃaufɪnamasaɡaleɲateɪnkʼumnewahelaintahinɪwontɪakanatifɪsabdifɪnamɪmatʃaulenɪinhɪ??omata?owontumanɪatinɪhodʒatuwansunɪtʃʼahaallatatedɪotutʃʼahaarkʼɪnakʼataabasidaletʃʼahaakʼasɪhadatanteatoɪsinɪdʒarteleintufatinɪduɡakʼaromabaratʃakʼalbɪwontɪkuninɪtʃʼahauftɪwanarɡatʃumalanɪdabuhɪmmalleabanɪnamaduɡainɡammadailmɪkʼaronɪabaɡammatʃisaabetifɪhateɡammatʃisɪakahatɪsidaltesinɪmatʃoftuilmakɪ??anatʃʼahaakʼasɪfanatɪ??aɪrainɡorinɪʃarmutafɪɡara?unɪakaalɡalakaradatuedʒandʒitekʼabdebolakʼilekʼaranamaheduballesitekesasibuftɪenutɪɡaraɡalakʼabaenutɪlalalakʼabaenutɪɡu??atʃʼahaufanamanɪwoldidaenutɪɡu??atʃʼahaufataeɡunɡumaenutɪfa??umatanamadaenuiltɪdɪmatɪwankanatʃʼahaufanamafarsonɪdallefarsoɡosaheduduɡutɪkʼabadadɪdimtutamudunukesatʃʼahaululututahodʒdʒaatinɪlikʼɪmsitusidʒalamɪoftuɪlalteinduɡinɪheɡerɪ?odudeborɪ??ateakawanbofɪsiɲatedotetʃʼahaiftaakawanbutinɪsiɪditeiltɪtantewanmamaaɡartekʼalbinɪtantelenɪhubatʃadabdewandubatuwollaltebopiftaatinɪnamabarinɪdawadʒabdukʼabukesahobolonɪdemukafiteutubaɪsitɪraraufakataatinɪ?anadananɪammowomaɪntane?anadananɪammokʼubaɪnkʼabuaninɪ?omɪdamakʼamefarsodibɪnabusadʒetatʃʼahaubitʃahaltʃitedʒalaintolfatinɪworrɪwomahamtutoltʃutʃʼahaallahereɡadubinɪafanɪworrakesabatutʃʼahauftɪtanamawotoltʃitumanakʼaromafɪbekhanɪ?a?abanɪdʒaranɪnamɪwobekhumanaufɪmihadansaitɪbɪtetɪsuninɪtʃʼahaokhanamɪkʼaromakʼabunamadʒabairrekʼabuiradʒiranamɪbekhakʼabulenɪnamadʒabairadʒirawontɪakanatifɪatinɪatodulaɪndemnemarɪatʃumalteammalleɡorsɪhedunɪatinɪnamairaarɡatuɲapalesidabsatʃisadallenɪhaɡumadʒirtudʒetʃakʼaroinhubatuɪsinɪɡadisakorakesaletɪbetewomaindubatunamahodʒdʒatʃʼahaufawantʃʼahaubumalatudɪbditʃadʒedaninɪdallenɪtʃʼahaubumalewomainheredunamɪlenɪnamanamatufatuɪndʒiba?odibɪsitɪdumannanɪatinɪufɪdʒɪbateatinɪlafaduanamadabanɪɪdʒetʃaɡesanɪlububasɪinsodatinɪatoatinɪwontɪkuninɪhudʒɪti??anitɪaninɪkesaɪmbudʒetelewakʼɪkahereɡanamatʃʼahaufabekhuwansunɪɪnarɡuinnɪkʼarasɪumaeɡudʒirawankanketʃʼahaufaɪmbekhainnɪdubawomaatinɪtoltʃituɡulawansimalesitoltʃailmakɪ??adammɪwandansaɲadɪakumadammɪmɪaekʼuntulauakasumakʼaromɪlenɪwoɪsibahakʼaromabarbadɪdubawontɪtʃʼahauftɪsitoltɪakatʃʼahaubitʃamalatemananamaduɡatʃʼahaabsesamatuintahinɪnamɪduɡaatomarohedudʒɪɡeleɪnumakaammotʃʼahaubitʃɪɪnumabada?oɲapɪkankeɡufatedʒiɡeɡarɡalakesasenuinɡammadinɪ?owanakasɪsunidʒetekʼilɪtamteabowakʼɪheɡerɪhereɡakankebekhesidʒibenamakanɪlakisafanamɪtʃʼahaubu?adasiinarɡinɪ?okhanɪworraleinhaltʃinɪtʃʼahaubitʃɪboroɪnkʼabuwandabatuleɪnkʼabuilmakɪ??aabowakʼasodadɪha??ulesalfadɪnamaworrakanalamanɪdiduwahelatolfateɡulaindeminɪworrɪakasɪsunɪ?osubadaatinɪakawakʼafɪha??unɪdandanɪsiballesanɪdɪkʼoleinheredudʒetʃakanaleworrumakʼarotɪdʒededʒarsɪɡadisakorakesatɪdubinɪnamairatʃʼahaisudansanitɪ?oinnɪnamawollalakʼabunɪwollalaɪnkʼabdudʒedenamɪtʃʼahauftɪisadʒibeisaabaraammodʒarsɪnamawollalakʼabuwollalaitɪmuruebafɪɡurradansalearɡatanamɪduɡasitɪdubatudʒalakankekaduɡatɪhaɡaobrukʼotateakadansamidafatewanɪraɲatuarɡatutɪmanaindʒaratinɪfa??umatanaduɡanamabatewannamadibɪindubatinɪ?okhanɪhamtutokoleindubatinɪammalleaninɪwomainnɪnatoltʃeɪsaletoltʃeakasinɪhalobafadaindʒedinɪaninɪobrumidanɪtifɪtatsabibutanamitʃalafadallitʃatokotinɪdatubaheobrusunɪtamukhakʼoratɪbafteharamanɪbadedakhanɪɪsinɪmarsanɪdʒaranɪlenɪtʃʼahauftɪdʒiɡearɡeaninɪakanumatɪedʒeobrusunɪɪlalehereɡeirawoɪbaradeammoatoatinɪraftuhi??umtɪdufteakaʃiftasihatɪkuninɪmammasadibɪha??unɪsolomoninɪmammakhekadʒarɪmanaha??u?udakahetsekiadʒedanɪkesahodʒatutafenuwakʼawaninnɪwodossufɪɡudimnaammoha??otawanɪsinɪwoɪnamabarsiftenamadɪdufɪulfesinanamɪdandaehereɡaha??uɪmbekhuhereɡɪɪsanuraolfaɡodʒiraakumawakʼaolfaɡate?okhanɪakumadimmubɪsanɪɡadɪfaɡatakʼarsɪbassɪkʼulkʼullesɪakatumtitʃɪwandansanɪmɪdasunamatʃʼahaubitʃaha??umaladaubɪrabasɪakafinnɪinnɪnamafidukaduɡatahufullafullanɪtuninɪtanamaɡudatɪarmakaɪdʒedanɪsitʃʼahaersanɪ?oufinɪsi?amanɪkotɪaramadurataɪsinɪdʒedanɪiradʒirtɪwanakadansaaɡarteinhubatinɪɡadisakoratɪinɡesinɪ?onamɪdɪbinɪdufedubɪtedaresesitʃʼahaersemanɪtata?onamanɪdubɪɪratɪwoldabdanɪatonamutuwolɪinɡesineisanumanɪhobafadaakanamɪdɪbinɪwoldabakesanɪsunɪindaɡenneheɡerɪnamɪakaatinɪwomaindossinɪsiarɡeakasinɪtʃʼahaerɪkankedɪdatɪɡabahadubinɪakumaisɪmalteɡuladubatanɪakumawanworkʼɪɪramidasanɪkʼarsinɪbarresanɪtʃʼahaokhanɪdʒirtɪɡorsɪnamɪwobekhunamaisadaɡauɡorsukʼubeworkʼɪtifɪ?okhanɪfa?aworkʼɪtʃʼahautʃulukʼairadʒiranamɪdansanɪ?oerɡatanɪerɡamɪdasunamaisaerɡatusunɪakumabɪsanɪnamaadukesamɪdanɪmurukʼabanesanɪnafaɪsakʼabanesanamɪkʼarawosikennadʒedeammoeɡesidowatudumansafɪbubeboka?aɪnkʼamnefakatanamɪobsakʼabukaha??usosobudandaeɪsaleatoinnɪkʼaraakadʒabadidakʼabateleufɪɡuladebisadammamiaɡulaɲateufiradabarsiteindɪdɪɡinɪammohaɡumaɲadɪufɪeɡadɪɡu??atʃʼahaufamanaollaketɪtinɪimarinɪheɡerɪinnɪsihɪfatesidʒibanamɪwandaratinɪnamahɪmatuakumaɡoradefɪbokufɪtɪ?akʼarakʼabduhamanamɪnamadabuɪnkʼamneiraufɪka?enamaɪlkanɪtʃotʃoatinɪwoɲatu?okhanɪnamamilanafatenɪlafatɪedʒandʒatademufakatanamɪnamaɡaranɪhamatetɪsirbunamaɡu??adamotʃawo?aisaɪrabasuka?okhanɪsodamadadɪmtutɪriɡufakata?owankanatoltʃɪtefɪatinɪtʃʼahaileowitumataɡubatɪɡurteabowakʼɪlenɪsiebisaakumabubenɪmɪrɡaboka?anɪduftuhamtɪnamɪnamahammatulenɪdallansunɪduftɪfullanitɪdɪbditɪnamaɡarɡaltʃɪtunɪwolinɪɡalanɪnamabirabaheɡosetɪɡalutɪiradʒiranamɪodudansalafafaɡotɪduftudaɡa?unamabɪsanɪkʼabanaohodʒdʒadebotuduɡufakatanamɪdansanɪdubɪnamahamaɡuladebiuakamadoturesanɪballesanɪ?okhanɪelahadaitɪnakʼanɪdʒiradammɪɲatanɪufiradabarsanɪhamaammalleakasumanamɪakaɡudonamɪisaowisufedulenɪdansanitɪ?oatinɪdallansuinobsinɪatinɪakumadiranaboɲapanɪufiradowuɪnkʼamnedʒirtaakumakʼabantɪbonahaɡa??ainfakanne?okhanɪbokenɪlenɪfullamɪdanɪmuranɪinfakanneulfɪnnɪlenɪdalleinfakanneakumaburɪ?aɡodantu?okhanɪakumaworabatɪbariftuabarsɪsihimmallinɪsiinkʼabatuakumafardalɪtʃonɪdananɪ?okhanɪɡanɡeluɡamanɪdalleleakasumadananɪulenɪkʼadʒeltʃumalanɪ?onamɪdubɪakaɪndʒirresiɡafateatɪnɪlenɪdubumaakasɪsunɪdebɪftefɪakumaɪsadalletatanamadubɪakaɪndʒirresiɡafateatɪnɪlenɪdubumaakaɪndʒirredebɪsifɪdubanamɪsiɡafatesuninɪakawomaɪmbenneufɪarɡa?oatinɪdalleerɡatedamsanahimɪdʒetenɪatinɪakumanamaufɪɡarɡaltʃemilaufirakutudʒirtamammasɪdalleakumanamamilanafatewomaimbanefinɪdemudʒiranamɪdalleɡudiseowiseakumanamadakhaɡullubanɪdarbanɪɡullubakesatɪhidudʒiradallenɪmammakhuakumanamafarsoduɡematʃaekʼoratɪharkakesafudatudʒiranamɪnamumaarɡutʃʼahaufahereɡamalehudʒɪkʼoruufumaɡarɡalasenenamasunileɡarɡalakesabusanamakʼarointahinɪkaammokʼaroufɪsehudalleratutɪiradʒiraabebɪmafɪmanaɪmbaneinnɪɲentʃasodataakumabalbaltɪmikhɪkɪlatɪedʒitutʃotʃotuakasumaabebɪsireirabudidetaekesatɪtʃotʃotʃoanamɪɡarɪlafebadesaɡaleɡaratɪɲatuleafanɪke?atʃudadabanamɪlafanɪwomaɪnɡunnewannamatorbakamalamaltekʼabuirawobekhuufɪsehanamɪdubɪisainɡahinɪkesabuakumanamasarekarademtutʃʼahaeɡurrakʼabudʒiranamɪsobenamaballeseammoeɡeufumatabadadʒedumarataworanahamanamaidʒesunɪtabatufakatakʼoranɪmaleɪbidɪɪndamafullahamtɪindʒɪrrelewoldabɪɪndʒiruakumabarbadɪibɪdatʃʼahailebobesu?okhanɪkʼoranɪlenɪɪbidabobesanɪnamɪdɪbanɪdemulenɪwoldidaowisadubinɪnamawohamatuakadammamɪoftɪ?olikʼɪmsanɪɪsinɪakamɪnamatɪmɪoftɪdubinɪsobataatinɪwanhamtuɡarakʼabdunɪdossituakaokotefarataalalumutanɪmidasanɪdʒirtɪnamɪdartitʃɪafanɪnamatɪmɪdaɡeammoɡaraufɪkesawanhamtunamatɪhereɡadubinɪisatʃʼahauftɪdansafakatɪammoatinɪwansunɪinduɡefatinɪwontɪakanatifɪɡaraɪsawomahamtutʃʼahaallatɪɡuteinnɪheɡerɪhamennaufɪdossaammonamɪtʃʼahauftɪwanhamtuinnɪtoltʃuɪnarɡanamɪbolakʼa??anenamakʼotuufumakesabuaammallenamadakhaɡaraɪraɡaka?uledakhumasunitɪtʃʼahaarasanamadʒɪbanɪsɪlaftuɪnumaarabsanɪdubinɪsobalenɪbadinɪnamatɪduftɪnamɪdɪbinɪatokessumaletatehasisadutɪammoatinɪufɪinsadinɪdibɪdallenɪnamatinɪduftumansafɪdakhaleiranamatɪulfatadallansunɪwanhamtuwanwoballesatɪammodɪbinɪwanhaɡasɪɪratɪdubinɪdidesanɪnamanɪɡorsanɪdʒalaladossairadʒirtɪ?oharkɪɲapaketɪsimadeselewomanitɪammodunɡoɲapaketɪufiraeɡadɪnamakʼufakʼabudammɪlenɪitɪimɪauammonamabelakʼabuwontɪhadalenɪitɪmɪoftɪnamɪworraufɪɪrafaɡodʒirusɪmpirremanaisɪirafaɡodʒirtufakatakʼa??afɪdadanɪurɡanɪnamaɡammatʃisaammoɡarɡalɪkʼalbɪsi?akenaɡa?asidowadʒallowanɪtetifɪtaabaketɪindedinɪ?oɡarɡalakesasenteobolesakankekasɪrafaɡodʒirukʼarkʼarsainkadatinɪnamɪollaketɪkasitɪanuobolesakankekafaɡodʒirusunɪirasidʒirailmakɪ??aatinɪ?okʼarotatenaɡammatʃiftadubanamawankɪ??adubatuaninɪ?osunɪwandʒedunɪkʼabanamɪwobekhu?oakaɡarɡalɪitɪdufuarɡuduraɡoraammonamɪwomaɪmbenneeɡɪkesaseneufiɡabanamɪakamaledallaenamafulaimbennenɪanatɪɡatɪsibasadʒeduhorɪɪsaakakʼabdotɪɪrafudumalanɪnamɪɡanamanɪdʒalaufitɪlalabenaɡa?afudelafakasuserumanamaisaabarenɪtinɪdibdɪtinɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufalolademtuakumadimpuɡu??arobadɪmpiftɪnamɪisɪtʃʼahaallɪsɪsitɪitɪɡamenamumabubedowe?okhanɪdadaharkatɪnakʼatedʒiɡudowufakataakumasɪbilɪsɪbiladibɪkʼarunamɪlenɪwoɪwolbarsisa?omukhaodakʼorkʼoratemɪdanɪɪsaɲataammallenamɪabaɪsakʼorkʼoratulenɪɡurradansaarɡataakumaɡandidunamadandanɪbɪsanɪkesatɪarɡanɪakasumaɡaraufɪkesaletɪnamɪakadʒiruufɪarɡadaranɪnamaakumabolaekheradʒirtɪtahaɡumadʒirtuinɡutamneakumakʼarsifɪworkʼɪbassanɪilalanɪakasumaɡurranamahamafɪtolallelalanɪatoatinɪdallebututʃitedanteledallumaɪsadandetekesaɪmbaftulonifɪretantehaɡadandetuakadansakʼorkʼoradɪwontɪakanatifɪhorinɪwanbaratokofadabanɪha??ulenɪhaɡadʒirudʒɪrennaɪntau?ofullaatinɪokha?ahamtefɪbu?onɪdɪbinɪbatenɪdubaammallebu?oɡarairadʒɪrtuletʃʼahaufahamanɪatinɪdandeterɪfensaholɪ?etantetɪbadonɪdatebeseatinɪretanteɡurɡurranɪarɡatelelafanɪbɪtatarenɪirahaftetanɪsifɪworraketifɪdubrasihodʒatuleamesatatɪtʃʼahaubitʃɪatonamɪinɡussineufumanɪbakʼataammonamɪduɡadʒannaakaɲentʃatɪɡotʃitɪtʃʼahaubutoltʃituɡarɡaltenamɪheduisɪmohataammoɡotʃitɪhodʒdʒanamɪkʼaronɪwobekhumohatudʒabatekaindʒɪdʒɪramnenaɡumanɪtetɪnamɪnamamohatukahi??esadabsuboka?atamnakamɪdanɪballesufakatanamɪseraɡulaɪndemneɡolɪtʃʼahaubɪtʃatɪammonamɪseraɡulademuɡolɪɪsaɪntahunamɪwanhamtutoltʃuduɡaɪmbekhuammonamɪabowakʼaɡulademuakadansawanɪsihubatahi??esaduɡaɡulademutɪduresatʃʼahaubitʃairadʒirakaimɪseraɡutunamawobekhuammoɡurbanɪseseɡaɡulademuabaufɪɡurraɪdʒesanamɪɡatɪnamakenneammallekaradabatanɪtirfɪɪrafudatumarɪmarsɪhorɪɪsanamahi??esanahutɪfudata?onamɪseraɡulademudiduwakʼɪkadatʃaɪsaledʒibetʃʼahaakʼasuledidanamɪnamaduɡakʼadʒelasobewanhamtukesabusuufumabolakesaufɪbusaammonamɪtʃʼahaubuɪnkʼamnetakatanawandansadaladuresɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufakʼaroufɪsehaammohi??esɪwobekhuakakʼaromɪɪsasuninɪdaraɪnarɡahodʒdʒanamɪduɡaɡudinnalafanɪfiduarɡatunamɪtʃʼahauftɪinɡammadaammo?onamɪhamanɪlafafidunamɪtʃʼahauftɪindokhatanamɪtʃʼahaubuufɪdossuwomainhoratuammonamatʃʼahaubuufɪhɪmateɪradebiuwakʼɪinnahafɪa??anaɪsatɪkaabowakʼasodatuammonamɪmatadʒabatewodiduɪnumabada?otʃʼahaubitʃɪlafamohatuhi??esɪwantahuɪnkʼabuinnɪakumaɲentʃaɪtanu?okhanɪɡordʒamadutudʒiranamɪdallenɪlafamohatunamadabseɪrrenɪnamabultʃaammonamɪdabadidubarahedulafafidanamɪnamaɪdʒesebolumaufɪkʼotatʃudʒiranamɪtokolenɪɪraindowinɪnamɪduɡaɡulademuwanhamtudʒalabahaammonamɪtʃʼahaubuɡulademudɪramadʒiɡebadanamɪobruufɪkʼotatusaɡaleɪndabuammonamɪwanwomaɪmbaneɡula?auinhɪ??omatanamɪduɡaɡulademuhaɡadʒirutʃʼahaufanaɡa?akʼabaammonamɪ?osuwohoratʃufeduɡarɡalakesasenumaleɪntaunamɪnamafɪlatudansanitɪammodʒarsɪɡarɪɡumbodikʼotokodʒededubɪkesanamairatʃʼahaisaufonɪnama?osuwohoratʃufedaakahi??umtɪisakʼabatuleimbekatu?oatinɪnamaɡorsiteinnɪeɡɪsunɪsobairaɡorsasunɪdʒalatanamɪakanɪtʃʼahaubunitɪdʒedeabafɪhadaufɪɪrawohatuwahelanamawo?akutɪnamɪufonɪwanhamtunɪlafadufaammonamɪabowakʼaduɡefatuwanɡudohoratanamɪhereɡaufɪtʃʼahaallaɡulademudalleammokanamakʼaroɡulademuwanhamtudʒalabahanamɪhi??esawokennuwomaɪndabuammokahi??esalaludiduabarsaheduarɡata?onamɪhamanɪlafamohatubi??atɪbakʼatedokhatɪammo?oisaɡarɡaltʃanɪnamadansatɪdebiemohatanamamatadʒabateɡorsafudatʃudidutakatanaimballesanɪdebieɪnkauhodʒdʒanamɪduɡalafamohatunamɪinɡammadaammo?otʃʼahaubitʃɪlafamohatunamɪɡarɡaleɡunɡumanamɪkʼaromadʒalatuabaufɪɡammatʃisaammonamɪʃarmutaɡulademu ɪsafɪnamɪlamahadisanamatokodabsateufiradowafunnomusensasadinɪdanɪakatabatɪinkutanɪnamɪhi??esɪdandaehi??umakesabaheha??ulafaufɪtaha?okhanɪhɪdansakesabahenamalafafidutahaammohodʒdʒainnɪdʒarumaɪsakesadallaeɡorsanamadiduinnɪhi??esakaimakakʼalbɪkʼabuɪnɡahuaninɪwannamalafatanakesadʒirutʃʼahaufahereɡedʒennanɪakaworrakanakesanamɪkaimatokokahudʒɪha??uɪrafududʒiruarɡenamɪha??unɪfiduheɡerɪmummeɪnkʼabuammo?oinnɪlubudabenamɪwaninnɪtoltʃekʼabateɡalatadebɪsufɪɪndʒirutunɪnɪlenɪwomaɪmbatuserumanamakʼɪllensaɡussutɪhodʒdʒamanawakʼatɪkadatʃudatuufɪeɡadɪ?owobaratʃamanawakʼadateirasidʒirtɪfullaatinɪakaworradallekadarafɪduɡaɡarɡarɪɪmbennesoriobaftuhubatemaleindubatinɪammallehereɡamalewakʼawotoltʃaindʒedinɪinnɪɡubadʒiraatinɪlafadʒirtatanafɪwandʒetʃumaltemaledubɪinderɪsinɪakumaatinɪwanɡudo?adunɪakasumaobdʒuhamtuobdʒataammalleakumadubɪɡudatunɪdallumtɪsitɪɡudatɪ?o?uatinɪwakʼawokakhatekakhusunɪhurrisɪɡutifɪinnɪdallewomairaɪnkʼabutanafɪatinɪwankakhatesunɪɡutifɪfullakakhudandeteɪnɡunnekakhatu?oafanɪkʼabateufirateteirasidʒirtɪarabɪkanketʃʼahaubukesasiimbusinɪakaheɡerɪkakhutantetanaerɡatuwakʼaduratɪimormannemafɪwakʼaufitɪdallansiftamafɪakainnɪhudʒɪatinɪtoltʃituballesuitɪlakiftaatoɡudoobdʒatehudʒɪwomakesaɪndʒirrehodʒate?okhanɪdubɪderatelewakʼasodatʃumaltehodʒdʒaatinɪlafatokokesatɪhi??esadabsanɪduɡafɪkʼadʒelumadowanɪarɡiteimaminɪnamaɡudatʃʼahaufanamaisairadʒɪrutɪtissaammoworralatʃulenamaworrairadʒɪrutɪtissaha??ulenɪwanlaftɪbaftumaleindʒɪratunamɪbesedʒalatuɪnkʼufunamɪduromabarbaduwanfedutʃʼahaufainarɡatutunɪnɪlenɪwomaɪmbatuakumanamɪhorɪɡudakʼabunɪnamaheduɲatʃisatɪrfinɪinnɪwankanaɪrakʼabumanɪaɡartailamalenamɪharkanɪhodʒatu?owandɪkʼofɪɡudoɲatulehɪribadansahalkanɪɪndabuduresɪammoatowanɲatuɡudolekʼabate?adaɪmbuluwontɪhamtunɪtokotaaninɪlafatanakesatɪarɡetananamɪbeseɡudowoɪdʒedeolka?udubamudanɪitɪɡaltewanɪlmanɪɪsaɪradaltuledabanamɪakumakʼullaɡarahadakesabaheakasumalafatanaɪraduaatoinnɪhodʒatewanɡudokʼabateleɡafaduharkumaduwabɪrademaakasɪkʼadʒelanitɪkanamɪakumadufedebiuinnɪɡudohodʒatekʼɪllensakʼabɪtʃatɪɡamemanɪarɡatereinnɪdukanakesalalefatʃafɪɡarɡalafɪdallansufɪfa??adabanɪtawontɪaninɪarɡetanawontɪwantʃʼahaufairadansakanamutoltʃumaleakawanhodʒatearɡateɲateduɡeɡammadunɪhaɡabultɪɡababduwakʼɪkennefɪtanadʒirudʒɪrunɪnamatutanuma?owakʼɪduromafɪkʼabennanamakennenamamatʃesenamɪsuninɪsilaɡalataɪsadebisewanhodʒatekaleɪraɡammadumaletuninɪtʃʼahauftɪkennɪwakʼatɪwanwakʼɪisaɡammatʃɪsefɪinnɪdʒɪrennaɪsaɡababakanaɡudoi??aduwontɪaninɪarɡelafatanakesadabaɡudatoltʃanɪwakʼɪduromafaulfɪnnafakʼabennafɪwantʃʼahaufakanamɪfeduinkennafɪammoakainnɪkʼufematʃaunɪitɪillakisuammofullaɪsanamumadibɪkainnɪimbennetɪduɡekʼufematʃanɪtunɪlenɪwomaɪmbatuwomadabatɪ?onamɪlububuleɪdʒolledibatokodaleammoɡammadafɪawaladansaledabenaɡaratʃanamairabahutɪirawo??adalotɪɪlmanɪsunɪwomaɪmbahudukanakesabadeatʃumatɪdedanɪinnɪtakaaduleinarɡine?okhanɪtakawomaleimbaranneammohatatutɪ?afullabokʼotaɡahenamafinnaufɪimatʃinɪiraatonamɪsunɪɡannakumalamataelesɪlaftuworrɪlatʃufullumataka?awontɪnamɪhodʒatufɪakumaɡaraufɪkʼubsuammoɪnkʼufunamɪkʼaronɪkarakaminɪdalleiradʒirahi??esaarɡadaɡetinɪmalbatɪtunɪlenɪwomaɪmbatuserumanamakʼɪllensaɡussutɪfullailaderatu?owanharkakʼabdukʼuftudansawantahatʃʼahaufadurumuranɪammallenuɪmbennanamɪnamaisairadʒabadandaeimorkunɪdubinɪakumaderatunɪmɪadabdɪkarakaminɪɡomitakʼabdɪnamɪtokolenɪakaminɪdandaewanɪsamaledʒɪrennaɪsaɡababakawomaɪmbanekaakaɡandidudabrukanakesatɪbekhaenutɪwaneɡɪinnɪduelafakesatɪtahabekhafullamanadʒilademanɪhodʒdʒamanabohademanɪiradʒirtɪwannamɪdʒiruakadotɪisaeɡatuufɪkʼabsɪsufɪlalefatʃanɪkoblairadʒirtɪ?ofulasi?akɪtelehubatʃasikennitɪnamɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufawanɡammadahereɡudallenamɪkʼaronɪwanduahereɡafulladallenɪsiɡorsuhodʒdʒakʼaronɪsiɡorsuirasidʒirtɪ?odallenɪkofaltukoblɪɪsikʼoratɪibɪdatɪnakʼanɪtadudukʼiftufakatatunɪlenɪwomakesaɪndʒirtukʼaronɪnamasobudallefakataammalleɡumboɲatʃɪtinɪɡurranamaballesitɪmummenɪwantʃʼahaufaumamaɪsiiradʒirtɪobsɪlenɪufɪsaduiradʒirafinnɪdurɪesafinnaammairadʒiraindʒedinasuninɪɡafɪdallumatɪnamɪdʒirutʃʼahauftɪkʼarotahumalewontɪakanatifɪkʼaromɪdalairawonamabahaammalleakumabesenɪnamawantakatanalenamakʼarkʼartuinnɪlenɪnamakʼarkʼarakʼaromɪnamakʼorkʼorataakɪbekhɪwonamabahuakanamewanwakʼɪtoltʃehereɡɪentudandaewanwakʼɪdabsekʼadʒeltʃahodʒdʒawosimidaɡanɪɡammadɪammallehodʒdʒaɡarɡalɪdufuwankanakʼabaduwakʼumatɪɡammadafɪɡarɡalalenamatinɪdufanamɪdandaewanitɪdemuɪmbekhudʒɪrennɪkɪ??akʼarawomakesaɪndʒiruammohatatutɪisakesatɪɡudowoarɡeatonamɪkʼadʒelanɪdansanɪdunamɪhamanɪatohamatelelububulatanafɪɡudonamaduɡatate?okhanɪkʼarotatewantʃʼahaufakesaindabrinɪmanifɪufumaufɪballesitaammoakumasunɪnamahamatate?okhanɪdalletatewantʃʼahaufakesaindabrinɪmanifɪatoɡu??anɪkankeɪnɡenneufɪɪdʒeftaɡamalatʃuɡulaindʒɪɡinɪdʒɪdumakesatɪhafɪammo?oatinɪnamawakʼasodatutateɪnumadabsataha??otakudanɪtadiratokokesadʒirtuirakʼaromɪnamakʼarodʒabesalafairanamɪtokolenɪkahodʒdʒatʃʼahaufaduɡatoltʃewollalaɪnkʼamneɪndʒirudubɪnamɪdʒedutʃʼahaufaɡulaindeminɪheɡerɪhodʒatutantetasiarabsɪtufadaɡetaatɪlenɪɪmbetaakamarohedunamaarabsitewananinɪdʒedekanatʃʼahaufakʼaromaki??anɪlalearɡeaninɪkʼarotahufedeammotahudadabenamɪakamɪdandaeakadʒɪrennɪdʒiruhubatadʒɪrennɪkuninɪwannamɪakaisabekhunitɪdandanɪinhubatanɪammoatoakasiletateaninɪufɪbaseakabekhanɪwobaraduammalleakakʼaromafɪwanimbennelebaradeakawonɪhamtunɪdallumafɪmaratuhubaduaninɪwanduisairahamtuarɡenadenɪdʒalaltɪɪsinɪsikʼabduakatururanamakʼabdɪharkɪɪsikanamamarsuakumasansalatanamahidanamɪwakʼadʒalatudandaedʒalabahaammoɪsinɪnamadabaɪnumakʼabdɪabanɪhereɡawandʒedeaninɪatotokotokonɪbarbaduwoarɡeaninɪwandɪbilehereɡanɪbarbadearɡudadabeaninɪnamakumatokokesanamadiratokokaɡomuarɡeammonadenɪtokoleɪnɡarrewontɪaninɪarɡetanatʃʼahaallawakʼɪkʼadʒelumanɪnumɪdaseammonamɪakairaufɪɡorseufɪbabadesaentunamakʼarofakataentuwandubinɪtʃʼahauftɪdʒetubekhakʼaromɪhamennanamairaballesenamamɪdasawanha??unɪdʒedetoltʃɪheredemalewakʼaduratɪwomainkakhatinɪha??unɪwanfedutoltʃatanafɪisabɪrademumaltefullasodataakanatanakesaintainɪdubinɪha??udʒabennakʼabdɪentuatinɪmafɪwankanatoltʃitadʒedeisaɡafatanamɪdubɪɪsaɡutuwomaɪntahukʼaronɪdubɪsunɪakaɡutufɪhodʒdʒaɡutuleɪmbekhahodʒafɪkaranɪdansanɪwotoltʃanɪɪndʒ ?adabeduɡaheraɡɪisa?anɪilmɪamotsɪisaarɡudakʼewandʒedenɪabowakʼɪwansinɪdʒeduwankanketʃʼahaufamidafadudamaduatinɪdukubakanaɪraɪnhaftuɪndotadʒennanɪhetsekɪanɪfulamanatɪdefatewakʼakadatewandʒedeeabowakʼaakaaninɪɡaratokonɪsihodʒadesisalfadewomaatinɪfetutʃʼahaallatoltʃekʼabaduakasɪdʒedeakahamabohedʒennanɪabowakʼɪwanisa?anɪdʒededebɪwanhetsekɪanɪdʒetuaninɪabowakʼɪwakʼɪababokankedaudɪ?a?ukadatʃatantedaɡa?eimɪmanɪkankearɡeammaɡannakudanɪʃanɪɡu??akanketɪsidaraaninɪammallesifɪdira?erusalemukanaharkaha??uaʃurukesabasedirasuniledʒabeseɲapaɪradowaabowakʼɪakhekhakanasikenneakananɪkakhuɪsaɡutafanoha??uahatsinɪdʒareɡubaabowakʼɪɡandiduedʒatakudanɪdudadubatɪdebisadubaɡandɪdunɪedʒatakudanɪdudadubatɪdebitehetsekɪanɪfa??adabafa??edʒennanɪfarutanatafewandʒedeaninɪtʃʼahaɪmumatɪ??akesaatodʒareufɪindʒɪbatinɪwanduefullaekheratɪdemuufɪsehewandʒedelafatanaɪratɪdebieabowakʼafɪnamalubukʼabuɪnarɡuakumawarobukʼɪsanɪfudanɪlubutɪ??anarafudanɪakumawo?anarakutanɪwoltɪdatʃasanɪaninɪwanwakʼɪlubunarafuduseheaninɪhalkanɪtʃʼahaufaakawanɲentʃɪlafenatʃʼahaabsudʒirudukubsadebohewanwakʼɪlubunarafudusehekʼonkʼonɪtɪ??alaftekʼallatekʼonkʼosabalisafakatewananinɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufataewakʼailalufɪiltɪnaarteaboɡarɡalakanatʃʼahaufakesanabasɪammoaninɪmanɪdʒetʃudandaabowakʼatɪwankananatoltʃeɡaranɪnahamatehɪribɪilakesanabadeaboaninɪsimalewomaɪnkʼabudʒɪrennɪkɪ??asɪumanafa??isɪnadʒɪresɪɡaranɪkɪ??akakʼarahamateɡaraɡaleammanaɡa?ahorataatinɪlubutɪ??awanhamtutʃʼahaufadurabaftetʃʼahaubutɪ??adudaitɪɡaltenaararamtenamɪfullaekheradʒirutokolenɪdandaesiɪnfarsuekheranɪdandetesiduɡefatesiinabdatunamalubukʼabutɪdandaesifarsaakumaaninɪammataesifarsukanaabotinɪduɡatanteɪlmanɪufibarsiftɪabowakʼaatinɪlanafa??iftenuammatanahaɡadʒirukɪrarɪdofnemanakankekesatɪsifarsinadubaisa?anɪkʼarawandʒedemɪdanɪodafudadullaɪsatɪmatansadubainnɪinfa??awontɪinnɪakasɪdʒedefɪha??uhetsekɪanɪkʼaraakhekhɪaninɪmanawakʼatinɪsenukamɪdʒedeisaɡafatebarasunɪha??unɪbabɪlonɪkamerodakabaladanɪilmabaladanɪdʒedanɪakahetsekɪanɪfa??adabedaɡa?etatabefɪwandibɪerɡefɪhetsekɪanɪworraerɡ utɪdandaebɪ??elafatʃʼahaufamudunutokotɪdebisa?okhanɪɡarenifɪkubɪleletʃʼahaufamɪsanatakaɪratɪbimaenutɪdandaeɪsabarsise?okhanɪwoɪitɪhimawakʼɪbekhafɪhubatʃafɪmalawoinɪtoltʃanɪenuirafudataabowakʼaduratɪɡotʃitɪtʃʼahauftɪwomakesaɪndʒirtudimpubɪsanɪfakatɪlaftɪfaɡotabɪsanɪdʒidudʒirtulenɪakumaawarasablatɪbɪnensɪbadalebanonɪkesadʒirulenɪtʃʼahauftɪsoriowakʼakennabasanɪɪnɡahumukhɪisɪlenɪkʼoranɪibɪdaɪnɡahuɡotʃɪtɪlenɪɪsaduratɪwomanitɪ?okhanɪwomakesaɪndʒirtu?okhanɪenutɪdandaeakainnɪdʒirunamatɪhimainnɪwanhoɡesɪharkanɪmidasenitɪ?okhanɪkatumtunɪworkʼinɪmidasitewankʼarsinɪmidasanɪdʒaladadabdenitɪnamɪirrekʼarsifɪworkʼinɪhoratuɪnkʼamnemukhuinhuromnefɪlatehoɡesadansatɪɡeseakhekhainkʼarinemidafataɪsanɪimbetanɪɪsanɪindaɡenneakalaftɪdurɪumamteammalleimbarannenamɪumenamabartʃumaɪsairaɡubawantʃʼahaufataunamɪisadʒalatɪdidɪkʼatetutɪfakatainnɪɡubaakaɡollaballiseakawaronamɪkesatautoltʃeinnɪnamairrekʼabukalafafiduballesenamawomakesaɪndʒirretoltʃaworrɪmukhadikʼa?adioobranɪkahidaimbasinɪfakata?oabowakʼɪbubeɡadɪerɡuɡoɡoɡeakabuabu?obubenɪfutɪwakʼakʼulkʼulloenunɪwolbirakʼabanɪnamɪakaɪsalafakesaɪndʒirameɡubaɪlalaurdʒɪɪsanɪaɡartanɪtanaenutɪumenamɪumeɪsumakaisɪtokotokonɪɡa?asuinnɪhaɡaɪsiɪmbekhaammalletʃʼahaufamakʼumaisɪtinɪ?amaɪrrenɪɪsaɡudodʒabdutanafɪurdʒinɪsunɪtokolenɪɪmbadue?akoboatinɪmanifɪɡunɡumteabowakʼɪɡarɡalakɪ??aɪmbekhu?okhanɪ?onadabsanileinnɪwomairaɪnkʼabudʒetaɪsanɪimbetanɪɪsanɪindaɡenneabowakʼɪwakʼahaɡadʒirudʒɪrennadʒirulafatʃʼahaufahaɡumaɡetunɪisumatɪumeinnɪdadabeɪllafunamɪtokolenɪhereɡaɪsainhubatuinnɪlafafɪdadabadʒabesaidʒollenɪlalaftekaɪmɪlenɪɡaɡaɡabaammonamɪabowakʼaduɡefateisaeɡatudebieirrearɡataworrɪakumarisabarɪsaorieindadabu?omɪlanɪ?aule?aeindadabuwakʼɪwandʒeduɪsanɪworrɪlafafaɡotʃʼahaallisanatʃʼahaakʼasawandubatʃufetanɪkurfefadakotadubadakotawolwoldennenamaduɡakʼabuɪlalaenutɪnamawohaduilaborutɪɡakasefullainnɪbahetʃʼahaufadabsatʃakennafɪenutɪha??otafɪɡosaletʃʼahaufaisadabsatʃisainnɪɡoradeufɪtinɪworradaebullesetɪ?aisatinɪakabuabu?okʼillensatɪfɪrfirsainnɪhordoferebekamilɪɪsaakawanbarisudʒir adadifɪsaɡaledansaaninɪɡu??atʃʼahaufasoraduworralekennaammallehaɡaɡannasadɪworrabarsisaeɡɪsunɪnatinɪkotadʒedeworrafohatanɪsunɪkesanamɪafurɪɡosa?udadʒarɪsunɪafranɪkanadanɪelɪhananiamiʃaelɪatsarianamitʃɪhodʒatumatakanɪmakʼaharesaworrabasedanɪelinɪbelteʃatsadʒedehananɪanɪʃadrakadʒedemiʃaelinɪmeʃekɪdʒedeatsarɪanɪabedneɡodʒededanɪelinɪakasaɡaledansafɪdadɪha??unɪsoratusorateakasinɪufɪinturesinekutatedubaaʃpenatsɪkadateakainnɪsaɡalesunɪɪsainkenninedʒennanɪabowakʼɪaʃpenatsɪɪsanasiseammoaʃpenatsinɪha??udetewandanɪelinɪdʒedeha??unɪwanɪsanɪɲatanɪdudanɪ?amure?oatinɪhalatedʒarakanɪhankʼateinnɪheɡerɪnaɪdʒesafadubadanɪelinɪnamitʃaaʃpenatsinɪɪsafɪdʒarasadenɪkanɪkʼorkʼoradadʒedenɪkanɪdakʼewandʒedenɪbultɪkudanɪnuɪlalɪrafufɪbɪsanɪtʃʼahaallanukennɪdubanufɪkaimasaɡaleha??udansaɲatukanɪwoltɪɪlalɪwanaɡartuɡulawandʒetʃumaltedʒedɪdubainnɪdubɪsunɪɡulabultɪkudanɪworraɪlalebultinɪkudannanɪtanɪhobatedʒennanɪworrɪworrasaɡaleha??uɲatukanɪiraɡabatemɪdaɡedubaartɪasɪnamitʃɪworraɡololtʃukanɪsaɡaleha??ulakiserafunɪworraɡololtʃewakʼɪdʒarakaimaafranɪkanɪbekhafɪhubatʃawansomaninɪbaratanɪkennefɪtanamaleleinnɪdanɪelɪkʼalbɪinnɪda??afɪobdʒunɪhimukennefɪɡannɪsadenɪha??unɪdʒedekanɪhobaedʒennanɪaʃpenatsinɪdʒarakaimakanɪtʃʼahaufanebukadretsaduranɪdufeha??itʃɪworratʃʼahaufanɪdubatedʒennanɪdanɪelifɪhananɪafɪmiʃaelifɪatsarɪanɪworrakanɪtʃʼahaufairaha??uɡammatʃɪsanɪdubaakananɪworrɪhudʒɪha??ududewantatefukaha??unɪɡafatutʃʼahaufawankʼaromatifɪ?okhanɪkahubatʃaletananɪdʒarɪafranɪkuninɪnamawohɪmufɪfalfaltulafainnɪmohatukesadʒirtutʃʼahaufamarokudanɪirawobekhadanɪelinɪhudʒɪha??usunɪhaɡakoreʃinɪlafababɪlonɪha??uitɪtahekesataeɡannalamesokanebukadretsanɪlafamohateinnɪobdʒuobdʒateobdʒunɪsunɪɡudohereɡaisanaterafudowartedʒennanɪinnɪworrawohɪmufɪfalfaltufɪnamamurmabafatufɪkaa??anaheduwoltɪ?amewanobdʒunɪtɪ??adoftunatɪhimadʒedeworrɪisaduradufedʒennanɪwandʒedenɪobdʒunɪaninɪobdʒadesuninɪɡudohereɡanatinɪduftewanɪsibekhufedanatɪhimadʒennanɪworrɪafanɪaramutinɪwandʒedeeha??itʃalububulɪobdʒutantenutɪhimɪwanɪsinɪdoftusitɪhimnaha??itʃɪwanwor ehaɡatʃʼahauftɪbukhofteolbatutɪ?esonɪmammasanɪwankanatʃʼahaufaworratɪhasaemammasamalewomatokolenamatɪinhasomnetuninɪakawontɪraɡɪdʒedeɡutamtuaninɪafanɪkɪ??abanademammasanɪdubadaaninɪwanhaɡalaftɪumamtedossanɪhimadʒennanɪɡumɪbɪradememanatɪɡaledʒarɪɪsaɡaraɪsadufewandʒedenɪmammasarafuobrukesadɪdesɪnutɪhimɪ?esonɪwandʒedenɪnamɪmɪdanɪdansafatʃasuilmanamatɪobrunɪlafatanamɪdanɪdansanɪɪlmanɪfinnawakʼatɪrafunɪɪlmanɪhamakanɪɲapɪisɪfatʃaseʃetanamuransɪwaneɡɪtanaworrɪmurulenɪmalaikaakumarafuwoltɪɡuranɪibɪdanɪɡubanɪakasumaeɡɪtanaletatɪilmɪnamamalaikaufɪerɡeɪsinɪfinnaɪsakesawandabatʃʼahaufafɪworrahamennatoltʃutʃʼahaufawoltɪɡurteɪbidabalaliukesaɡatɪatʃitɪbohanɪɪlkanɪkʼaranɪɡafasɪdʒarɪduɡaakaadufinnaabaworrakesatɪifsa?oɡurrakʼabatanɪdaɡa?afinnɪɡubaakahorɪobrukesatɪdossanɪdʒirakanamɪarɡatebɪ??eɪratɪdebisebɪrademeɡammadaufɪkesawankʼabutʃʼahaufaɡurɡureobrusunɪbɪtataammallefinnɪɡubadaldaltudokʼamɪdadubarbadufakatadokʼatokotaɡatɪɡudoarɡɪnanɪdemewankʼabutʃʼahaufaɡurɡurebɪtataammallefinnɪɡubatururaɡalanakesabusanɪkʼurtumɪɡosatʃʼahaufawoltɪɡuraninɪfakata?oɡutameafanɪɡalanatɪhirkɪsanɪtatanɪkʼurtumɪɡarɡarɪfɪlanɪdadansaolke?atanɪhamamtuɡadɪɡatanɪeɡɪtanaleakasumatatɪmalaɪkanɪduftenamahamamafɪdadansaɡarɡarɪbaftɪɪbidabalalɪutɪɡurtɪatʃitɪbohanɪɪlkanɪkʼaranɪwankanatʃʼahaufahubatanɪworrɪedʒedenɪ?esonɪwanworranɪdʒedetanafɪnamɪserabekhukawanfinnaɡubabarateakaabaworrakasubaufɪkesawanharesafɪdullatʃabasufakata?esonɪmammasakanahobamnanɪatʃɪkaedemelafaufɪdakʼemanawakʼaitɪkadatanɪkesatɪnamabarsisenamɪisatʃʼahaakʼasetʃʼahauftɪmadefatewandʒedenamitʃɪkuninɪkʼalbɪtanafɪhumnawanmamakananɪtoltʃuesaarɡatekuninɪilmanamitʃawobotʃukanɪnitɪmakʼanɪhadaisamarɪamunitɪobole?anɪɪsa?akobofɪ?usufufɪsimonifɪ?udanitɪobole?anɪɪsatadubranuwolinɪdʒirtɪnitɪnamitʃɪkuninɪdʒabennakanatʃʼahaufaesaarɡateredubaisakʼufudɪdanɪdʒennanɪ?esonɪwanworranɪdʒedefullatʃʼahaufatɪraɡaɡudɪsanɪollafɪworraɪsakesamaleinnɪwanmamaatʃitɪintoltʃinemaroworrɪduɡefatʃainkʼamnefɪha??uherodebarasunɪwan?esodaɡa?ewantɪsseleufɪtinɪdʒedenamɪkuninɪ?ohananamabatisuinn utʃʼahaufaisatoltʃaammo?oinnɪhodʒatuhamtutatewaninnɪufinɪdʒeduabanɪkɪ??adufuɪnɡennedʒedehodʒatutʃʼahaufadanesaɡaleɲateworrafarsoduɡuwolinɪduɡaabanɪhodʒatusunɪɡu??ainnɪinsehannefɪhodʒdʒainnɪɪmbennedufeabanɪkanɪɡarɡarɪisatʃʼahaɪtʃiredʒarakikɪ??ɪbanɪwoltɪdaraatʃitɪboheɪlkanɪkʼaraʃanɪkʼarotanɪɡowotaɡowolenɪtanɪifsefudateammodadabobesaninɪlakiftekʼaronɪtanɪwandadaitɪnakʼanɪdadaɡutefudateabanɪfudaturedʒennanɪdubritɪtanɪmuderaftehalkanɪɡudokʼonkʼonɪdufteabanɪfudakanakotaisaarɡadʒedanɪdubritɪkudannanukateifsebobefateɡowolenɪtanɪwankʼarotaninɪdʒetedadanutʃʼahaobsaɪfsenɪtennadamudʒirtɪkʼaronɪtanɪwandʒetenɪhɪ??owoltɪnuɪnɡahubenabɪtadaɡowolenɪtanɪdadadibɪbɪtatʃudatɪitɪdabannanɪabanɪfudadufedubritɪkurfotatetanɪdʒilafudaoldudebalbalatʃʼahaufanɪammoabanɪfudawandʒedelakisaaninɪfulaɪsanɪɪmbekhueɡadadubaɪsanɪɡu??afɪhodʒdʒaimbetanɪinnɪnamatʃʼahaufawaninnɪdandauitɪkennetokoʃɪlinɡɪkunkɪʃantamaitɪkennekalamesokunkɪdɪdamaitɪkennekasadesokunkɪkudanɪitɪkennekaeitɪdabatenamitʃɪkunkɪʃantamaitɪkennanɪkanɪdakʼedaldalenɪkunkɪʃantamadibɪarɡatenamitʃɪkunkɪdɪdamaitɪkennanɪlenɪakasumakunkɪdɪdamadibɪarɡateammonamitʃɪkunkɪkudanɪitɪkennanɪkanɪdakʼebolakʼotehorɪkanɪatʃitɪdosseabanɪhodʒatutanɪɡudotureɡadɪdebiehennasunɪtʃʼahaufaworrawolinɪtoltʃenamitʃɪkunkɪʃantamaitɪkennanɪkanɪdufekunkɪʃantamadibɪitɪkennewandʒedeatinɪkunkɪʃantamanatɪkenniteɪlalɪkunkinɪʃantamadibɪlenɪtanaabanɪwandʒedenɪakadiratoltʃiteatinɪakadansadaldaltetanafɪaninɪwanɡudoharkaketitɪkennakotɪwolinɪɡammannanamitʃɪʃɪlinɡɪkunkɪdɪdamaitɪkennanɪkanɪdufewandʒedeatinɪkunkɪdɪdamanatɪkenniteɪlalɪkunkinɪdɪdamadibɪlenɪtanaabanɪwandʒedenɪakadiratoltʃiteatinɪakadansadaldaltetanafɪaninɪwanɡudoharkaketitɪkennakotɪwolinɪɡammannadʒennanɪnamitʃɪʃɪlinɡɪkunkɪkudanɪitɪkennanɪkanɪdufewandʒedeaboaninɪɪmbekhaakaatinɪnamahamaatinɪwaninobrinɪmurtemɪdanɪimfatʃasinɪkhodotɪɡaltʃitaaninɪsodadehorɪkankebolakesatɪdosseɪlalɪhorinɪkankekanaabanɪwandʒedenɪatinɪhodʒatuhamtuammallelafaatinɪakaaninɪwaninobrinɪmurademɪdanɪimfatʃasinɪkhodotɪɡaltʃuimbeta?u?osɪhorɪkɪ??aolɪnaka?uma daimaɡombokesarafɪsanɪwo?adaimaitɪu?ɪsanɪarɡɪtanɪdʒennanɪmalaikasunɪwolinɪdulɪmalaikahedunɪtassadufewakʼaɡudisewandʒedeɡudinnɪɡarawakʼaɡubahatahulafakesalenaɡennɪhatahuɡaradʒarainnɪebisumalaɪkanɪkateɡubatɪoldatʃatedʒennanɪtissɪtunɪwanwolinɪdʒetebenahaɡabethlehemunu?asawanwakʼɪnubesisekatahekanalalladubatitɪmanɪ?anɪmarɪamufɪ?usufufɪdaimaɡombokesarafɪsanɪarɡanɪwankanaarɡɪnanɪoduɡurbatadaɡa?anɪtanɪodesanɪnamɪtʃʼahauftɪkawantissɪtunɪhimtedaɡa?eɡudomameammomarɪamunɪdubɪsunɪɡaraufɪkesake?ateheredetissɪtunɪdebitemarowantʃʼahaufakadaɡetearɡɪtefɪwakʼaɡudiftefarsitewontɪtʃʼahauftɪakumamalaɪkanɪworratɪhimtetatewontɪakanatifɪserawakʼakesatɪwantafanɪilmaanɡafatʃʼahaufaabowakʼabasumalanɪdʒedanɪammalleworrɪsoriobasudemeakaseraabowakʼakesatɪhɪmanɪsabalisadɪdikʼalama?okhanɪɡuɡurdalamanamatokotɪdʒiraka?erusalemutaukasimeonɪdʒedanɪinnɪnamaduɡatɪwakʼasodatebafamaisraelɪeɡataammalleinnɪlubukʼulkʼullokʼabaɪsinɪakainnɪhaɡakristoilmawakʼaarɡutɪɪndoneisabesiftelubunɪsunɪɪsatɪakhetedʒennanɪinnɪmanawakʼaolsenedubaabafɪhatɪ?esoɡurbanɪolsennanɪakaɪsaadaserɪfeduɡutanɪsimeonɪɡurbaolhamparewakʼafarsewandʒedeammaaboakaatinɪdʒeteɡulaɡarbitʃakankenaɡa?anɪdemsisɪwontɪakanatifɪiltɪtɪ??a?a?ubafamakankeaɡartekaatinɪfulaɡosatʃʼahaufaduratɪkurfesiteammallekaɡudinnaɡosatanteisraelitɪkennuabafɪhatɪisalenɪdubɪsimeoninɪwanɡurbadubateɡudomamanɪsimeoninɪworraebisewanhadaɪsamarɪamunɪdʒedeɡurbakana?afohatanɪakanamɪhedunɪisraelɪkesadʒɪdʒiɡe?okhanɪkakauammalleakaakhekhawannamɪhedunɪdʒibutahuakahereɡɪɡaranamahedumullatulalaltɪlenɪonnetanteworantɪdʒartɪtokodʒirataraɡatamakʼanɪisɪannaɪsinɪdubrafanuelɪkaɡosaaʃerɪannanɪdirsaisɪwolinɪɡannatorbatamatetedirsɪdonanɪhaɡaɡannɪɪsisadetamɪafurɪɡahutɪtetemanawakʼakesaɪmbatuhalkanɪɡu??aɪsinɪwakʼaɡudifteaɡabdewakʼakadateisɪlenɪhodʒumasunɪduftewakʼaɡalatadebiftewanɡurbadikʼakananamabafama?erusalemueɡatutʃʼahaufatɪodesiteɡurbanɪsunɪɡudatedʒabateammalleɡudokʼaroebawakʼakʼabaɡannɪɪsakudanɪlamaɡennanɪakumaadaworraɡuladʒiladakʼanɪdʒiltɪhobatedʒennanɪatobi??itɪɡaltu?esonɪ?erusalemutɪhafeabafɪhatɪɪsakʼubainkʼabanɪammowaninnɪɡumɪwolinɪdʒirusehanɪdubaɡu??atokotʃʼahaufademnanɪfɪtafɪwahelakesaisabarbadanɪisadamnanɪ?erusalemutɪdatʃanɪbarbadanɪeɡɪɡu??asadɪmanawakʼakesatɪarɡanɪatoinnɪdʒidukʼaloletaeufiletʃʼahaakʼaseworralewoɡafatunamɪisadaɡa?etʃʼahauftɪbekhumafɪdʒetʃaɪsaɡudomadefateisaarɡɪnanɪɡudomamanɪdubahatɪwandʒetenɪɡurbaatinɪmafɪakananutoltʃiteanafɪabetɪlenɪɡudonanesibarbannedʒennanɪinnɪwandʒedenɪmafɪnabarbadanɪakaaninɪmanaabakɪ??akesataumaleimbetanɪammodubinɪinnɪworranɪdʒedeworraɪnɡalledʒennanɪinnɪworrawolinɪdebienatsaretitɪɡaleworrasalfatehatɪɪsadubɪsunɪtʃʼahaufaɡarakesake?ate?esonɪolɡudatekʼalbɪhoratewakʼafɪnamɪlenɪisaebiseɡannakudanɪʃanesokakaɪsarɪtiberɪonɪlafafideɡafapontiopilatonɪlafa?ahudɪfidekaherodenɪha??uɡalɪla?akaobolesɪɪsafilɪponɪha??ulafaitureafɪtrakonitɪlisanialenɪha??ulafaabɪleneɡafaanasifɪka?afanɪkʼaloleɡuɡurdotahanɪɡafasɪdubinɪwakʼalafaalotɪ?ohanailmatsekarɪatɪduftetanafɪinnɪlafatʃʼahaufatadawatuɡalana?ordanɪdakʼenamatɪodesewandʒededabaɪradebiabatɪfamaakadabaɪsanɪararamanɪakumakɪtabaraɡaisa?akesatɪtafanɪkʼonkʼonɪnamalafaalotɪɪ?uwandʒetukaraabomɪdasadandɪɪsakʼadʒeltʃabalenɪtʃʼahauftɪinɡutamtɪɡarenifɪɡorotʃʼahaufaindɪrɪrsanɪfulladabdutʃʼahaufakʼadʒeltʃanɪkarakʼukʼatʃʼahaufawolkʼɪtesanɪnamɪtʃʼahauftɪbafamawakʼailaufɪtinɪarɡahudʒɪnamɪdabaɪradebiutoltʃutoltʃaabanɪkennaabrahamuufinɪindʒedinawananinɪdʒeduwakʼɪdakhakanakesaɪlmanɪabrahamumɪdasuindandaammatanadaɡara?ahidamukhadʒalaka?anɪtanafɪmukhamɪdanɪdansaɪmbamnetʃʼahaufamuranitɪɪbidakesabusanɪdubaɡuminɪwanɪsanɪdʒetenumanɪtanareinnɪwandʒedenɪabanɪkotɪlamakʼabunamatokoleɪnkʼamnehakennuammallekasaɡalekʼabulenɪakasumahatoltʃudʒarɪɡɪbiraɡurulenɪbatɪfamudumnanɪwandʒedeabonumaltahumalleinnɪwanworranɪdʒedehaɡadamosaɡuradʒedanɪindabarsinaaskartɪlenɪwandʒetenuammomaltoltʃumalleinnɪwandʒedenɪnamatokoleɪrrenɪ?okhanɪkaradaratinɪhorɪiraimfudatinaammohorɪɪsanɪkennanisifefadaatobi??itɪwandufaedewan?ohanaheredekristoisasetuinnɪwanworratʃʼahaufanɪdʒededuɡumaaninɪbisaninɪɪsanɪbatisaammonamanaraɡudatokotɪdufakasemsakopeɪsaaninɪhikhuhimmalinɪinnɪlubukʼulkʼullofɪibɪdanɪɪsanɪbatisainnɪhafareharkakʼabaakafulladarɡa?eitɪhafarsanɪkʼulkʼullesedarɡa?ekhodotɪɡalfatuammokʼolaɪsifullaɪbidɪindamnetɪɡubaduba?ohananɪdubɪhedunɪnamaɡorseodudansalenamatɪodeseammoinnɪwanha??uherodeodesemaroherodenɪwosilaufɪherodiabaratefɪammallemaroinnɪdabadibɪhedutoltʃefɪdʒennanɪherodenɪhaɡakʼarairahamate?ohanalehidedubaeɡɪnamɪtʃʼahauftɪbatɪfame?esolenɪbatisoarɡateatoinnɪkadatuɡubanɪbanamtelubunɪkʼulkʼullonɪtabifasabalisakʼabduisairabutekʼonkʼonɪɡubaduftewandʒeteatinɪilmakɪ??akaaninɪdʒaladuɡudonaɡammatʃiftaɡafa?esonɪhudʒɪufɪitɪke?ateɡannɪɪsasodomafanamɪilma?usufuisasehe?usufunɪilmaelɪelinɪkamathatɪmathatinɪkalawɪlawinɪkamelkɪmelkinɪka?ana?ananɪka?usufu?usufunɪkamatathiamatathɪanɪkaamosɪamosinɪkanahumunahumunɪkaeslɪeslinɪkanaɡaɪnaɡainɪkamathɪmathinɪkamatathiamatathɪanɪkasemeɪsemeinɪka?usufu?usufunɪka?uda?udanɪka?oana?oananɪkaresaresanɪkatserubabelɪtserubabelinɪkaʃealtɪelɪʃealtielinɪkanerɪnerinɪkamelkɪmelkinɪkaadɪadinɪkakosamukosamunɪkaelmadamuelmadamunɪkaerɪerinɪka?oʃua?oʃuanɪkaelɪetserɪelɪetserinɪka?orimu?orɪmunɪkamathatɪmathatinɪkalawɪlawinɪkasimeonɪsimeoninɪka?uda?udanɪka?usufu?usufunɪka?onamu?onamunɪkaelɪakimuelɪakɪmunɪkameleamealanɪkamenamenanɪkamatathamatathanɪkanathanɪnathaninɪkadaudɪdaudinɪka?ese?esenɪkaobedɪobedinɪkaboatsɪboatsinɪkasalmonɪsalmoninɪkanaʃonɪnaʃoninɪkaamɪnadabuamɪnadabunɪkaaramuaramunɪkahesronɪhesroninɪkaperesɪperesinɪka?uda?udanɪka?akobo?akobonɪkaɪsakʼoisakʼonɪkaabrahamuabrahamunɪkaterateranɪkanahorɪnahorinɪkaseruɡɪseruɡinɪkaraɡauraɡaunɪkapeleɡɪpeleɡinɪkaeberɪeberinɪkasalasalanɪkakennanɪkennaninɪkaarfaksadɪarfaksadinɪkaʃemuʃemunɪkanuhunuhunɪkalamekɪlamekinɪkamethuselamethuselanɪkahenokohenokonɪka?aredɪ?aredinɪkamahalalelɪmahalalelinɪkakennanɪkennaninɪkaenoʃɪenoʃinɪkasethɪsethinɪkaadamuadamunɪkawakʼa?esonɪlubukʼulkʼullonɪɡutamnanɪɡalana?ordanitɪdebielubunɪsunɪlafaaloisaɡesitehaɡabultɪafurtamaʃetanɪisailalateinnɪhaɡasunɪtʃʼahaufasaɡalemaletaedubaɡu??anɪhobananɪɡudobelaeʃetanɪwanɪsanɪd ?esoɡurɡuredʒennanɪinnɪworrawolinɪɡabueballinnalafakesadʒaraufɪheduwolinɪedʒeammalleɡumɪɡudota?erusalemutifɪtalafaafanɪɡalanatirotifɪsidonitɪdufteakadubɪɪsadaɡetedukubafa??ɪtutɪisawolinɪdʒiranamɪdʒɪnninɪɡarɡaltʃitelenɪimfa?eammallewandʒabennɪisakesabaheworratʃʼahaufafa??ɪsefɪɡuminɪtʃʼahauftɪisatukʼufete?esonɪdʒaraufɪmɪllatewandʒedea??anakesanɪhi??e?ɪfinnɪwakʼakesanɪa??anakesanɪkaammabelakʼabuɪsanɪkʼufsanɪa??anakesanɪkaammabotanɪeɡɪtanaɪnumakofaltanɪɡu??asunɪɡammadakʼilɪtamaoltʃetʃeawontɪakanatifɪwanɡudoɡubaarɡatanɪababotɪworralenɪakasumadurɪraɡotatoltʃiteammoɡarɡalakesanɪdure?ɪkʼodakesanɪkaɡammadalaarɡatanɪɡarɡalakesanɪkaammakʼuftanɪeɡɪtanaimbeloftanɪɡarɡalakesanɪkaammakofaltanɪeɡɪtanalalefatanɪbotanɪɡarɡalakesanɪhodʒdʒanamɪtʃʼahauftɪɪsanɪsaduwontɪakanatifɪababotɪworraakasumaraɡotadarasadeammowananinɪɪsanɪkadaɡetaninɪdʒeduɲapakesanɪdʒaladanamaɪsanɪdʒibuwandansatoltʃanamaɪsanɪabaruleebisakaisanitɪdʒallatelekadadanamabokʼotokosidabanasutaledurakʼabadunamawo?atantesirafudatukotileindowinɪnamawoɪsikadatutʃʼahaufakennɪammallenamawosirafudatuiraimbarbadinɪakumaakanamɪwandansaɪsanɪtoltʃufetanɪakasumanamalewandansatoltʃa?onamaɪsanɪdʒalatudʒalatanɪebatamɪarɡatanɪnamɪhamamalenɪnamaworradʒalatudʒalata?onamawandansaɪsanɪtoltʃewandansatoltʃɪtanɪebatamɪarɡatanɪnamɪdabakʼabulenɪakasumatoltʃaammalle?oɪsanɪnamaɪrawoɪarɡatʃanɪsetanɪtʃʼahaallawoɪerɡɪftanɪebatamɪarɡatanɪenamɪdabalenɪwolɪwoerɡisaakawanakasɪarɡatuammoɲapakesanɪdʒaladawandansatoltʃafɪerɡɪsafɪammowomaɪraineɡatinadubawanɡudoarɡatanɪɪlmanɪwakʼaɡubadʒirutatanɪwontɪakanatifɪinnɪworraɡalataimbennefɪworradabaleinahafɪakaabanɪkesanɪkaɡubalenɪnamanahuisanɪlenɪnamanahawannamainkʼorinawakʼɪlenɪwankesanɪɪnkʼoruwollalanamatɪimurinawakʼɪlenɪwollalaisanitɪɪmurunamaararamawakʼɪlenɪisaniararamawanamakennawakʼɪlenɪisanikennawanɡamɪtʃanɪkahumnanɪkaɪranɪdambalaharkakesanitɪnakʼanɪakumaɪsanɪnamabimɪtanɪakasumaisanibɪmanɪnamɪbarsɪsanɪnamaisabarsisuiraɪndʒiruammonamɪtʃʼahauftɪɡafawobaratekʼitenamaisabarsisetahaatinɪmalifɪhubailaobolesakankekesa ɪnifɪ?esonɪammallewanworranɪdʒedeaninɪɡaradakʼaɪsanɪnabarbadanɪammalledabakesanɪkesatɪdotanɪɡaraanɪdakʼuleɪsanɪdandetanɪinduftanɪdʒennanɪ?ahudinɪwandʒeteinnɪwandʒeduɡaraanɪdakʼudandetanɪinduftanɪdʒedaɪsiinnɪufɪɪdʒesufeda?esonɪwanworranɪdʒedeɪsanɪlafatanabatanɪaninɪɡubaɡadufeɪsanɪkalafatanatɪaninɪkalafatanatɪnitɪwontɪaninɪisaninɪdabakesanɪkesatɪdotanɪdʒedefɪtanaammalleɪsanɪdabakesanɪkesatɪɪnumadotanɪ?oakaaninɪduɡumaɪsumaduɡefatʃudɪdanɪworrɪwanɪsanɪdʒedeatinɪennukana?esonɪwandʒedenɪakumakʼaraaninɪisanitɪhimesunɪaninɪwanhedukʼabatadubadewankesanɪkʼoruammonamɪnaerɡekaduɡatɪammallewananinɪisairadaɡa?etʃʼahaallanamatɪhimaworrɪakainnɪababaneimɪdafannetanafɪ?esonɪwandʒedeeɡɪilmanamafannɪftanɪɡafasɪbetanɪakaanɪduɡumaɪsumaammalleakaaninɪufumanɪwointoltʃineammowanabanɪnabarsisetʃʼahaalladubadubetanɪammallenamanaerɡenuwolumanɪdʒirrainnɪkobatɪnaillakisuwananinɪɡu??atʃʼahaufawanɪsanɪɡammatʃisatʃʼahaallatoltʃufɪinnɪwankanadʒennanɪnamɪhedunɪisaduɡefateduba?esonɪ?ahudɪisaduɡefatenɪwandʒedeɪsanɪ?odubɪtɪ??aɡutanɪduɡumadʒarakɪ??atatanɪduɡaleimbaratanɪduɡalenɪɪsanɪbaltʃomsitɪworrɪwandʒedenɪnudalotaabrahamutɪtakaletissenamaɪntaneatɪakamɪɪsanɪbaltʃomsanɪnunɪdʒeta?esonɪwanworranɪdʒededuɡumawananinɪisaninɪdʒedunamɪdabatoltʃutʃʼahauftɪtissedabatɪtɪssenɪmanakesaɡu??atʃʼahaufaɪntetuammoilmɪɡu??atʃʼahaufata?oilmɪɪsanɪbaltʃomseakaduɡabaltʃomtanɪaninɪɪmbekhaakaɪsanɪdalotaabrahamuammoɪsanɪnaɪdʒesufetanɪwandubinɪtɪ??aɪsanɪkesaindʒɪrrefɪaninɪwanfullaabaki??atɪarɡedubadaisanɪlenɪwanabakesanɪiradaɡetanɪtoltʃɪtanɪworrɪwanɪsanɪdʒedeabanɪkennaabrahamu?esonɪwandʒedenɪ?oɪsanɪɪdʒolleabrahamutatanɪsilahudʒɪabrahamunɪtoltʃetoltʃɪtanɪammoammanaɪdʒesufetanɪnamawanduɡakawakʼaɪradaɡa?eisanitɪhimeabrahamunɪakasɪintoltʃineɪsanɪhudʒɪabakesanɪtoltʃɪtanɪdʒedeworrɪwandʒedenɪaberanɪnuindaltʃineabatokotʃʼahaallakʼamnawakʼa?esonɪwandʒedenɪ?osilawakʼɪabakesanɪtaheɪsanɪnadʒalatanɪwontɪakanatifɪaninɪɡarawakʼatɪbahe?adumaki??anɪɪndumneammoɪsatɪnaerɡeɪsanɪmafɪdubɪaninɪdʒedesunɪinhubannewonɪɪsanɪinhubannefɪdubɪtɪ??adɪkʼoledaɡa? aaninɪɡafakʼaraisanitɪɪnhimnewannuwolinɪdʒɪrufɪammoammaɡaranamanaerɡeɡalaɪsanɪkesatokolenɪkaɡaramɪdemtadʒedenaɡafatuɪndʒirutatulewananinɪwankanaisaninɪdʒedefɪlaɡudolalefatanɪaninɪammodubɪduɡaisanitɪhimaakaaninɪdemutɪiraɪsanɪdʒirawontɪakanatifɪ?oaninɪindeminɪkʼarkʼarsɪkanɪisaniɪndufuammo?oaninɪdemeaninɪisaisanierɡainnɪɡafadufuakadabɪdʒɪrufɪakaduɡanɪdʒɪrtufɪakawakʼɪwollalanamatɪmurunamaɡarsisehubatʃisaakadabɪdʒiruwanworrɪduɡefatʃudɪdufɪakaduɡanɪdʒirtuwananinɪɡaraabadakʼufɪdubaɪsanɪitɪdebɪtanɪnainarɡɪtanɪakawakʼɪwollalanamatɪmuruwanha??ulafatanawollalaitɪmuranifɪaninɪammallewanhedutaisaninɪdʒedukʼabaammoammadandetanɪimfudatanɪtatulehodʒdʒalubunɪduɡaduftuɪsitɪwanduɡaitɪɪsanɪkʼadʒeltʃaɪsinɪwanufɪindubatuammowandaɡetetʃʼahaufadubatɪwaneɡɪtanadufaleisanitɪhimtɪɪsinɪnaɡudiftewankɪ??afuteɪsanɪaɡarsiftɪwontɪabonɪkʼabutʃʼahauftɪtɪ??atanafɪaninɪɪsinɪwankɪ??afuteɪsanɪaɡarsiftɪisaninɪdʒedaeɡɪbultɪdikʼodebɪtanɪnainarɡɪtanɪammalleeɡɪbultɪdikʼodebɪtanɪnaaɡartanɪdʒennanɪdʒarɪɪsakaɡarɪwanwolinɪdʒedewontɪinnɪnunɪdʒedukuninɪmanɪinnɪeɡɪbultɪdikʼonainarɡɪtanɪdʒedaammalleeɡɪbultɪdikʼodebɪtanɪnaaɡartanɪnunɪdʒedainnɪammallewananinɪɡaraabadakʼadʒedefɪakasɪdʒedeworrɪdubawandʒedewontɪinnɪeɡɪbutɪdikʼodʒedetuninɪmanɪwaninnɪdʒedefɪimɪdafannedʒedanɪ?esonɪakaworrɪisaɡafatʃufedubennanɪwandʒedenɪwananinɪdʒedesunɪwolɡafatanɪtaeɡɪbultɪdikʼonainarɡɪtanɪammalleeɡɪbultɪdikʼodebɪtanɪnaaɡartanɪdʒedesunɪduɡumawananinɪisaninɪdʒeduɪsanɪlalefatanɪbotanɪammonamɪlafaiɡammadaɪsanɪilalefatanɪammolalaltɪtesanɪɡaraɡalteɡammadatatɪnadenɪ?otʃʼahainɪnfatuilalefatɪmaroɡu??anɪɪsinɪdetuɡahefɪammoeɡɪɪsinɪilmedetedebitelalalasunɪinkʼabatumaroɡammadadaimalafatɪdaltefɪtanafɪɪsanɪammalalalakʼabdanɪammoaninɪdebɪetɪɪsanɪarɡaɡaranɪkesanɪinɡammadaɡammadakesanɪkananamɪdandaeɪsanɪiraimfudatuɡu??asunɪwomanainɡafatanɪduɡumawananinɪisaninɪdʒeduwanɪsanɪmakʼaki??anɪabakadatanɪtʃʼahaufainnɪisanikennaarraduratɪtakamakʼaki??anɪwomainkadannekadadainarɡatanɪakaɡammadɪkesanɪkʼɪtauwankanaaninɪmammasanɪisanitɪhimeɡu??anɪaninɪdandaemammasanɪisanitɪindubanneɪndufaammodɪdesewanabaɪsanɪaɡarsisaɡafasɪmakʼaki??anɪkadatanɪammalleaninɪabaisanikadadaɪndʒeduwontɪakanatifɪabanɪufɪ?uɪsanɪdʒalatainnɪɪsanɪdʒalatawanɪsanɪnadʒalatanɪakaaninɪɡarawakʼatɪdufeduɡefatanifɪaninɪɡaraabatɪbahelafatɪdufeammalleaninɪɡaralafatɪbaheabatɪdebiadʒededʒarɪɪsawandʒedenɪɪlalɪatɪammamammasanɪindubatuammodidesitedubataammatanaakaatɪwantʃʼahaufabetunulahubannewannamɪwosiɡafatufɪɪnkʼabduwankanafɪakaatinɪɡarawakʼatɪdufteduɡefanna?esonɪwandʒedenɪɪsanɪammatanaduɡefatanɪɪlalaɡu??anɪɪsanɪɡarɡarɪfirfɪrfamtanɪɪndufaamma?adufenamɪtʃʼahauftɪɡarɡarɪfirfɪrfamekobanalakɪftanɪammoaninɪkobaɪndʒiruabawolumanɪdʒirrawankanaaninɪ?aisanitɪhimeakanakesanaɡa?aarɡatanɪlafakesadipuarɡatanɪammoɡaradʒabadaaninɪ?alafadabsade?esonɪdubɪtanadʒennanɪɡubaolmɪllatewandʒedeabohodʒdʒanɪ?aɡeteilmakankeɡudisɪakailmɪsiɡudisuatinɪhumnanamatʃʼahaufaira?aɪsakenniteakainnɪnamatʃʼahaufakaatinɪɪsakennitedʒɪrennaheɡerɪkennufɪammalledʒɪrennɪheɡerɪkanaakaatinɪwakʼatokotʃaduɡasibekhanɪ?esokrɪstolekaatinɪerɡitebekhanɪhudʒɪatinɪnakennitesunɪhobamnanɪaninɪ?alafakesatɪsiɡudiseeaboammatanaɡudinnanakennɪɡudinnanuatolaftɪinumaminɪwolinɪkʼamnusunɪaninɪmakʼakankenamaatinɪlafakesanakennite?aaɡarsiseworrɪkʼaranamumaketɪatɪlenɪ?aworranakenniteworrɪdubɪtantelaɡuteammawanatinɪnakennitetʃʼahaufaakaɪsinɪɡaraketɪbatu?abaratanɪaninɪdubɪatinɪnakennite?a?uworrakenneworrɪlenɪ?a?ufudateakaaninɪɡaraketɪbaheworrɪ?aakaɪsinɪduɡabekheammalleakaatinɪnaerɡite?a?uduɡefateaninɪmaroworratifɪkadadamaronamalafatɪinkadaduammonamaatɪnakennɪtefɪkadadawontɪakanatifɪworrɪketɪwontɪkɪ??atʃʼahauftɪketɪwontɪkankelenɪkɪ??aɡudinnɪkɪ??aworrakesamullataaninɪammatanalafakesaɪntauammodʒarɪkuninɪlafakesataaninɪɡarakankedufaeabokʼulkʼullodʒabennakankekaatinɪnakennitesuninɪworrakʼorkʼoradɪakaworrɪakumakennatakatahuhaɡaaninɪworrawolinɪdʒirumakʼakankekaatinɪnakennitesuninɪaninɪ?a?uworrakʼorkʼoradeanɪla?uworratissetokolenɪɪmbanneilmabadɪsunɪmaleakatafinɪɡutamtuammatanaaninɪɡarakankedufawankanalafakesatɪdʒedaakaɡammadɪkɪ??aɡaraworraɡutuaninɪdubɪt kasumawanɪsanɪnasuarɡatanifɪ?ahudinɪammawakʼatʃʼahaakʼasudidɪakaworrɪlenɪammanasuwakʼaarɡatuwontɪakanatifɪwakʼɪnamatʃʼahaufa?atʃʼahaubuworrakesatɪhideakanamatʃʼahaufanahuakumatafinɪdʒetuentukʼalbɪabobekhaentudandaeisaɡorsaakainnɪɡalatadebɪsufɪtanafɪobole?anɪtɪ??amaronasuwakʼaɡudotifɪaninɪɪsanɪkadadaakasoriodʒirtuwakʼaufɪbasahudʒɪɪsahodʒadaisaɡammatʃisatuninɪadaduɡataɪsanɪtolfatʃumaltanɪadalafatanadʒalatanɪɡulaindeminaammohawakʼɪɡarakesanifɪkʼalbɪtesanɪdʒidʒɪrutɪ?osɪfedɪwakʼabaratanɪwandansakaisaɡammatʃisakakʼitemaroebawakʼɪnakennefɪaninɪwanɪsanɪtʃʼahaufanɪdʒeduufɪsadanɪufɪinɡudɪsinaammohereɡakesanɪkesatɪufɪdɪkʼesaammallenamɪtʃʼahauftɪduɡefatʃawakʼɪɪsakenneɡulahaufɪkʼorutɪnafɪnamamitahedukʼabaammallemɪtanɪtuninɪtʃʼahauftɪhudʒɪufɪkʼabdɪakasumaatonunamaheduletanekristokesanunɪtʃʼahauftɪnamatokoammalleakumamɪtanɪnafatʃʼahauftɪwoltɪedʒitunulenɪwoltɪedʒinatanafɪwankʼamnutʃʼahaufanɪebawakʼɪnukenneɡulahodʒatʃumalle?ohudʒinɪtennadubɪwakʼaodesitɪtateduɡefatʃawakʼɪnukenneɡulaodesumalle?onamahodʒanneakadansahodʒatʃumalle?onamabarsimneakadansabarsisumalle?onamadibɪdʒabesineakadansadʒabesumallenamɪwanharkakʼabunamanɪɡahufeduhaardʒomanɪɡahunɪnamɪnamadurademuhaakadansadurademunamɪnamanahuhaɡammadanɪnahudʒalaltɪhawanduɡatatutɪwanhamtudʒibawandansadʒabesaakaobole?anɪkristokesawolɪdʒaladaammallewolɪtʃʼahaeraakadansahodʒadaufumaintatainaɡaraowanɪabohodʒadaabdinɪtesanɪɡammadaisanikenninaɡarɡalaarɡatanɪobsahodʒdʒatʃʼahaufawakʼa?amadawankʼabdaninɪobole?anɪɡarɡalakʼabdukʼarkʼaraworrakesanitɪkessumabultʃaworraɡammaduwolinɪɡammadaworrabohuwolinɪbohanamatʃʼahaufanɪwoldakʼaufɪinɡudɪsinaammohudʒɪɪsanɪdikʼesɪtulehodʒadakʼaroufɪinsehina?onamɪwanhamtuɪsanɪtoltʃewanhamtuisaintoltʃinawannamɪtʃʼahauftɪdansasehutʃʼahaallatoltʃahaɡadandetanɪɡamakesaninɪnamatʃʼahaufanaɡa?anɪwolinɪtahaloimbafatinadʒalanɪtɪ??aammohadalansunɪwakʼahaloɪsanɪbaftutɪwontɪakanatifɪtafinɪwandʒetuanatɪhalobasaabonɪakanadʒededʒetɪammoakumatafinɪdʒetu?oɲapɪkankebelakʼabateɲatʃisɪ?oinnɪdebukʼabatebɪsanɪobasɪ?owankanatoltʃitetʃʼahail
