?atokodʒabasehumaroabotifɪsehanamɪwantʃʼahaufaɲatulenɪmaroabotifɪɲatawaninnɪatosaɡalesunɪiɲatinɪwakʼaɡalatadebɪsufɪnamɪsaɡaleɡarɪɲatʃudidulenɪmaroabotifɪdidainnɪlenɪwakʼaɡalatadebɪsafɪnamɪufumadʒɪratuɪndʒiruammallenamɪufumaduɪndʒiru?odʒɪranneabofɪdʒɪranna?odoneleabofɪdona?odʒirannefɪ?odoneledubanukaabotɪwontɪakanatifɪkrɪstonɪakanamadʒɪrufɪkadueleabatahufɪduekaetanafɪatinɪmafɪobolesakankekʼorta?okhanɪatinɪmafɪobolesakanketuffatanunɪtʃʼahauftɪfulawakʼaduraedʒannaakainnɪnukʼoruwontɪakanatifɪtafinɪwandʒetuabonɪwandʒeduwakʼɪanumanamalekadɪbinɪɪndʒiruammallenamɪtʃʼahauftɪnaduratɪdʒilbɪfateakaaninɪwakʼahimatanafɪnunɪtʃʼahauftɪwantoltʃinewakʼaduratɪhɪmatʃumalletanafɪdubawolɪkʼoritɪlakimnafullaɪsiwankanakutannawanobolesakennaɡufatʃisedabakesabusaintoltʃinubekhɪaninɪabo?esobekhuakawontɪtokolenɪturɪɪnkʼamnenatɪhimaammo?onamɪwanwontɪtokoturɪkʼabduseheɪsaturɪkʼabdɪ?owontɪatinɪɲatuobolesakankedukubsitedʒalaltɪsikesaɪndʒirtusaɡalenɪatinɪɲatunamakrɪstonɪduefɪimballesinɪwontɪatinɪwandansasetumakʼahamainhoratinɪwontɪakanatifɪfinnɪwakʼawanɲatanɪduɡanɪnitɪammoduɡafɪnaɡa?afɪɡammadalubunɪkʼulkʼullonɪnamakennitunamɪkarakanaɡulakristohodʒatuwakʼaɡammatʃisenamalekʼufsatanafɪnuhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufawannaɡa?anukennafɪtawolɪdʒabesitɪbarbadumallesaɡaledʒetanɪwanwakʼɪtoltʃei?akinasaɡaleɡosatʃʼahaufaɲatʃumalanɪammosaɡalenamadibɪdabakesabuftuɲatʃuhɪmmallewontɪkʼadʒelaakafonifɪdadifɪwandibɪtaobolesakankedabakesabuftulaɡatanɪadawankanataduɡefatuufifɪwakʼatʃʼahaallatɪdofadua??ananamasunɪka?owanɡaranɪɪsadʒalatutoltʃewollalaufitɪɪmurreammo?oinnɪwanɲatuɡaratokonɪɪɲannewakʼɪwollalaitɪmurahodʒdʒainnɪɲatumaroduɡefatʃanɪwaninnɪtoltʃesunɪbiraindʒɪrrefɪwontɪduɡefatʃanɪbiraɪndʒirretʃʼahauftɪdabanuworrɪduɡefatʃadʒabdukʼabulafinnaworralalafaobsineulfinnaɪsanɪbatʃumalleufɪtʃʼahaallaɡammatʃisuhɪmmalleammonamɪtʃʼahauftɪhaobolesaufɪkʼarkʼareɡammatʃisuakaduɡefatʃakesatɪisadʒabesanɪwontɪakanatifɪkrɪstonɪufɪtʃʼahaallainɡammatʃimneammoakumatafinɪdʒetuarabɪnamɪsiarabse?anatɪdebiewontɪakanatifɪwantafɪkesatɪtafanɪtʃʼahaufaakanub ?abesisu?odudanɪtʃʼahaufanakʼabadadʒedewontɪakanatifɪhaɡaabonɪdufutɪ?okʼitakanaɲatanɪmudunutanakesadudanɪtʃʼahaufaɪsanɪduisaɪsaodesɪtanɪtanafɪ?onamɪadabahamanɪkʼitaaboɲate?okhanɪmudunuaboduɡeinnɪ?anafaabotifɪdiɡaaboletɪdabenamɪtʃʼahauftɪufɪkʼorkʼoratʃumaledubakʼitaɲatemudunuhaduɡuwontɪakanatifɪ?oinnɪulfinnanafaabohodʒdʒainnɪsoratuɪnɡarre?oɲateduɡutʃʼahaufakʼorsumaufɪtinɪdufamarowankanatifɪisaninɪhedunɪfa??adabdanɪlaftanɪhaɡɪtokolenɪrawatanɪnu?osilakʼarafiteufɪɪlalekʼorsumawakʼakesaɪndunuammoabotɪnukʼorenukʼadʒeltʃaakanamalafawolinɪnuɪnkʼorretanafɪobole?anɪtɪ??a?owolwoldetanɪsaɡaleaboɲatanɪwolɪeɡa?onamɪbelakʼabatehamanaufitɪsaɡaleɲatuaka?owolwoldetanɪkʼorsumawakʼakesaɪnsennewanhafekanɪaninɪhodʒdʒadufumɪdasaammawankennitɪlubutaɪsanɪnaɡafatanɪaninɪakaɪsanɪwanɪsikaduɡabaratanɪfedaobole?anɪɪsanɪimbetanɪakaɡafaɪsanɪwakʼaɪmbennewontɪharkanɪbotʃanɪtawomaɪmbaneɪsanɪmohatekarairaɪsanɪɡorsitehubatʃumaltanɪakanamɪlubunɪwakʼademtunɪtokolenɪdandae?esoinabareammallenamɪtokolenɪdandae?esonɪaboɪndʒedu?olubunɪkʼulkʼullonɪɪsanɪdemtumalekarahedutɪkawoinɪhodʒatanɪdʒiraammoabotokotʃahodʒatanɪhumnahedutɪtawoinɪhodʒatanɪdʒiraammowakʼatokotʃʼahaallatɪhumnawoinɪhodʒatanɪnamatʃʼahaufakennanamatʃʼahaufabesisalubutokokennanɪakawolɪwobahulubunɪnamatokodubɪkʼalbɪkennitɪammonamadibɪlubumanɪsunɪdubɪhubatʃakennɪtifɪlubunɪnamatokoduɡefatʃakennitekadibɪtʃʼahaɪrrumakennɪtifɪtokodʒabennainnɪwanmamatinɪtoltʃukennitekadibɪdʒabennadubɪwakʼatinɪdubatukennɪtifɪammallenamadibɪdʒabennainnɪkennitɪlubuɪraduftefɪtaɪraindufinɪhimukennɪtifɪnamatokodʒabennaafanɪdibɪdubatukennitekadibɪkʼalbɪafanɪsunɪdebisukennɪtifɪammolubutakatitɪwankanatʃʼahaufatoltʃaɪsinɪakumafetunamatʃʼahaufakennɪakaakakennitɪakasumanutʃʼahaufa?ahudifɪɡosadɪbiletɪssefɪbaltʃale?alubunɪnafatokotʃakanatɪnubatifteammallenutʃʼahaufa?alubutakakʼufsanɪnafɪmitatokotʃʼahaallaɪnkʼabuammomitahedukʼaba?osilamilɪaninɪharkanitɪtanafɪmitanafatɪnitɪufinɪdʒedesuninɪmitatahuindowartu?osilaɡurrɪaninɪilanitɪtanafɪaninɪmitanafatɪnitɪufinɪdʒedetuninɪmitanafatahuindowar duftukrɪstonɪha??otafɪdʒabennafɪhumnatʃʼahaufadabsatetɪfinnatʃʼahaufaharkawakʼaabatɪkennakrɪstonɪfidumalehaɡawakʼɪɲapatʃʼahaufadabsatemilaɪsadʒalanakʼutɪɲapɪeɡekʼɪtisuballesanɪduisawontɪakanatifɪtafinɪwandʒetuwakʼɪ?awantʃʼahaufamilaɪsadʒalanakʼe?owantʃʼahaufadʒedanɪwakʼɪkawantʃʼahaufamilakristodʒalanakʼekesaɪndʒirusunɪwanɡafɪkʼabatɪnitɪ?owantʃʼahaufamilakristodʒalanakʼanɪ?osɪilmɪlenɪwakʼadʒalaufɪka?akawantʃʼahaufaisadʒalanakʼedubawakʼɪwantʃʼahaufakaratʃʼahaufanɪfidaworramaronamaduetifɪbatɪsanɪmanɪtoltʃanɪreworrɪmanɪtoltʃufeda?oakɪworrɪnamɪdueduisakesaɪnkaudʒeduduɡatatemafɪmaroworraduetifɪbatɪfamanɪrenumanifuhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufaɡarɡaladuakesaufɪsensimnaobole?anɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufaduatɪharkanakʼabawananinɪmarotesanifɪkristo?esoabokennakesatɪufɪɡudɪsufɪaninɪwankanadʒedaatosilaaninɪefesokesatɪbɪnensaalahademarofedɪnamatifɪaninɪmanɪarɡade?osilanamaduedʒirennatɪɪnkamnemammasɪtokowandʒeduarraɲannedunnaborɪɪndonainsobaminawahelɪhamanɪadabadansai?akakʼalbɪtesanitɪdebiakarakesanɪkadabalakisanamɪɡarɪwanwakʼaɪmbekhuaninɪakaɪsanɪtʃʼahaertanifɪdʒedanamɪtokoheɡerɪakanaɡafatanamadueakaminɪkasanɪnafaakamɪhorataatinɪdalle?omɪdanɪfatʃaftehaɡabikʼɪlanitɪɪmbanɪwontɪatinɪobritusuninɪsaɲumaheɡerɪdarɡa?e?okhanɪmɪdanɪdibɪammomɪdanɪbahudʒirunitɪwakʼatɪnafafedumɪdanɪsunɪkennaisumatɪnafamalefɪkennafɪfonɪwantʃʼahaufaakatakaindʒɪranɪnamɪfonɪufɪkʼababɪnensɪkaufɪkʼabasimpɪrrenɪkaufɪkʼabdɪkʼurtumɪlenɪkaufɪkʼabdɪammallenafalafatifɪkaɡubatɪdʒiramidaɡumtɪtalafatifɪtaɡubalenɪɪndʒirtɪadunɪmidaɡumaufɪkʼabdɪdʒɪlenɪmidaɡumaufɪkʼabaurdʒɪlenɪmidaɡumaufɪkʼabdɪwontɪakanatifɪurdʒɪkesaleɪsinɪtʃʼahauftɪtakanitɪɡafaworraduedʒirennatɪkasanɪakanarefɪawalanɪwanduatɪhodʒdʒakasanɪitɪdebieɪnduhodʒdʒaawalanɪfulɪhamafɪlafaɡafakasanɪmɪdaɡadansahodʒdʒaawalanɪnafadalotaɡafakasanɪnafalubu?onafɪdalotadʒɪratenafɪlubulenɪɪndʒirawontɪakanatifɪtafinɪwandʒetunamakʼaraadamunamadʒiruumanɪammoadamunɪmummelubudʒɪrennanamakennitulubunɪduratɪɪnduftuammonafɪdalotadufetɪdubalubunɪfanaduftɪadamukʼarabɪ??elafatinɪumanɪadamunɪlamesoɡubadufeworrɪbɪ??eakanamabi??enɪumanɪdʒiraworrɪɡubaakanamaɡubadufedʒiraakumaammanamabɪ??efakannuakasumaeɡɪtananamaɡubafakannawontɪaninɪdʒetʃudʒirutanaobole?anɪwontɪnafafɪdiɡakʼabakʼodafinnawakʼainarɡatuammallewontɪduadandeteduufɪindowartuakailalɪfsatuhodʒdʒamaɡalatamummedanɪwontɪakanatifɪhodʒdʒadanɪworradueakadebɪanɪɪndoneduisakesakasanɪnunɪtʃʼahauftɪdʒidʒɪramnawontɪhobawaninhobaneke?atʃumaltewontɪduawanɪndoneke?atʃumaltedubahodʒdʒawontɪhobawaninhobaneke?ateammallehodʒdʒawontɪduawanɪndoneke?ateɡafasɪduɡanɪtafɪmullatɪtadualalikʼɪmsanɪdabsatʃanɪ?akʼɪtoftedʒetueduisadukubɪtinɪtantemeduisɪdʒabennanamanɪdukubsudabairaarɡatadabɪlenɪdʒabennaufiserairaarɡataammoɡalatɪwakʼaimbadinɪkadabsatʃanukennumaroabokenna?esokristotifɪtanafɪobole?anɪtɪ??adʒabadaedʒadahudʒɪabohodʒdʒatʃʼahaufahodʒadadʒabesawontɪakanatifɪɪsanɪimbetanɪhudʒinɪabotaɪsanɪhodʒatanɪdandetelafatɪɪnhaftuɡu??akʼarakatorbanɪtʃʼahaufaisaninɪtʃʼahauftɪhorɪlafaka?umaltanɪwanarɡatanɪɡulaaka?oaninɪdufehorɪwoltɪɪnɡurreeɡɪaninɪdufedʒaraɪsanɪfohatanitɪtatabekennehorɪsunɪ?erusalemuɡesadʒedanɪ?oanɪlenɪworrawolinɪdemumalewolɪ?anaaninɪbaradamotʃatʃʼahaufafullatesanɪtadubaɪsanɪworeɡanatoltʃɪtanɪaninɪɪmaltutɪ??ademafullademufedutʃʼahaufaaninɪhaɡadikʼatokotʃʼahaallaɪsanɪbiratauɪmfeduhaɡaɡudaɪsanɪwolinɪtaufeda?oabonɪdʒedebalbaltɪhudʒɪdʒabdunɪhodʒadu?aarmatɪnabanamteatonamɪnanɪmorkuhedunɪdʒiratelenamɪtokolenɪisaintufatinɪammalleworeɡaɪsatoltʃaakainnɪɪmaltuufɪnaɡa?anɪdemeɡarakɪ??adebiuwontɪakanatifɪaninɪobole?anɪwolinɪisaeɡudʒiraammawanobolesakennaapoloaninɪɡudoitɪdubadeakainnɪobole?anɪdibɪwolinɪɡarakesanɪdakʼuammoinnɪammatanadɪkʼoledemuɪmfedu?okʼomnɪarɡateɪndemakurfotaduɡefatʃatesanɪkesadʒabadainsodatinadʒabadahudʒɪtesanɪtʃʼahaufadʒalalanɪtoltʃaaninɪɪsanɪkadadaobole?anɪtɪ??aworraakanakanatʃʼahaakʼasaɡula?aammallenamaakaworrahodʒateɡarɡalutʃʼahaufaledufisɪstefanatifɪkafortunatotifɪkaakaikoɡudonaɡammatʃise?afullaɪsanɪɪndʒirrebuanɪammalleɡaranadʒabesanɪakumaisanileɡaradʒabesanɪnamaakanakanatʃʼahaufaulfesumalanɪobole?anɪtʃʼahauftɪnaɡa?aɪsanɪdamtɪdunɡoob kennaisanitɪmullimneɡarakennaɪsanɪduraɪnhinneisanitɪɡarakesanɪhidemaleaninɪakawanɪsanɪɪdʒolletɪ??aisanitɪdubadawannuɪsanɪsenuisanɪlenɪnusehaɡarakesanɪnubananamainduɡefatɪninɪhaɡatakainhodʒatinawontɪsunɪɪntatuduɡafɪwollalɪwahelawolɪtahuindandaɪfsafɪdukantɪlenɪwolinɪtatɪhɪ??okrɪstofɪʃetanɪwoldakʼuindandanɪnamaduɡefatefɪkainduɡefatinɪmalwolɪɪrakʼabanɪmanɪwakʼawanharkanɪbotʃanɪkaworrɪwakʼaɪmbennekadatunɪwolɪntanɪnumanawakʼadʒɪrutɪakumawakʼɪufinɪdʒedeaninɪmanakɪ??aworrawolinɪdʒaradeworrawolinɪtaaninɪwakʼaworrataheworrɪlenɪɡumɪtɪ??atahaworralakisabɪra?awanturɪkʼabaintukʼina?osɪaninɪɪsanɪfudadaɪsanɪɪlmanɪtɪ??atadiratifɪtadubratatanɪaboɡudanɪakanadʒedakakhutanatʃʼahaufanukhakhatanɪdʒalanɪtɪ??atanafɪwannafafɪlubuturesalaɡannakʼulkʼullomnesodawakʼakesataumalleɡarakesanɪkesatɪfullanumɪdasanuwollalanamutuintoltʃinenamuimballesine?okhanɪwomanamairaimfudanneaninɪwankanaakawollalaisanitɪmuruɪndʒeduakumaaninɪkʼaradʒedewannuɡudoɪsanɪdʒalannufɪnuhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufawolinɪdʒirra?odʒɪrrufɪ?odoneleaninɪɡudowankesanɪbekhamarotesanifɪufɪkorsaɡarɡalakennatʃʼahaufakesatɪaninɪɡaraɪllafuammoɡammadanɪkʼilɪtamaammowakʼɪkaworraɡaralafudʒabesunudʒabesetitonutɪarɡedufisaɪsatʃʼahaallanitɪammoinnɪakaɪsanɪisadʒabesɪtanɪnutɪodeseammalleinnɪakaɪsanɪɡudonaarɡufetanifɪakaɪsanɪmarotɪ??alalefatanifɪammalleakaɪsanɪkurfodʒɪrtanɪakanakʼarkʼartanɪnatɪhimetanafɪaninɪɡudoɡammadeatotatabenɪtɪ??atakʼaraɪsanɪlalefatʃɪfteleaninɪwantafefɪɪnɡabu?osilaakatatabenɪsunɪhaɡadikʼatokotʃʼahaallaɪsanɪlalefatʃiftearɡeufiɡabaammoammaaninɪinɡammadamaroɪsanɪlalefatʃɪsenitɪammomarolalefatʃanɪtesanɪdandɪtesanɪɪraɪsanɪɡorsɪtefɪlalefatʃasunɪwakʼatɪhudʒinɪhodʒateammonuwomaɪsanɪintoltʃinelalefatʃawakʼɪhudʒinɪhodʒatesunitɪɡarakesanɪɡarɡaltʃebafamaisanikennemarowansunɪtifɪnuufɪinɡabinuammolalefatʃanɪnamaduɪsanɪduftɪwanwakʼɪlalefatʃatesanɪtoltʃeɪlalaɪsanɪdʒabatanɪufɪdubatanɪdalantanɪrifatanɪnaheredanɪowɪtanɪakaduɡatoltʃanɪbarbadanɪdubɪtanatʃʼahaufakesaakanamawollalaɪnkʼamneufɪmullɪftanɪtanafɪatoaninɪtatabesunɪtafeleaninɪmaronamawollalatoltʃefɪmaronamawollalaitɪtoltʃanɪfileɪntamneammowonɪaninɪtafefɪakafulawakʼaduratɪakaɪsanɪnudʒalatanɪdɪdeseaɡarsisumarowankanatifɪnuɡaradʒabannenuɡaratʃʼahaallaindʒabanneammoɡammadatitoarɡɪnanɪɡudoufileɡammanneɪsanɪtʃʼahauftɪtitokʼarkʼartanɪɡammatʃɪftanɪaninɪɡudowankesanɪɪsatɪodeseisanɪlenɪnaintʃersinenuhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufa?aduɡaisanitɪdubanneakasumawontɪnutɪtonɪdʒenne?aduɡatatedʒalaltɪinnɪɪsanɪdʒalatu?aitɪdaramteduba?oinnɪakaisaninɪtʃʼahauftɪkurfodʒɪrtanɪkʼabateakaɪsanɪsodafɪnasunɪisafudatanɪaninɪɡudoɡammadawananinɪdandaeɡaratokonɪɪsanɪhereɡadufɪobole?anɪnuwanebitɪwakʼaɡumɪmakedonɪatɪtoltʃiteɪsanɪbesisufenaɡarɡalɪworrɪarɡateɡudoworrailalateammoɡudoɡammadanɪardʒomanɪnamawokennanɪatohi??e?ɪtahanilewananinɪisanitɪhimuhaɡumadandanɪkennanɪammallewansunɪiraworrɪfedɪufɪtinɪakaɡumɪ?udeakʼarkʼaranɪɡudonukadatenuwanworrɪwankanatoltʃuɪnsenekʼarafiteaboufɪkennanɪlamesolefedɪwakʼaɡulanuleufɪkennanɪtanafɪnutitokahudʒɪtanaitɪke?atekadanneakainnɪduradabreɪsanɪkʼarkʼarehudʒɪdʒalalatanawolinɪhobaftanɪɪsanɪwankʼabdanɪtʃʼahaufakesaɡudodure?ɪduɡefatʃafɪhasafɪhubatʃafɪkʼarkʼarsaakatʃʼahaufatifɪdʒalalatennakesaletɪtanafɪnuɪsanɪkadannaakahudʒɪdʒalalatanakesaletɪdʒabatanɪaninɪseraisanitoltʃutɪɪndʒiruammohaɡabi??itɪdɪbinɪkʼarkʼarufeteɪsanɪaɡarsisedubaakadʒalaltɪtesanɪtaduɡaarɡufedaɪsanɪebaabokenna?esokristoimbetanɪinnɪduresaammomarotesanifɪufɪhi??omseakahi??umaufɪtinɪɪsanɪduromsuwankanaaninɪakanahereɡasilairaisaniɡomtɪ?owanɡannadabreitɪke?atanɪhobaftanɪɪsanɪworrakʼarakawankanatoltʃesunɪtʃʼahaallanitɪammoɪsanɪworrumakʼarakafedɪufɪtinɪwankanatoltʃufededurademahobasadʒabadaakaakumaitɪke?atanɪhobaftanɪammallewankʼabdaninɪhobasa?oɪsanɪɡudowokennufetanɪwakʼɪwanɪsanɪkʼabdanɪkaɪsanɪbaftanɪfudatawanɪsanɪɪnkʼamneimbarbaduaninɪbaulfonamadibɪɪrafudeɪsanɪiraka?utɪɪndʒiruammowanɪsanɪammaɡudowokʼabdanifɪnamaɡarɡalakʼabukʼarkʼarumaltanɪ?osɪɡafaɪsanɪɡarɡalakʼabdanɪammoworrɪwanɡudokʼabuworrɪlenɪɪsanɪkʼarkʼarakarakananɪnamatʃʼahaufawolkʼɪtesanɪakumatafinɪdʒetunamɪnamatʃʼahaufairaɡurateɡudoɪnkʼabuarɡeammokadikʼoɡurateɡud ʃanɪtesanɪɡudatenuhudʒɪhaɡasɪiradansahodʒatʃudandennuammokʼodawakʼɪnuhereɡeɡula?osɪdandenneodudansalafaɪsanɪdubakesaletɪodesinaakanuhudʒɪobruabadibɪkesatɪhodʒatanifɪufɪinɡudimnewontɪakanatifɪnamɪ?owakʼɪwanɪsadansahereɡutʃʼahaalladansataha?oinnɪwanufɪdansahereɡunitɪ?oaninɪdikʼodalletahelenaobsaaninɪɪsanɪkadadaaninɪmarotesanifɪhɪnafaakumawakʼɪmarotesanɪhɪnafuwontɪakanatifɪɪsanɪɪntalaɡametaaninɪnamatokotʃʼahaallakennefakatanɪnamɪsunɪlenɪkristoaninɪinsodadaheɡerɪkʼalbinɪtesanɪhamatedʒalalakristokʼulkʼullolakɪftanɪakumabofɪhawaɪmaltenɪsobeɪsanɪnamadufewankristodibɪisanitɪhasautʃʼahaufaimfudatanɪkanuisanitɪhasomnenitɪammalleɪsanɪlubufɪodudibɪtalubufɪodudansanuisanitɪodesineimfakannefudatanɪwananɪsehuaninɪworraerɡatuufinɪdʒedusunɪkaratokolenɪmandanitɪaninɪheɡerɪɡudodubatʃuɪmbekhuammohubatʃaɪnumakʼabawankananu?amarotʃʼahaufafɪkaratʃʼahaufanɪisanitɪhimneaninɪɡafaodudansatawakʼaisanitɪodesewomatokoleɪsanɪiraimfudanneaninɪufɪdɪkʼeseakaɪsanɪɡudisuwankanaaninɪwollalatoltʃeɡafaaninɪdʒidutesanɪhodʒadeɡumɪfulladɪbitɪhorɪnabaseaninɪworradurawofudadeisaninɪkʼarkʼareɡafaɪsanɪwolinɪdʒiruaninɪ?ohorɪfedeleɪsanɪinɡarɡaltʃinewontɪakanatifɪobole?anɪmakedoniaduftewananinɪfedutʃʼahaufanakenniteakumadurɪtoltʃeheɡerileɪntoltʃaaninɪhaɡumadʒirubaulfoisanitɪɪmfahuduɡakristotinɪkakhadahaɡaaninɪlafaaka?atanakesadʒirunamɪtokolenɪdandaedubɪtɪ??atanaindaresuaninɪmafɪwankanadʒedamaroaninɪɪsanɪindʒalannefɪakaaninɪɪsanɪdʒaladuwakʼɪlenɪɪmbekhaaninɪwanammatoltʃukanadurademetoltʃufedaakaerɡatunɪdɪbinɪtanɪkʼomnɪarɡateakakesanɪhodʒannadʒeteufɪinodesineworrɪsuninɪerɡatuduɡatɪnitɪworrɪerɡatudaratawanhudʒɪufɪdaradubateerɡatukristotaduɡaufɪfakesitudubinɪtunɪmamaɪnkʼabduʃetanɪlenɪufɪdʒɪdʒireerɡatuɪfsaufɪtoltʃuindandatanafɪ?oerɡatunɪɪsaufɪdʒɪdʒirteerɡatuduɡaufɪtoltʃɪtelewandɪkʼoledʒabatatɪnitɪɡafamummewanworramalearɡatanɪaninɪdubɪtanaammalleitɪdebiedʒedanamɪtokolenɪdallenainsehinɪammo?onasetanileakumadallenafudadaakaaninɪwandikʼotokotaufinɪɡudisuarɡaduwontɪaninɪammadubadukuninɪwanabonɪfedunitɪwanufɪɡudɪsitɪkanaaninɪ batoltʃeammohamennasunɪkaakadabaalɡalomatifɪkadarahamtuiraindebinɪbohuaninɪworradurɪdabatoltʃefɪnamakanɪtʃʼahaufaɡorsufedaaninɪdurile?adʒedeɡafaɪmaltulamesoɡarakesanɪdufeammoammalleɪndʒedakaammaɪsanɪɪrafaɡodʒiruɡafaaninɪtakatanaammalledufunamɪtokolenɪɡarɡaladuraɪmbahuhodʒdʒasunɪakakrɪstonɪafanɪki??anɪdubatuinarɡɪtanɪ?oinnɪwoɪɪsanɪtoltʃuinnɪlafanitɪammodʒabennaufɪaɡarsisaatolafɪnnanɪmaskalɪɡubatɪisaidʒesaniledʒabennawakʼatinɪammadʒiranulenɪisakesalalafoammodʒabennawakʼakaɡarakesanɪdʒɪrunɪisawolinɪtennaufɪɪlalaufɪkʼoraakaduɡefatʃakesatetanɪufɪaɡartanɪɪsanɪakakristo?esonɪɪsanɪkesadʒirubetu?oɪsanɪufɪindʒɪbatinɪheɡerɪakanuufɪindʒɪbatinɪinaɡartanɪnuwakʼakadannaakaɪsanɪdabakesaɪnsenneakanuwandansahodʒannedabsanneaɡarsiftunitɪammoakaɪsanɪwankʼadʒelatoltʃɪtanɪatonunamaufɪdʒɪbatefakannelenudandenneduɡawakʼai?akinuammoinhodʒannafɪnuhodʒdʒalamneammoɪsanɪdʒabatanɪinɡammannatanafɪnuwakʼakadannaakaɪsanɪkʼitetatanɪmarowankanatifɪaninɪtatabetanaatofaɡoɪsanɪiradʒiradeleisanitɪtafaaka?odufuaninɪdʒabennaabonɪnakennenɪisanitɪindalannedʒabennaisaninɪdʒabesukaisaninɪballesunitɪammaobole?anɪtɪ??anaɡa?atɪwankʼɪtomabarbadawaninnɪdʒedutʃʼahaakʼasawoldakʼanaɡa?anɪwolinɪta?osɪwakʼɪnaɡa?atifɪkadʒalalaɪsanɪwolinɪtadunɡoobole?anumatinɪwoldunɡadaɡuminɪwakʼatʃʼahauftɪnaɡa?aisanidamtɪebitɪabokenna?esokristodʒalaltɪtawakʼawoldakʼisɪlubukʼulkʼullolenɪhanutʃʼahaufawolinɪtaumakʼanɪkɪ??apauloka?amitʃɪakaaninɪerɡatutahunamanɪindufinɪ?okhanɪnamairaindufinɪammo?esokrɪstofɪwakʼaabakaduisakesaɪsakaseɪradufeobole?anɪarmanawolinɪdʒirtutʃʼahauftɪɡumɪɡalatiadʒirtunaɡa?adamtɪwakʼaabakennafɪabo?esokrɪstonɪebafɪnaɡa?aisanikenninaakadalotahamakanakesanubasukrɪstonɪmarodabakennatifɪufɪbasefedɪwakʼaabakennatɪɡuteɡudinnɪhaɡaheɡerileɡarawakʼatahinnaaminɪɪsanɪɡudonamamsɪftanɪ?osunamaebakristotinɪɪsanɪ?amelakɪftanɪodudibɪɡula?atanɪodunɪdɪbinɪɪndʒirtuammoaninɪwankanawannamɪɡarɪkaɪsanɪɡarɡaltʃeodukristoɡaraɡaltʃufedudʒɪrufɪdʒedeammo?onu?okhanɪmalaɪkanɪɡubabateodutanuɪsanɪbarsimneɪsanɪiraɡorsitetadibɪisanitɪodesitenamɪsuninɪha woldakʼɪsanɪisaniduftunaɡa?ɪkrɪstonɪnamakennuhaɡarakesanɪkʼorutɪwontɪakanatifɪwakʼɪɡaratokonɪnaɡa?akanatɪɪsanɪtʃʼahaufa?ameammalleɡalataisadebisadubinɪkristohaɡudateɡarakesanɪkesahatetukʼalbɪtʃʼahaufanɪwolbarsisawolɡorsawakʼafarsasirbaɪsasirbafaruɪsadahadaɡarakesaninɪwakʼaɡalatadebisawanɪsanɪdʒetanifɪwantoltʃɪtanɪtʃʼahaufakesamakʼaabo?esotinɪtoltʃaammallemakʼaisatinɪwakʼaabaɡalatadebisawantoltʃɪtanɪtʃʼahaufakesaɡaratokonɪtoltʃaakawannamainhodʒanneammoabohodʒatanɪkʼabadaabonɪɡalataisanidebisawaninnɪɡumɪufitɪolka?einarɡatanɪwontɪakanatifɪabanɪɪsanɪhodʒatanifɪkristonamawanhamtutoltʃuabaufɪtananilewanhamtuisatoltʃanɪwakʼɪnamatʃʼahaufaakatokotuhereɡahodʒdʒatʃʼahaufakadadaindadabinailafinawakʼaɡalatadebisanulewakʼakadadaakainnɪbalbalanubanenudubɪɪsaodesinewandossakristohimnumarowansunɪtifɪaninɪhɪdansakesadʒirawakʼakadadaakaaninɪkarakʼadʒelanɪodesenamɪhubatu?ohasoftanɪdubɪdansamɪoftuhasaammallenamawoɪɪsanɪɡafatekʼadʒeltʃadebɪsafɪmarowankanatifɪaninɪisaɡarakesanɪerɡaakainnɪwannukesadʒirruisanitɪhimeɪsanɪɡammatʃisuonesɪmonɪobolesakennakaduɡakaɡumɪtesanɪkesadʒiruwahelaɪsatɪwannukesadʒirrutʃʼahaufaworratɪisanitɪodesa?esonɪka?ustodʒedanɪlenɪnaɡa?adamaworrɪ?ahudɪkaduɡefatekafinnawakʼatɪdʒedenuwolinɪhodʒatudʒarakanatʃʼahaallaworrɪɡudonakʼarkʼareaninɪwanhudʒɪinnɪisanihodʒateisanitɪhimuindandataɡumɪlaodikɪafɪhierapolilelukatʃʼahaɪresakennatifɪdemanɪnaɡa?aɪsanɪdamanɪobole?anɪlaodɪkiakesadʒirtunaɡa?anufudaammallenɪmfafɪɡumɪmanaɪsikesatɪwolwoldetuleeɡɪtatabetanasomtanɪkʼorkʼoradaakaɡumɪlaodikɪaletɪsomanɪtatabeɡuminɪlaodɪkiaisanitaftulesomaarkɪponɪhudʒɪabotaharkaketitɪkennanɪhodʒaduɡutɪdʒedinɪaninɪwankanaharkaki??anɪtafapaulonɪnaɡa?aɪsanɪfudahadananɪhɪdanɪindedinaebitɪwakʼaɪsanɪwolinɪdʒiratinnaebafɪnaɡa?ɪhakesanɪtahunuhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufamarotesanifɪwakʼaɡalatadebimnekadatʃatennakesamakʼakesanɪdomnawontɪakanatifɪnuwakʼafɪabakennaduratɪkʼabannaakaɪsanɪduɡefatʃatesanɪhudʒinɪhodʒatanɪakadʒalaltɪtesanɪhudʒɪɡudoɪsanɪtoltʃɪsifteammalleakaabdinɪtesanɪabo?esokristokesadʒabdunuɪmbennaobole?anɪtenna tinɪwanbarsɪsanɪduɡafetubarsisumaltedʒarolenɪufɪiwolalinakʼalbɪhoradaufɪkʼorkʼoradaduɡefatʃadansafɪdʒalalafɪobsahoradadʒedinɪakasumadʒarolenadenɪlenɪakanadenɪdʒɪrennakʼulkʼullokʼabdutahadʒedinɪnamahamatanɪ?okhanɪtissefarsoleintahinadʒedinɪwandansabarsisumalteakanadenɪkaimadʒalaladirsatifɪtaɪdʒolleufɪbarateufɪkʼorkʼoratekʼulkʼullomtehallakʼomafɪadabanɪdirsaufɪsalfatuakanamɪtokolenɪhamennadubɪwakʼaindubanneakaskasumakaɪmalenɪufɪkʼorkʼoradadʒedinɪatinɪakhekhahudʒɪdansawantʃʼahaufakesatɪworratahɪbarsisatantedʒabesɪakadansabarsisɪdubɪdansatanamɪdandaeintufannedubaduakaɲapɪkankewannunɪdʒedudabetʃʼahaerutisselelenɪhaabotɪufɪɡutewantoltʃitutʃʼahaufanɪɡammatʃiftuammalledubɪafanɪkesadebifteabotɪwomadurainhatinɪammohadansomafɪduɡaɡarsɪsanɪakabarsisawakʼakʼarkʼarsakennawantoltʃanɪtʃʼahaufakesatɪduɡesituwontɪakanatifɪwakʼɪ?aebaufɪmarobafamanamatʃʼahaufatifɪmulliseebitɪsuninɪwannunɪdʒetuwanhamtukawakʼɪinfenefɪdaranafalakisaufɪkʼorkʼoradakʼadʒelalafatanakesadʒɪrennawakʼɪfedukesataatoɡu??aebakanuabdannueɡannuɡu??aɡudinnɪwakʼaɡudafɪkʼarkʼarsakenna?esokrɪstonɪmullatuinnɪnafaufɪnukenneakahamennatʃʼahaufakesanubaseɡumɪɪsakʼulkʼullotawandansatoltʃufetunutoltʃuwankananamabarsisɪdʒabennakanketʃʼahaufanɪnamasitʃʼahaakʼasutʃʼahaufadʒabesɪɡorsɪnamɪtokolenɪsiintufatinɪɡumɪtetinɪdubɪdʒaralafafidutifɪtaworraɡuɡurdatʃʼahaakʼasaɡutawandansatʃʼahaufatoltʃadʒedɪkʼabsisɪhamennanamatokoleindubatinaammohodʒdʒatʃʼahaufanaɡa?afɪdʒalafɪadabadansanɪnamatʃʼahaufawolinɪtadʒedinɪwontɪakanatifɪnulenɪdurɪdalledubɪintʃakʼamnetawollalatoltʃitunutɪsseledaranafatifɪɡammadaɡosatʃʼahaufatanedʒɪrennakennatʃʼahaufadallumafɪdibɪkesatennenamɪhedunɪnudʒibenulenɪworradʒɪbineammonasufɪdʒalaltɪwakʼakʼarkʼarsakennamullannanɪinnɪnubasemarohudʒɪdansanuhodʒannefɪnitɪammomaronasuisatifɪnubaselubukʼulkʼullonɪnudikʼeɪsinɪdalotaharesafɪdʒɪrennaharanukennitewontɪakanatifɪwakʼɪɡudɪsetɪlubuufɪnurabusemaro?esokristokʼarkʼarsakennatifɪakamaroebaisatifɪnuwakʼanɪwoltɪararamnedʒɪrennaheɡerɪkanuabdannuarɡannudʒetʃɪkuninɪkaduɡatɪaninɪsiwanka amatɪdʒaraammallewantʃʼahaufawakʼatɪdʒaremusanɪhudʒɪmanawakʼatʃʼahaufaɡuteinnɪhodʒatuwanwakʼɪheɡerɪdubatutʃʼahaufaladubateammokrɪstonɪakailmamanaabakʼorkʼoratuwantʃʼahaufaɡutenumanaɪsatɪ?onuwanabdannusodamaleɡaradʒabanneduɡefanne?okʼonkʼowakʼaarradaɡetanɪakadurɪmatadʒabatanɪwakʼadɪdanɪammaindɪdinaakaɡafadurɪlafaɡamodʒɪkesatɪisailalatanɪatʃitɪababotɪtesanɪnatɪɡamteatowananinɪɡannaafurtamakesatɪtoltʃearɡɪtelemarowankanatifɪaninɪworrakanatɪdalanewandʒedeworrɪkunɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufawanhereɡukesatɪwollalakʼabatakakarakɪ??aimbaranneaninɪdalanekakhadewandʒedeworrɪkunɪhaɡumadʒirubokʼotaaninɪworrakurfeseinarɡatuobole?anɪtɪ??aeɡadaakanamɪtokolenɪɪsanɪkesaɡarahamakainduɡefannearɡatewakʼadʒɪrennaɪraɡarɪnɡaleammoakadabɪnamatokole?akesobemataindʒabesineɡu??atʃʼahaufawolɪkʼarkʼarahaɡatafinɪarradʒetutʃʼahaufanunɪtʃʼahauftɪkrɪstonɪwolɪwahela?onuduɡefatʃatennahaɡamummedʒabesinekʼabanne?okʼonkʼowakʼaarradaɡetanɪakadurɪmatadʒabatanɪwakʼadɪdanɪindɪdinawakʼɪɡannaafurtamaennutɪdalaneworradabatoltʃekalafaɡamodʒɪkesatɪrawatetʃʼahaufaɡafawakʼɪkhakhateworrɪkunɪhaɡumadʒirubokʼotaaninɪworrakurfeseinarɡatudʒedeinnɪwanennudubateinnɪwanworradubɪɪsadidedubatetanafɪakaworrɪwanduɡefatʃudɪdefɪbokʼotasunɪarɡatʃudadabearɡinadubawakʼɪ?anutɪkakhateakanuolseneisawolinɪbokʼonnutanafɪnukʼorkʼoratʃumalleakaɪsanɪtokolenɪbokʼotasunɪɪndamnenulenɪakumaworraodudansadaɡenneworrɪodudansa?adaɡa?eammowomaworraɪmbanemarodaɡennanɪduɡefatʃanɪimfudatɪnifɪnuworrɪduɡefateolsennewakʼawolinɪbokʼonnaakumainnɪdʒedeaninɪdalanekakhadewandʒedeworrɪkunɪhaɡumadʒirubokʼotaaninɪworrakurfeseinarɡatuatohudʒinɪɪsatadurɪtaumamahobateleinnɪwankanaladubatewontɪakanatifɪfullatokotafinɪwanɡu??atorbesoakanadʒetɪwakʼɪɡu??atorbesohudʒɪufɪtʃʼahaufaɪrabokʼoteammallewandubɪtanadubatanɪworrɪkunɪhaɡumadʒirubokʼotaaninɪworrakurfeseinarɡatuworrɪkʼaraodudansadaɡa?ebokʼotasunɪinarɡannewanwakʼadidanifɪammonamaɡarɪbokʼotasunɪinarɡatamarowankanatifɪwakʼɪɡu??adibɪfohatekaarradʒedanɪɡannahedueɡɪsunɪafanɪdaudɪtinɪdubatetafɪkʼaramakʼadanɪkesatɪwandʒede?okʼonkʼowakʼaarradaɡetanɪmatadʒabatanɪindɪdinatanafɪbokʼotaɡumɪwakʼaɪndʒiraammalleakumawakʼɪɡu??asabatobokʼotesunɪwontɪakanatifɪnamɪbokʼotawakʼɪkennufɪarɡatutʃʼahauftɪakumawakʼɪhudʒɪɪsaɪrabokʼotebokʼotatanafɪnuhaɡadandennudʒabatʃumalleakabokʼotasunɪarɡannununɪtokolenɪakaworrɪsunɪtʃʼahaakʼasudidebokʼotaarɡatʃudadabetahuhɪmmallewontɪakanatifɪdubinɪwakʼadʒɪrennakʼabdɪammalledʒabduʃeftɪtʃʼahaufairakʼarakʼabdɪnafatʃʼahaufatarsaftɪhaɡafullaonnefɪlubunɪwoltɪedʒɪtufɪfullamɪtafɪdutɪwoltɪedʒituɪsinɪfedifɪhereɡaɡaranamaɪlaltɪwantokoledandanɪwakʼaindossanɪwontɪlafakesadʒiratʃʼahauftɪilaɪsaduradʒirtɪisaduratɪwankennatʃʼahaufahɪmatʃumalletanafɪduɡefatʃatennadʒabesumalenukʼalluɡudakafulawakʼadurasenekʼamna?esoilmawakʼakʼallunɪkennaɡudanɪnamalafinnakennanahudidunitɪammonukʼalluɡudakaakumakennakaratʃʼahaufanɪilalatanɪammodabaintoltʃinɪkʼamnatanafɪdʒabannebartʃumawakʼatɪdufumalefullaebitɪdʒirtuatʃitɪnasufɪebaarɡannatahodʒdʒanudibakʼabannenukʼarkʼartukʼalluɡudadʒidunamakesafohatanɪakamaronamatifɪwakʼahodʒatuinnɪwanwakʼabasanifɪsoriotadababaftubasanamadallefɪkawollalatoltʃuobseɡorsudandawaninnɪlenɪlafinnakʼabufɪmarowankanatifɪinnɪmarodabaɡumɪtʃʼahaallanitɪammomarodabaufilesoriokʼallumalenamɪɡudinnakanaufinɪimfudatuammowakʼatɪ?amaakumadurɪharunɪ?amanɪatinɪilmakɪ??aaninɪarra?aabasitaheatinɪkʼalluhaɡaheɡeriledʒirutataadakʼallumatamelkɪtsedekɪɡulaammoatoilmawakʼataheleinnɪkaraɡarɡalatinɪwakʼaɡutubarateinnɪkʼitomnanɪababafamaheɡerɪkanamaisasalfatutʃʼahaufatahewakʼɪkʼalluɡudaisatoltʃeadakʼallumamelkɪtsedekɪɡulawanhedutɪdʒiratasilanudubɪtanaɪratɪdʒennuammoɡudodʒabatɪakaisanitɪhimnuwanɪsanɪɡudomatadʒabatanifɪɪsanɪhodʒdʒatanadʒaranamabarsisutahumaltanɪufiftunamawankʼaratadubɪwakʼaɪsanɪbarsisufetanɪɪsanɪharmahodumaltanɪsaɡaledʒabduindandetanɪwontɪakanatifɪnamɪharmahoduammalleɪdʒolledarafɪduɡaɡarɡarɪɪmbekhuammosaɡalenɪdʒadʒabdunɪtanamaɡuɡurdatɪkahubatʃaarɡatewandansafɪhamtuɡarɡarɪbekhutanafɪbarsisakʼaratakristolafadamnedurademnetahaɡasɪiradʒadʒabdubaratʃumallenuwan?a?abaduɡefatʃatennadebineke?annufɪɪnkʼamnutaakahudʒɪwomaɪmbaneɪradebɪtifawakʼaduɡefatʃafabarsisawanbatɪsotifɪtaharkairaka?anifɪkaisanamaduetifɪkʼorsumaheɡerɪduftu?owakʼɪdʒedeakanatoltʃinanamakʼaraduɡefateeɡelakiseɪrabadedandanɪdabaɪrawodebɪsanɪdurɪworrɪifsawakʼakesadʒiraɡalataɡubamiefatekʼodaufɪkalubukʼulkʼulloarɡateakadubinɪwakʼadansaarɡanɪammalledʒabennadalotadufulebekhanɪamma?adʒɪɡanɪtanafɪdandanɪdabairaindebɪsanɪwanilmawakʼaammallemukhaɪratɪfannɪsanɪnamatʃʼahaufaduratɪtʃʼahaersanifɪlafaɡu??atʃʼahaufabɪsanɪdudetamɪdanɪitɪobranɪabaitɪobrebaftuwakʼɪinebisaammo?okʼoratifɪharamaɡudobaftewomaɪmbatuwakʼɪheɡerɪinabaraeɡeibɪdanɪballesanɪammo?oakasɪdubanneledʒalanɪtennanuwankesanɪ?akʼumnenuɪmbennaakaɪsanɪebaɡudotabafamaɪsanɪkennitukʼabdanɪwakʼɪkaduɡatɪinnɪhudʒɪɪsanɪmaroisadʒalatanifɪtoltʃɪtanɪɪndeduhodʒdʒaɪsanɪɡumɪwakʼadurɪkʼarkʼartanɪarralekʼarkʼartanɪfedinɪtennaɡudonɪakaɪsanɪowaammakʼabdanɪkanahaɡamummetetaninɪakawontɪɪsanɪhereɡatanɪtʃʼahauftɪisanitatunuisanilalaftanɪɪmfenuammoakaworraduɡefateobsutatanɪfenaakawanwakʼɪkakhatearɡatanɪɡafawakʼɪabrahamutɪkakhateinnɪakawankʼaradʒedeɡutukakhatewannamɪtokolenɪkaisairaɡudaindʒɪrrefɪinnɪɡafakakhatemakʼaufɪdaeinnɪwandʒedeaninɪinkakhadaakasiebiseɪlmanɪhedusikennuabrahamunɪobsedʒennanɪwanwakʼɪitɪkakhatearɡate?onamɪkakhatuinnɪmakʼanamaisairadʒirutinɪkakhataammallekakhunɪwannamɪɪratɪwoldabetʃʼahaufainduɡefatʃiftɪwakʼɪworrawaninnɪitɪkhakhatearɡatetʃʼahaufadɪdeseitɪhimufedeakakʼalbɪufɪɡarɪnɡalfannetanafɪakadʒabakakhatedubawanlamatɪdʒirataindʒɪdʒiramnefɪtawakʼɪdandaeɪratɪinkɪ??imneabdinɪtunɪdʒabduakamalenudʒabesitɪɪsinɪdʒabdufɪduɡaammalleɡollamanawakʼakaɡubadʒirukesasentɪhaɡafullakʼulkʼullo?esonɪ?amarotennafɪnuduraseneinnɪ?akʼalluɡudahaɡaheɡerɪtaheadakʼallumamelkɪtsedekɪɡulaabrahamunɪkʼodakudannesokawankʼabutʃʼahaufakennefɪmakʼanɪkʼarakamelkɪtsedekɪha??uduɡatɪmaroinnɪha??usalemutifɪmakʼanɪɪsaammalleha??unaɡa?atɪmelkɪtsedekinɪabafɪhadaɪnkʼabuammalleababotaleɪnkʼabudalotafɪduaɪsalenamɪɪmbekhuinnɪakailmawakʼadʒirahaɡadʒirukʼalluakainnɪɡudainaɡartanɪ?uabrahamunɪabanɪkennaɡudanɪkʼod ufɪtifɪammallemarodabanamaleinnɪsoriotokobasetakakʼubatʃʼahaallaɡafanafaufɪbaseserɪmusanamakʼiteintahinɪkʼaloleɡuɡurdotoltʃaammokakhunɪwakʼataeɡɪseradufteilmafohatɪkahaɡaheɡerɪkʼitetoltʃanɪinnɪhudʒɪkʼalluɡudafullakʼulkʼullotɪhodʒatawaroabonɪdabekesatanamɪdabenitɪkʼalluɡudatʃʼahaufaakainnɪɡalatafɪsoriowakʼabasufohatanɪtanafɪkʼallitʃɪkennaɡudalenɪwobasumale?osilainnɪlafadʒɪratekʼallutahuindandauwanadasera?ahudaɡulakʼalolenɪɡalatabaftudʒɪrtufɪhudʒinɪworrɪakakʼalolehodʒatuɡandɪdufɪfakennumawanɡubadʒɪratɪmusalenɪakumakanaɡafainnɪdɪkʼumawaroindabinɪwakʼɪwandʒedenɪwantʃʼahaufaakumaɡaraɡubatɪarɡiteɡulatoltʃɪammo?esonɪ?ahudʒɪkʼallumatataworraɪradʒirtuarɡateakumawoldakʼisɪinnɪwakʼafɪnamadʒɪdutɪtoltʃelenɪiradansawontɪakanatifɪwoldakʼisɪsuninɪkakhuwaniradansakʼaba?osilawoldakʼisɪkʼarakʼitetahewontɪkalamesotoltʃanifɪɪndʒirtuammowakʼɪwollalaɡumɪɪsaɪratɪarɡewandʒedeabonɪwandʒeduɡu??anɪɪndufakaaninɪwoldakʼisaharaɡosaisraelɪtifɪta?udawolinɪtolfaduakawoldakʼisaaninɪababotaworrawolinɪtoltʃetɪnitɪɡafaaninɪworraharkakʼabelafamɪsirɪkesabaseworrɪwoldakʼisaaninɪworrawolinɪtoltʃeindʒabesinetanafɪaninɪwanworrai?alletuninɪdubɪabowakʼɪdʒedeabowandʒeduwoldakʼisɪtakatanaɡosaisraelɪwolinɪtoltʃukanaaninɪserakɪ??akʼalbɪworrakesaka?eɡaraworrakesatɪtafaaninɪwakʼaworratahaworrɪlenɪɡumɪtɪ??atahanamɪtokolenɪɡafasɪnamadibɪimbarsisu?okhanɪnamɪtokolenɪobolesaufɪtinɪabobekhaɪndʒeduwontɪakanatifɪworrɪtʃʼahauftɪnabekhadɪkʼafɪɡudanɪworralenɪaninɪtʃʼahaubuworrainararamafɪitɪdebiedabaworrainkʼabaduwanwoldakʼisaharadubannanɪwakʼɪkakʼaraladullomsewontɪdullomatetʃʼahaɪtʃitetʃʼahauftɪ?osubadɪwoldakʼisɪkʼaraadakadatʃatifɪfullawakʼaitɪkadatanɪnamɪharkanɪmɪdasekʼabawarodabanɪbadaɪsifullakʼulkʼullodʒedanɪbadasunɪkesaɪfsefɪmesafɪkʼitawakʼabasanitɪdʒiraɡollalamesodubawarotafullafullatʃʼahaufairakʼulkʼullodʒedanitɪdʒiraisɪkesafullahɪtanaitɪarsanɪtaworkʼinɪmidasanifɪsandukʼawoldakʼisakawakʼakaworkʼɪdibanitɪdʒirasandukʼɪkanɪeleworkʼɪtasaɡalemannadʒedanɪkʼabdufɪuleharunɪtabalabaftefɪdakhalamakadubɪwoldakʼisaɪratɪtafisakʼabduk ananɪammowollalasunɪobsɪtanɪmanɪisanibatɪammo?owankʼadʒelatoltʃɪtanɪɡarɡalaobsɪtanɪwakʼɪmarosunifɪɪsanɪebisawankanatɪwakʼɪɪsanɪ?amewontɪakasɪtifɪkrɪstonɪdurɪmarotesanifɪɡarɡaleakhekhaisanitaheakaɪsanɪfanaɪsaɡula?atanɪinnɪtakadabaintoltʃine?okhanɪnamɪtokolenɪisadaradubatuindaɡenneɡafaisaarabsanɪinnɪtakanamainarabsineisaɡarɡaltʃɪnanɪinnɪnamatokoleinsodatʃimneammoabdɪufɪwakʼaduɡakaduɡaɡulawokʼoruɡubake?atekrɪstonɪdabakennamaskalitɪbateakanudabanɪdoneduɡanɪdʒɪrannumadaisatinɪɪsanɪfa??ɪsanɪɪsanɪkʼaraakaholɪ?ekaraɪrabadedʒɪrtanɪammoamma?atissɪtufɪkʼorkʼoratulubutesanitɪdebɪtanɪworrɪadabakesanɪdansafɪkʼulkʼulloarɡematʃamatafilatʃafɪfahɪnakʼatʃafɪwo?anakʼatanɪkesatɪʃobuhɪmmalleammomidaɡumtɪtesanɪtaɡarakesatahinnamidaɡumalubulanafɪobsataɪndʒaretuninɪwakʼaduratɪwanɡudokarakananɪnadenɪdurɪtawakʼaabdateufɪmidasitedɪrsoleufitɪtʃʼahaertesaranɪdurɪakasɪtateɪsinɪabrahamutʃʼahaerteakaabaufɪhereɡateɪsanɪammaɪdʒolleɪsitatanɪ?owandansatoltʃɪtanɪwomainsodannedubɪbufatahereɡatakafɪɡaratakakʼabatʃumaltanɪakaobole?anɪwolɪdʒaladawolɪnahawolɪsalfadanamawanhamtuɪsanɪtoltʃewanhamtuintoltʃinanamaɪsanɪabareinabarinaammoebɪsafɪwontɪakanatifɪwakʼɪɡafaɪsanɪ?ameebaisanikennadʒedeakumatafinɪdʒetunamɪdʒɪrennafedukaɡammadanɪtaufeduwanhamtudubatʃuhɪmmalledaraledubatʃuhɪmmalleinnɪhamennaɪradebiewandansatoltʃumaleammallenaɡa?adʒabesebarbadumalewontɪakanatifɪabonɪilaufɪtinɪworraduɡakʼorkʼorateɡurraufɪtinɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufakadatʃaworradaɡa?aammoworrahamennatoltʃuinnɪdudaitɪɡarɡalaentuwoɪsanɪtoltʃa?oɪsanɪwandansaɡudotoltʃufetanɪammo?owandansatoltʃɪtanɪɪsanɪɡarɡaltʃanilea??anakesanɪnamainsodatinaɡaraufɪindaninaammoɡarakesanɪkesatɪkristoɡudisaaboisatolfadanamawanabdɪɪsanɪufɪkesakʼabdanɪɪsanɪɡafatuakaitɪhimatanɪhodʒdʒatʃʼahaufakurfotahaammoɡaralafɪnatifɪkatʃʼahaeratinɪtoltʃakʼalbɪtesanɪkʼulkʼullefadaaka?oɪsanɪarabsanɪnamɪmaroɪsanɪadabadansanɪkristoɡula?atanifɪhamennaisanitɪdubatutʃʼahaeruwontɪakanatifɪɡudoiradansa?owandansafɪɡarɡalanɪfullawanhamtufɪɡarɡalanɪ?oɪsinɪfedɪwakʼatatewontɪakanatifɪkristolenɪnamɪdansanɪm omaroɪsanɪkristɪanatifɪɪsanɪɡarɡaltʃanɪintʃerinaammoɡalatawakʼadebisawanɪsanɪmakʼakristokʼabdanifɪhodʒdʒanɪkʼorsuma?aɡetekʼarafiteworrawakʼakʼoranɪ?okʼaranunɪitɪke?atanɪworraodudansatawakʼainduɡefannemanɪtoltʃanɪakumatafinɪdʒetu?oakɪnamɪdansanɪbahuɡarɡalatatedʒaradabakawakʼaɪmbennemanɪtoltʃanɪtanafɪworrɪmarofediwakʼatɪɡarɡaluhahudʒɪufɪdansanɪharkanamaworraumekahodʒdʒatʃʼahaufakakhuufɪɡututɪkennutɪaninɪdʒaroleɡumɪtadʒidutesanɪdʒirtukadadaanɪlenɪdʒarsaaninɪɡarɡalakristoilati??anɪarɡedubaɡudinnaeɡɪtanamullɪsanɪkʼodakesakʼabaaninɪɪsanɪkadadaholɪ?ewakʼɪisanikenneɡaratokonɪtissaɡaralamanitɪakumawakʼɪakaɪsanɪtoltʃɪtanɪfeduhudʒɪtesanɪhorɪkesaarɡatanɪtʃʼahaallafɪintoltʃinaammofedinɪtoltʃaworraharkakesanitɪkennanɪimohatinaammoakhekhadansaholɪ?etahadubaɡafatissɪtunɪɡudonɪduftusureha??umatahaɡadʒirtuadɪtʃʼahaamaarɡatanɪharkawakʼadʒalatɪufɪdɪkʼesadubaakainnɪ?ohodʒdʒanɪɡeteɪsanɪɡudisuɡarɡalakesanɪtʃʼahaufaharkaɪsatɪkennadawontɪakanatifɪinnɪɪsanɪdʒalatekʼorkʼoratakurfotaeɡadaɲapɪkesanɪʃetanɪakaɲentʃaitanademenamaɲatubarbadaduɡefatʃatesanɪdʒabesaisadidaɪsanɪimbetanɪakanamɪakakesanɪduɡefatelafatʃʼahaufakesaakumakesanɪɡarɡaludʒiruammoeɡɪɪsanɪbultɪdikʼotokoɡarɡaltanɪwakʼɪebatʃʼahaufakaakaɡudinnakristowolinɪkʼodatanɪɪsanɪ?ameɪsanɪkʼɪtesedʒabennaisanikenne?a?abadʒabaisanimɪdasainnɪdʒabennaammatifɪkaheɡerilearɡatinnaaminɪdunɡodʒalalakristɪanatinɪnaɡa?awolfudanaɡennɪɪsanɪworrakristotʃʼahaufawolinɪtahinnamakʼanɪkɪ??asɪmonɪpetroaninɪhodʒatufɪerɡatu?esokristoaninɪtatabetanaɡaraworraduɡawakʼatifɪtakʼarkʼarsa?esokristotinɪduɡefatʃadansaakatennaarɡatetɪtafaebafɪnaɡa?aɡudisaarɡadamarohubatʃawakʼatifɪta?esoabokennadʒabennɪɪsadʒabennawakʼatɪ?awannuarɡatʃumaletʃʼahaufanukenneakadʒɪrennadansanɪtennuwannunamanu?ameɡudɪnnafɪdansomaufɪnukʼodebennufɪkarakananɪinnɪ?akakhudansataɡudowonubatunukenneakaeɡɪwaninnɪkakhatearɡatanɪdarabadɪtalafatanakesadʒirtudurabatanɪwakʼafakatanɪdʒɪrennaɪsakʼodatanɪmarowankanatifɪdʒabadaakadansomaduɡefatʃatesanitɪdaratanɪdansomakesanitɪhubatʃadaradahubatʃatesanitɪufɪkʼorkʼort annetʃʼahauftɪkawakʼatɪnitɪakakainɪtahuhɪmmalleinnɪɡolɪʃetanataheobolesaufɪɪdʒesekainɪmafɪisaɪdʒesemarowontɪobolesɪɪsatoltʃekʼadʒelatatetainnɪtoltʃehamennatatefɪtanafɪhimaminaobole?anɪtɪ??a?onamɪlafaɪsanɪdʒibenuakadualakimnedʒirennatɪbanebennamaroobole?anɪtennadʒalannufɪwankanabennanamɪnamaindʒalanneduisakesadʒiranamɪobolesaufɪdʒibu?anamaɪdʒeseɪsanɪimbetanɪakanamɪnamaɪdʒesudʒɪrennaheɡerɪufɪkesaɪnkʼamneakɪnudʒalalabennukanakrɪstonɪdʒɪrennaufɪnubasenulenɪdubadʒɪrennakennaobole?anɪtennabasumalle?onamɪhorɪlafatanakʼabateammalleobolesaɪsakaɡarɡalakʼabuarɡeammoɡaraitɪdʒabateinnɪakaminɪwakʼadʒaladaufinɪdʒedaɪdʒolletɪ??adʒalaltɪtennadubɪafanɪtʃʼahaallaintahinɪammodʒalaladuɡatahumaltetahudʒɪdansanɪufɪmulliftukarakananɪnuakaduɡakesadʒirruufɪbennakarakananɪwakʼaduratɪɡaraufɪdʒabesina?ohereɡɪkennawollalanutɪmurenuakawakʼɪhereɡakennairaɡudakaammallewantʃʼahaufabekhuɪmbennatanafɪdʒallanɪtɪ??a?ohereɡɪkennawollalanutɪimurinɪnuwakʼaduratɪwomainsodannuwankadannutʃʼahaufaisairainarɡannamaronuseraɪsaɡunnewanisaɡammatʃisatoltʃɪnufɪwontɪinnɪfedutanaakanuilmaɪsa?esokristoduɡefanneakakrɪstonɪnutɪhimewoldʒalannunamɪserawakʼaɡulademutʃʼahauftɪwakʼakesadʒirawakʼɪlenɪisakesadʒirakarakananɪakawakʼɪnukesadʒirubennawaninnɪlubuufɪnukennefɪdʒalanɪtɪ??anamaaninɪlubuwakʼakʼabudʒedutʃʼahaufainduɡefatinaammoɡarɡarɪhubadaakalubunɪsunɪɡarawakʼatɪduftewontɪakanatifɪraɡɪdarahedunɪ?alafadufekarakananɪlubuwakʼabetanɪlubunɪ?esokrɪstonɪnamatahedʒetutʃʼahauftɪɡarawakʼatɪdufteammolubunɪ?esomormituɡarawakʼatɪɪndumnelubunɪtuninɪɡaraɲapakrɪstotɪdufteakaɪsinɪduftu?adaɡetanɪamma?aduftelafadʒirtɪammoɪdʒolletɪ??aɪsanɪkawakʼatɪraɡotadara?adabsatanɪwontɪakanatifɪlubunɪɪsanɪkesadʒirtulubuworralafakesadʒiruiradʒabduworrɪworralafatɪwanlafadubatamarotanafɪlaftɪworratʃʼahaakʼaftɪammonukawakʼatɪnamɪwakʼabekhutʃʼahauftɪnutʃʼahaakʼasakawakʼaɪmbennenuintʃakʼasukarakananɪlubuduɡatifɪlubudaraɡarɡarɪbennadʒalanɪtɪ??awoldʒalannawandʒalaltɪɡarawakʼatɪduftufɪnamɪdʒalalakʼabutʃʼahauftɪɪdʒollewakʼatɪwakʼaleɪmbekhanamɪdʒalalaɪnkʼamnewakʼaɪmbekhuwanwakʼɪdʒalalatifɪwakʼɪkarakananɪdʒalalaufɪnuɡarsiseinnɪilmaufɪtokotʃalafatɪerɡeakanuɪsanɪdʒɪrennaarɡannudʒalaltɪtanawannuwakʼadʒalannefɪnitɪammowaninnɪnudʒalateilmaufɪnuerɡeakananɪmarohudʒɪisatifɪdabakennanuararamanɪdʒallanɪtɪ??a?owakʼɪhaɡananudʒalatenulenɪwolɪdʒalatʃumallenamɪtakawakʼaarɡeɪndʒiru?onuwoldʒalannewakʼɪnukesadʒiradʒalaltɪɪsanukesatɪkʼɪtomtɪkarakananɪakaduɡumawakʼakesadʒirruammalleakawakʼɪnukesadʒirubennainnɪ?alubuufɪnukenneammallenu?aɡarreammallebi??atɪodesinaakaabanɪilmaufɪerɡeakakʼarkʼarsalafatahunamɪ?esonɪilmawakʼadʒedutʃʼahaufawakʼɪisakesatainnɪlenɪwakʼakesatanulenɪɪmbennaammalleinduɡefannadʒalalawakʼɪnukʼabuwakʼɪdʒalalanamɪdʒalalanɪtautʃʼahauftɪwakʼakesatamarowankanatifɪdʒalaltɪnukʼɪtoftɪakanuɡu??akʼorsumawomainsodannemarodʒɪrennɪkennalafatanakesaakakakristodʒɪrufɪsodanɪdʒalalakesaɪndʒirtudʒalaltɪduɡasodaballesitɪtanafɪnamasodakʼabukesatɪdʒalaltɪinkʼɪtomnewansodanɪɡarɡalakʼabdufɪwontɪnudʒalannufɪwakʼatɪkʼaranudʒalate?onamɪaninɪwakʼadʒaladaufinɪdʒedeammoobolesaufɪdʒibeinnɪki??ibainnɪdandaewakʼakaɪlanɪɪnɡarreindʒalatueɡɪobolesaufɪkaɪlanɪarɡuindʒalannetanafɪserɪkrɪstonɪnukennekananamɪwakʼadʒalatuoboleolesaufiledʒalatʃumalenamɪaka?esonɪkristoduɡefatutʃʼahauftɪɪdʒollewakʼanamɪabadʒalatutʃʼahauftɪilmaɪsaleindʒalatakarakananɪakanuɪdʒollewakʼadʒalannubenna?owakʼadʒalanneseraɪsaɡunnedʒalaltɪwakʼatanaakaseraɪsaɡunnuserɪisalenɪnamaɪndibuwanidʒollenɪwakʼatʃʼahauftɪlafadabsatʃudandetufɪakananɪlafadabsannaduɡefatʃatennanɪentudandaelafadabsatanamaaka?esonɪilmawakʼaduɡefatumale?esokrɪstonɪdɪɡafɪbisaninɪdufeinnɪbɪsanɪtʃʼahaallanɪɪndumneammobisanifɪdɪɡanɪdufeakawontɪkuninɪduɡalubulenɪ?a?uhimtemarolubunɪduɡatifɪduɡasaditɪdʒiralubufɪbisanifɪdiɡaworrɪsadenuwantakadubatanuduɡanamɪdubatuinduɡefannatawakʼɪdʒeduhaɡasɪiradʒabduammalleduɡanɪinnɪwanilmaɪsa?aduɡesenamɪilmawakʼaduɡefatutʃʼahauftɪduɡatanaɡaraufɪkesakʼabaammonamɪwakʼainduɡefanne?awakʼaki??ibatoltʃemaroinnɪwanwakʼɪwanilmaɪsaduɡeseduɡefatʃudɪdefɪduɡalenɪtanawakʼɪ?adʒɪrennaheɡerɪnukennedʒɪrennɪkuninɪilmaɪsakesadʒiranamɪilmakʼabutʃʼahauftɪdʒɪrennakanaɪnkʼabanamɪilmawakʼaɪnkʼamnedʒirennaleɪnkʼabuwontɪaninɪwankanaisanitafufɪakaɪsanɪakadʒɪrennaheɡerɪkʼabdanɪhubatanɪɪsanɪworrɪilmawakʼaduɡefatumarowankanatifɪnufulawakʼaduratɪinsodannunuabdɪkʼamnaakawannufenutʃʼahaufainnɪnukennu?onufedɪɪsaɡulakadanne?onuisa?amannutʃʼahaufainnɪnudaɡa?amaronuakawontɪkuninɪduɡabennufɪnuakainnɪwannukadannutʃʼahaufanukennuɪmbenna?onamɪobolesaufikadabanamaɪdʒesutoltʃuarɡehawakʼakadatufɪakawakʼɪdʒɪrennaɪsakennuwontɪkuninɪwannamadabanamaɪdʒesaintoltʃinɪdubatɪammodabɪnamaɪdʒesuɪndʒiraaninɪdabakanawakʼakadadaisaninɪɪndʒeduwollalɪtʃʼahauftɪdabaammodabɪnamainɪdʒemneɪndʒiranuɪmbennaakaidʒollenɪwakʼadabahodʒdʒatʃʼahaufaintoltʃinewontɪakanatifɪilmawakʼatɪisɪkʼorkʼorataakahamanɪkanɪdandaewomaisɪintoltʃinenuɪmbennaakanukawakʼaammalleakalaftɪtʃʼahauftɪharkahamakanɪkesadʒirtuammallenuɪmbennaakailmɪwakʼadufehubatʃanukenneakasinɪakawakʼɪduɡabennanuwakʼaduɡakesadʒirailmaɪsa?esokristokesawakʼɪduɡakanadʒɪrennɪheɡerɪlenɪkanaɪdʒolletɪ??awakʼotadaralaɡadaaninɪdʒarsɪɡaradʒartɪwakʼafohatetifɪɪdʒolleɪsitaanɪɡudodʒaladutafaaninɪtʃʼahaallanɪɪsanɪindʒaladuammonamɪduɡabekhutʃʼahauftɪɪsanɪdʒalatawontɪakanatifɪduɡanɪnukesadʒirtɪammallehaɡaheɡerɪnuwolinɪtetɪabawakʼafɪ?esokrɪstonɪilmɪabaebafɪnasufɪnaɡa?anukenninnawontɪkuninɪtʃʼahauftɪhaduɡafɪdʒalalanɪtennatatuaninɪakaidʒollenɪtantetaɡarɪduɡakesatetuarɡɪnanɪɡudoɡammadeakumaabanɪnutɪhimetanafɪaninɪsikadadaatonunɪtʃʼahauftɪwoldʒalannaserɪaninɪsitafukuninɪharesanitɪserumahaɡaduritɪharkakʼamnudʒalaltɪaninɪwanisɪdubadutuninɪserawakʼaɡutumaltanɪnunɪdʒetɪserɪɪsanɪhaɡumaduritɪdaɡetanɪkanawoldʒaladanamɪnamasobuhedunɪka?esokrɪstonɪfakatanamaɪntanedʒedu?alafadufenamɪakanakuninɪnamasobainnɪɲapakrɪstotɪufɪeɡadaakawanhodʒatanɪarɡatanɪimballesineammoɡalatakesanɪakadansaarɡatanɪnamɪbarsisakristokesaɪntenneammobɪradabruwakʼaɪnkʼabunamɪbarsisasunɪkesatauabafɪɪlmaleɪnkʼaba?onamɪdufebarsisatananɪsitɪɪndumnenamasunɪbalbalamanaketɪduraimbaninɪnaɡa?aleinfudinɪwontɪakanatifɪnamɪnaɡa?aisafudutʃʼahauftɪw
